\id LUK
\h SAN LUCAS
\toc1 A JE'RA' U JACH TSOYIR U T'…ÖN C'UJ TU TS'IBTA LUCAS
\toc2 SAN LUCAS
\toc3 Lc.
\mt1 A JE'RA' U JACH TSOYIR U T'…ÖN C'UJ TU TS'IBTA LUCAS
\c 1
\s1 Lucas cu y ånxchun u t' ån u b åjob Te√≥filo
\p 
\v 1 Quire' a wer Te√≥filo ya'ab mac caj u y ånxchun u ts'ibticob ba' u ber tu y ånenob uch a ti' y ån tu y åno'onex uch.
\v 2 Caj u y ånxchun u ts'ibticob u t' ån Jes√∫s. Caj u ts'ibtajob a ba' ara'b ten a mac tu yirob Jes√∫s a tu y ånxchun raji'ob xan caj m ånob u yamtejob u tsec'ticob u jach tsoyir u t' ån Jes√∫s.
\v 3 Rajen tin qui' c åxtaj in wirej xan wa taj caj u betaj Jes√∫s uch caj ts'oc in wiric taj a ba' caj u betaj Jes√∫s caj in ts'ibtaj a ba' caj u y ånxchun u betic Jes√∫s hasta baje'rer soc tech a wer u b åjob in b åj, Te√≥filo.
\v 4 Rajen caj in ts'ibtaj tech Te√≥filo soc a toc er a ba' taj tu camsech uch.
\s1 Y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj ya'ara bic tabar u rocha'r Juan ten u n å'. Raji' cu bin yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac
\p 
\v 5 Ti' y ån mac cu reyintic u ru'umin Judea, Herodes u c'aba'. Ra' u q'uinin cuxa'an sacerdote p åcha'an u c'aba' Zacar√≠as. Raji' cu beyaj yejerob yo'nen Ab√≠as. Zacar√≠as caj u raq'uintaj Elisabet ra' yo'nen Aar√≥n raji' yo'nen xan sacerdote.
\v 6 Zacar√≠as yejer u rac' caj yiraj C'uj taj cu quibicob u t' ån C'uj. Caj yiraj C'uj taj cu qui' m ånob ich u tsoyir a ba' caj u ya'araj C'uj.
\v 7 M åna' u parar Elisabet quire' m å'ju c'uchur u yor u parar ånc år. M å' ja wirej, u beri' m åna' u parar, toc ch'ija'an toc ca'turo' yejer u mam baje'rer m å' ju parar ånc år caj ch'ijob uch.
\v 8 Ra' u q'uinin toc p'isa'an tu cu beyaj Zacar√≠as an ten bic sacerdote ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ra' u q'uinin cu beyaj ti' yo'nen Zacar√≠as.
\v 9 An ten bic nanij cu bin u toquic a qui' u boque' ich carem naj. Caj bin Zacar√≠as quir u toquic quire' teta'b ten u yet sacerdote. Caj teta'b Zacar√≠as caj ts'oc u y år åc'tic chan tunich.
\v 10 Ra' u q'uinin cu toquic a qui' u boque' Zacar√≠as, tu cotor a pimo' tan u t' ånicob C'uj ich u tancabir carem naj.
\v 11 Y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj u yesaj u b åj ti' Zacar√≠as. Zacar√≠as caj yiraj y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj, ch'iquicbar ich u noj tu cu toquic a qui' u boque'.
\v 12 Caj yiraj y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj Zacar√≠as jach jaq'uij yor quire' m å' yer ba' u c'at y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj u ch'aj sajquir.
\v 13 Y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïM å' ju jac' år a wor ten, Zacar√≠as. C'uj cu yubic a t' ån rajen cu bin y åntar a parar ca' a p åchej u c'aba' Juan.
\v 14 Ca' bin qui'ac a wor jach manan qui' a wor. Ya'ab mac cu bin qui' tar yorob quire' y ån a parar Zacar√≠as.
\v 15 Quire' a parar ca' bin rochac ten u n å' jach carem  åc åtan u wich C'uj. M å' ju bin yuq'uic u c'ab uva a parar. Bayiri' trago m å' ju bin yuq'uic xan. Toc aca'an ti' u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quir u ts'urintic ca' bin rochac ten u n å'.
\v 16 Jach ya'ab cu bin yacsic tu yor ti' C'uj ca' bin yubej u tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj u winiquirob israel.
\v 17 A parar Juan cu bin u ts'urinbir u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj soc c'ucha'an yor ti' tu cotor ba' an ten bic El√≠as uch. Ca' bin yubob u winiquirob jud√≠o u tsec'tic u t' ån cu bin u quetquintic u yor u pararob yejer u tet soc p'eri'ob yor. Cu bin u tsec'tic ti'ob soc u c'axicob yor a mac a m å' ju quibicob C'uj. Soc cu bin u quibicob a mac taj yor, a mac u ne'er. Soc c'ucha'an yor u c' åmic a Cristojo' ca' bin tac.
\p 
\v 18 Zacar√≠as caj u c'ataj ti' y åjmasir u t' ån Jaj Ts'ur:
\p ‚ÄïBic tabar in jach er taj a ba' ca wac quire' jach uch ch'ijiquen yej in rac'?
\p 
\v 19 Caj u nuncaj y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïA teno', raji' in c'aba' Gabriel, quin beyaj  åc åtan ti' C'uj. Raji' tu tuchi'tajen quir in wa'aric tech a je' jach tsoy t' åna'.
\v 20 A techo' m å' ta quibaj in t' ån a ba' tin toc a'araj tech baje'rer. Baxuquech m å' ju bin joc'ar a t' ån hasta cu c'uchur tu q'uinin u rocha'r a parar ten u n å'. Jeroj cu joc'ar a t' ån. Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu bin joc'ar jach taj an ten bic tin wa'ara tech.
\p 
\v 21 Ti' y ån a pimo' ich tancab tan pajicob ca' joc'ac Zacar√≠as caj jaq'uij yorob quire' oma'an joc' Zacar√≠as ich japnin carem naj.
\v 22 Caj joc' Zacar√≠as m å' ju joc'ar u t' ån. Caj u najtajob a pimo' y ån ba' caj u yiraj Zacar√≠as ich carem naj, caj yesa yejer u c' åb Zacar√≠as quire' m å' ju joc'ar u t' ån.
\p 
\v 23 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u ts'ocar u beyaj Zacar√≠as ich carem naj, caj bin ich yatoch.
\v 24 Caj ur Zacar√≠as ich yatoch caj y ånjij u parar Elisabet. M å' ju c' ås joc'ar hasta manij cinco icn å'. Tan u tucric ich yor, Elisabet caj u tucraj tu yor:
\v 25 ‚ÄúIn Jaj Ts'urir caj u jawsaj in suraquir tu m å' ju y ån tar in parar. Caj u yamtajen C'uj, soc m å' jin p åyic in su'tar ti' a pim baje'rer.‚Äù
\s1 Y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj cu ya'aric je' u rocha'r Jes√∫s ten u n å'
\p 
\v 26 Y ån seis icn å' caj najij u n åc' yejer y år åc' och Elisabet, caj w åc' ås tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj y åjmasir u t' ån ra'iri' Gabriel ca' xic ich u ru'umin Galilea tu cajar Nazaret.
\v 27 Caj bin yiric turiri' xquic a m å' yer ba' hasta cu ch'ic u Mar√≠a quire' Jos√© cu bin raq'uintic Mar√≠a toy c'ata'b ten Jos√©, ra' u nunquir David uch.
\v 28 Y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj oc tu y ån Mar√≠a caj u t' ånaj:
\p ‚ÄïA C'ujo' cu bin u yamtiquech soc jach manan tsoyirech. M åna' u jer xquic baxuco' chen tech tsoyech.
\p 
\v 29 Mar√≠a caj yiraj y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj jaq'uij yor Mar√≠a a ba' yuba ya'ara' ti'. Caj u tucraj tu yor: ‚ÄúBiquinin cu t' åniquen baxuc aro'.‚Äù
\v 30 Y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïM å' ju jac' a wor ten, Mar√≠a, C'uj cu jach qui' qui' yajquintiquech Mar√≠a. M å' ja wirej, C'uj cu bin yesic bic u jach yajquintiquech.
\v 31 Baje'rer cu bin y åntar a parar raji' ca bin a rochej xib, ca' a p åchej u c'aba' JES√öS.
\v 32 A'a parar Jes√∫so' jach ne no'j, raji' u parar C'uj a ti' y ån ca'anano'. A Jaj Ts'ur a C'ujo' cu bin yacsic soc u reyinticob u winiquirob jud√≠o an ten bic u nunquir David caj u reyintajob uch.
\v 33 Raji' cu bin u reyinticob u winiquirob israel munt q'uin m å' ju ts'ocar u reyinticob u winiquirob israel.
\p 
\v 34 Mar√≠a caj u c'ata ti' y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïBic tabar in parar ånc år quire' m å' toy in ch'aj in mami'.
\p 
\v 35 Caj nunca'b ten y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj ara'b ti':
\p ‚ÄïJe' u tar tech u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj soc u y åntar a parar quire' jach y ån u muc' C'uj jach manan ti', rajen cu y åntar a parar. Ca' bin a rochej a parar y ån u bin s åjta'bir ten mac quire' u parar C'uj.
\v 36 Ira wirej, a b åjob a b åj Elisabet baje'rer y ån u parar cax uch ch'ijic y ånij u parar. Cax a ucho' caj u ya'araj u rac'ob m å' u y åntar u parar. Baje'rer y ån ti' seis icn å' caj y ånij u parar xib.
\v 37 Quire' a ba' caj u toc araj C'uj c'ucha'an yor ti' cax ca tucric C'uj m å' c'ucha'an yor ti'.
\p 
\v 38 Caj ya'araj Mar√≠a:
\p ‚ÄïA teno' ‚Äïquij Mar√≠a‚Äï, u c'urewen in Jaj Ts'urir. Arej ti' C'uj a ba' u c'at u betic ten tsoy quire' ti' y ånen quir u y åntar in parar.
\p Caj ts'oc u tsicbar Mar√≠a caj bin y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj.
\s1 Caj bin Mar√≠a irbir Elisabet
\p 
\v 39 M å' jach uch caj yiraj y åjmasir u t' ån Mar√≠a, caj bin yirej u b åjob u b åj Elisabet. Seb caj toc bin Mar√≠a ich u b åjob u b åj quire' ti' c åja'an Elisabet ich u cajar ich u ru'umin Judea a y ån u witsir.
\v 40 Caj oc Mar√≠a ich yatoch Zacar√≠as. Caj t' ån Elisabet ten Mar√≠a.
\v 41 Caj yubaj u t' ån ån Elisabet seb caj pecn åj ich u n åc' Elisabet u chan ochir. Quire' jach y ån ti' u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj Elisabet.
\v 42 Rajen caj c'am t' ån Mar√≠a ten Elisabet quire' qui' yor:
\p ‚ÄïA techo', Mar√≠a, jach manan u qui' yajquintiquech C'uj quire' m åna' u jer xquic teta'b an ten bic tech ‚Äïquij‚Äï. Jach tsoy a parar ca' bin a rochej quire' C'uj cu bin u yamtic a parar.
\v 43 Maqueni' cu tar yiriquen u n å' in Jaj Ts'urir C'uj? M å' ja wirej, tan u s åjtiquen Mar√≠a.
\v 44 Caj tarech caj a t' ånen caj yubaj a t' åniquen caj pecn åj in chan ochir ich in n åc' quire' qui' yor.
\p 
\v 45 Caj ya'araj Elisabet:
\p ‚ÄïJach qui' a wor Mar√≠a quire' ta quibaj u t' ån y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúJe' u y åntar a parar.‚Äù M å' ja wirej, a wer bin u nup'ur a ba' caj u ya'ara tech C'uj.
\p 
\v 46 Caj u nuncaj Mar√≠a:
\q1 Jach qui' in wor quire' caj in wa'araj ti' in Jaj Ts'urir: jach caremech Jaj Ts'urir.
\v 47 Jach qui' in wor  åc åtan C'uj quire' raji' in w åjtaquir.
\v 48 A C'ujo' tu yajquin ten quire' u c'urewen C'uj cax m å' no'jen.
\p Caj ya'araj Mar√≠a:
\q1 Ca' bin ts'ocac in rochic in parar je' ya'aric a jach pimo': C'uj caj u betaj a tsoyo' ti' ten. Baxuc cu bin ya'ariquenob mac hasta cu xur t' ån.
\v 49 A C'ujo' jach manan chichir u muc' quire' caj u yamtajen. M å' ja wirej, jach carem u c'aba' quire' m åna' u si'pir.
\v 50 A C'ujo' cu yajquintic mac quire' a mac cu s åjtic C'uj. Cax ber u q'uinin ca' bin rochac ten u n å' cu bin yajquinbir ten C'uj wa cu s åjtic C'uj.
\v 51 A C'ujo' caj u yesaj wa raji' jach manan chichir u muc', bayiri' u ne'er tu cotor ba'. Raji' c'ucha'an yor u ch'esic u beyaj a mac a cu tucric jach carem, a mac a cu tucricob u jach ne'er ba' soc robob m å' u c'uchur u yor ti' m åna' ba'.
\v 52 A C'ujo' c'ucha'an yor u joc'sic a mac a cu ts'urintic u rac'ob a jach no'j u beyaj. Baxuc xan c'ucha'an yor u ts'ic u beyaj ti' a mac irir ten u rac'ob a m å' no'jo'.
\v 53 A C'ujo' cu bin u qui'quintic yor a mac a jach otsir yejer a ba' jach tsoyo'. Baxuc xan a mac neyaj u taq'uin, m åna' ba' cu ts'ic ti'.
\v 54 A C'ujo' caj u yamtaj u winiquirob israel quire' u yaj. A baywo' caj nup' u t' ån C'uj a ba' caj u toc araj ti' ic nunquir uch.
\v 55 Quire' caj u c' å'otaj u yajquintaj u winiquirob israel.
\m Baxuc caj ara'b ti' ic nunquir Abraham yejer u b åjob soc munt q'uin cu yajquintic ti'ob.
\p 
\v 56 Mar√≠a caj p'at yejer u b åjob u b åj Elisabet. Tres icn å' ti' y ån Mar√≠a ich u b åjob u b åj. Pachir caj u w åc' ås bin Mar√≠a ich yatoch.
\s1 Caj rocha'b ten u n å' Juan raji' cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac
\p 
\v 57 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin caj pararn åjij Elisabet, xib caj u rochaj.
\v 58 Caj yubob u rac'ob caj u rochaj u parar Elisabet, baxuc xan u b åjob caj r åc qui'ji yorob yejer Elisabet. Caj yajquinta'b ten C'uj rajen y ånij u parar. Rajen jach qui' yor u rac'ob yejer u b åjob.
\p 
\v 59 Caj manij turi' semana caj r åc tarob quir u chan sesic u b åq'uer an ten bic nanij cu beticob u winiquirob jud√≠o quir u yacsicob u c'aba'. U c'at u chen p åchicob u w åc' ås jer u c'aba' u tet Zacar√≠as.
\v 60 Caj u ya'araj u n å':
\p ‚ÄïM å' a p åchiquex u c'aba' Zacar√≠as, tsoy ic p åchic u c'aba' Juan.
\p 
\v 61 Caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïM åna' u c'aba' baxuc ich a b åjob.
\p 
\v 62 Caj c'ata'b ti' u tet ba' quir u c'aba' ca bin a p åchej, tan yesicob yejer u c' åb ti' Zacar√≠as.
\v 63 Caj u m åcantaj u c' åb caj u c'ataj u chan pequer che' caj tar purbir ti' caj u ts'ibtaj: ‚ÄúRa' u c'aba' Juan.‚Äù Rajen jaq'uij yor u rac'ob.
\v 64 Ray u q'uinino' seb caj joc' u t' ån Zacar√≠as caj u y ånxchun u t' ånic C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj.
\p 
\v 65 A mac ti' c åja'an tu cajar Zacar√≠as caj u ch'aj sajaquirob caj r åc m ån u jumintob ich tu cotor u ru'umin u witsir u ru'umin Judea a ba' u ber Zacar√≠as caj u p åchaj u c'aba' u parar.
\v 66 Caj yubob u m ån u jumintej caj u tucrob tu yor:
\p ‚ÄïA ba' u ber u parar Zacar√≠as?
\p Quire' a C'ujo' cu bin yamta'bir Juan.
\s1 Zacar√≠as cu c'ay quire' qui' yor
\p 
\v 67 U tet Juan Zacar√≠as jach y ån ti' u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj, rajen caj ya'araj ti' C'uj:
\q1 
\v 68 Jach caremech C'uj, quire' caj a c ånantaj u winiquirob israel. M å' ja wirej, caj a tacato'on baxuc caj a yamtaj ti'ob.
\v 69 A C'ujo' caj u ts'aj to'on ij c åjtaquir a mac manan chichir u muc'. Ra' cu tar ti' ic nunquir David a caj u reyintaj u winiquirob israel uch.
\v 70 Baxuc caj u toc araj ti' a mac ts'a'b u tucur ten C'uj uch.
\v 71 Baxuc caj u toc araj C'uj uch: ‚ÄúJe' in taquiquechex ti' a mac cu p'actiquechex a mac a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o‚Äù, baxuc caj u ya'araj C'uj.
\v 72 A C'ujo' caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúJe' in yajquintic ti' ic nunquir tan u yamtic ti'ob. M å' ju bin tubur ti' a ba' caj u toc araj uch.‚Äù
\v 73 Baxuc caj toc ara'b ti' ic nunquir Abraham uch:
\v 74 ‚ÄúCu bin tacbir ti' a mac cu p'actico'on soc c'ucha'an ij cor ij c'ujintic C'uj soc m å' ic ch'ic sajaquir ti' mac.‚Äù
\v 75 Caj u chajex to'on ij cacsic tij cor soc ij c ånic C'uj soc u bur u q'uinin ic manex tu tsoyir  åc åtan ti' hasta cu xur t' ån.
\v 76 Caj ya'araj Zacar√≠as ti' u parar: ‚ÄúA techo', in pararech, je' u t' åniquech y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj caj bin a p åyic u ber ic Jaj Ts'urir soc yer a rac'ob u winiquirob jud√≠o je' u tar Jaj Ts'ure'.
\v 77 A C'ujo' caj u tetaj to'on a techo', chan och, ca bin a wa'aric C'uj cu jawsic ic si'pir quir u taquic to'on.
\v 78 Quire' u jach tsoyir u pixam C'uj caj u yajquintaj to'on ca' bin tac tu q'uinin cu c'uchur.
\v 79 Ij c åjtaquir je' u sasich åjir u pixam ten C'uj. A mac a cu man tu yac'birir y ån u c'oxar u pixam ten C'uj quir u sasich åjir u pixamob. Cu bin u r åc ruc'sic a ba' quic s åjtic ij quimin.‚Äù
\p 
\v 80 Caj ch'ijij Juan caj bin u c åjtar ich t åcay ru'um. Caj u qui' c ånaj C'uj Juan. Hasta c'uchij tu q'uinin caj u yesaj u b åj ti' u rac'ob u winiquirob israel y åjp åyiren u ber Jaj Ts'ur.
\c 2
\s1 Caj rocha'b Jes√∫s ten u n å'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ1.18‚Äë25)
\p 
\v 1 Ray u q'uinin Augusto caj u reyintaj u ru'umin u winiquirob romano caj ya'araj rey ti' u winiquirob:
\p ‚ÄïCa' xiquechex a ts'ibtex a c'aba' quir in wiric mun u winiquirob y ån tera'. Tu cotor mac y ån u bin u ts'ibtic u c'aba'.
\p Baxuc caj ya'araj C√©sar Augusto.
\v 2 A je' beyaja' caj u ts'ibtajob u c'aba'. Ra' tu y ån bat'an ts'ibtaj u c'aba' caj oc u gobernador u ru'umin Siria, Cirenio, u c'aba' gobernador.
\v 3 Tu cotor ich u cajaririri'ej y ån u ts'ibtic u c'aba' xan. Jujuntur cu bin u ts'ibtic u c'aba' ich u jach cajar.
\v 4 Caj bin Jos√©, caj ruq'uij ti' u cajar Nazaret caj bin ich u ru'umin Judea quir u c'uchur tu cajar Bel√©n. Caj bin u ts'ibtej Jos√© u c'aba' ich Bel√©n quire' ra' u cajar u nunquir David tu rocha'b ten u n å'. Rajen caj u j åm åch p' åtaj u cajar Nazaret quir u bin.
\v 5 Caj binob Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a ich Bel√©n quir u ts'ibticob u c'aba'. Jos√© m å' toy u jach raq'uintej Mar√≠a chen tabar u rochic u parar.
\v 6 Ti' y ån Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a ich u cajar Bel√©n caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u rochic u parar.
\v 7 Mar√≠a caj u rochaj u chan och xib. Raji' tu y ånx rochaj Mar√≠a. Caj u tapa Mar√≠a yejer u tep' caj u chaquintaj tu cu bin u jansej y år åc' wac åx quire' m å' tu cu m åj ånticob naj quir u wen ånob quire' jach pimob caj u r åc ts'ibtajob u c'aba'.
\s1 Caj tarob y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj ich tu cu c ånanticob y år åc' t åm ån yuc
\p 
\v 8 B åyt åc ich u cajar Bel√©n ti' y ån y åjc ånany åjirob y år åc' t åm ån yuc. Cax ac'bir caj u c ånantajob y år åc' t åm ån yuc. Ti' y ånob tu m åna' u che'er chen suc y ån.
\v 9 Seb caj tar ch'ictar y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj tu y ån y åjc ånany åjirob t åm ån yuc caj tar u sasir C'uj caj sasich åjij tu y ånob. Rajen jach jaq'ui yorob.
\v 10 Caj ya'araj y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïM å' u jac' årex a worex ten quire' caj taren in wa'aric techex a je' tsoy t' åna'. Caj taren in wa'aric tech soc u qui'tar yor tu cotor mac.
\v 11 Baje'rer rocha'b ten u n å' ich u cajar Bel√©n. Ra' a w åjtaquirex a caj u ya'ara y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj je' u tare'. Raji' Cristo Jaj Ts'ur a' tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj.
\v 12 Soc a werex a ba' quin waquextech jaj. Je' a wiriquex charic tu cu jansic y år åc' wac åx ich u najir y år åc' wac åx.
\p 
\v 13 Seb caj tar u jer ya'ab y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj. Jach pim caj tarob. Ti' u tar ich ca'anan. Caj u y ånxchun u c' åyicob C'uj y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj. Caj u c' åyob C'uj:
\q1 
\v 14 Jach caremech C'uj a techo' a ti' y ånech ich ca'anan. Jach qui' yor a mac a ti' y ån ich yoc'ocab a tu qui' quiquintajob a wor C'uj. M å' ja wirej, caj a yamtaj ti'ob.
\m Baxuc caj c' åyajob y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj.
\p 
\v 15 Caj w åc' ås binob y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj ich ca'anan. Caj ya'arob ti' u rac'ob y åjc ånany åjirob:
\p ‚ÄïCa' xico'onex ich u cajar Bel√©n ca' ij quirej a ba' caj u ya'araj to'on y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj. Ca' ij quirej ba' u ber ti'.
\p 
\v 16 Ts'ajan yor binob caj u nup'ajob Mar√≠a yejer Jos√© ich u najir tu cu jansicob y år åc' wac åx. Ti' chara'an u chan ochir Mar√≠a tu cu jansic y år åc' wac åx. Caj ts'oc yiricob u chan ochir.
\v 17 Y åjc ånany åjirob t åm ån yuc caj ara'b ti' Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a a ba' ara'b ti'ob ten y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj. Caj ya'arob ba' cu bin u betic u chan ochir ich u rac'ob u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\v 18 Caj jac'ob yor tu cotor a caj u yuba ba' caj u ya'arajob y åjc ånany åjirob t åm ån yuc. Tu tsicb åtob bic tabar u chan ochir Mar√≠a.
\v 19 Mar√≠a caj u qui' tucraj a ba' yuba ya'ara'r ten y åjc ånany åjirob t åm ån yuc. Rajra' cu tucric ti' tu yor Mar√≠a.
\v 20 Caj w åc' ås sutn åjob y åjc ånany åjirob t åm ån yuc quir u beyaj. Caj ya'arob ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj, jach caremech C'uj quire' tij quiraj tij quich quire' baxuc caj a wa'ara to'on. Toc taj caj a wa'araj to'on ‚Äïbaxuc caj ya'arob y åjc ånany åjirob t åm ån yuc ti' C'uj.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj bin purbir ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o
\p 
\v 21 Caj man turiri' semana caj bin purbir Jes√∫s quir u sesic u b åq'uer chan xib an ten bic nanij u betic u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj pach u c'aba' Jes√∫s an ten bic caj ara'b ten y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj ti' Mar√≠a. Ra' u q'uinin m å' toy y ån åc u parar uch.
\p 
\v 22 Caj ts'oc u nup'ur u q'uinin an ten bic caj u ts'ibtaj Mois√©s uch. Ra' u q'uinin caj bin Mar√≠a quir u yesic u b åj  åc åtan C'uj ich carem naj an ten bic nanij cu betic u winiquirob jud√≠o, yet binac Jos√©. Rajen binob purbir Jes√∫s ich u cajar Jerusal√©n quir u yesicob ti' C'uj ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o soc C'uj y ånin ti'.
\v 23 Caj binob quir u nup'ur u t' ån a tu ts'ibtaj Mois√©s uch. Caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúA mac a y ån bat'an rochic u parar xib y ån u bin u ts'ic chan och ti' Jaj Ts'urir soc raji' y ånin.‚Äù
\v 24 Caj binob Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a quir u ts'ic ti' C'uj a baxuc caj u toc araj Mois√©s uch, caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúY ån a ts'ic ca'tur susuy wa m åna', y ån a ts'ic ca'tur chan tuch. Raji' y ån u quinsic sacerdote quir u toquic ti' C'uj.‚Äù Baxuc caj ya'araj Mois√©s uch.
\v 25 Ra' u q'uinin caj bin Mar√≠a yejer Jos√© ti' c åja'an ich u cajar Jerusal√©n, turiri' xib Sime√≥n u c'aba'. Raji' jach tsoy yor, cu jach c'ujintic C'uj. Caj u qui' paj u q'uinin ber ca' bin tac a mac a cu bin tuchi'bir ten C'uj quir u qui'quinta' yor u winiquirob israel. Quire' u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj caj u pay ber Sime√≥n.
\v 26 Rajen esa'b ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj ti' Sime√≥n: ‚ÄúM å' a quimin hasta ca wiric ta wich Cristo a mac Jaj Ts'ur, a mac tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj.‚Äù
\v 27 Sime√≥n caj bin ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, quire' pay u ber ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. Ba'iri' c'uch Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a yejer u chan ochir Mar√≠a, Jes√∫s u c'aba'. An ten bic nanij u yesicob u winiquirob jud√≠o ti' C'uj ich carem naj, rajen binob.
\v 28 Sime√≥n caj u nup'aj Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a, caj chuc u chan ochir Mar√≠a ten Sime√≥n. Caj u t' ånaj C'uj Sime√≥n:
\q1 Bayo' C'uj, quij.
\v 29 Jaj Ts'urir, quij Sime√≥n, baje'rer c'ucha'an in wor in quimin.
\v 30 Qui' in wor quire' caj in wiraj a mac a caj a toc araj cu bin tar. Caj in wiraj in w åjtaquir an ten bic caj a wa'araj ti' ten a mac a cu beyaj tech.
\v 31 A je' chan ocha' a quin rochic raji' caj a tetaj quir u taquic mac tu cotor. Tu cotor cu bin yiric.
\v 32 A je' chan ocha', je' u sasiquintic ti' mac cax a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o soc yerob bic tabar cu bin tacbir. U winiquirob jud√≠o cu bin s åjta'bir ten tu cotor mac quire' ti' u tar ti'ob a mac cu bin u taquic ti'ob.
\p 
\v 33 Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a u n å' Jes√∫s caj jaq'uij yorob quire' yubarob ya'aric Sime√≥n ti' chan ochir.
\v 34 Sime√≥n caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïCa' u yamtej techex C'uj.
\p Caj ara'b ti' Mar√≠a ten Sime√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïCa bin a muc'yaj Mar√≠a irej wa rambirech yejer chan mascab quire' a ba' cu bin tar ti' a parar. Ya'ab u winiquirob israel cu bin sat årob quire' m å' tu quibob a parar tech. Chen ya'ab cu bin u cuxtar munt q'uin quire' caj u quibob ti'. Ya'ab mac cu bin u nunquicob u t' ån
\v 35 soc u joc'ar a ba' cu muc u tucricob tu yorob. Baxuc teta'b ten C'uj uch ‚Äïbaxuc caj ara'b ten Sime√≥n.
\p 
\v 36 Ti' y ån u jer xquic ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, ra' u c'aba' Ana, raji' u c'aba' u tet, Fanuel. Ana, raji' u jach  åj tseq'uir u t' ån C'uj. Raji' yo'nen Aser. Jach uch ch'ijic. Tan tu xur u baquer Ana caj raq'uinta'b ten u mam caj ts'oc u man siete yaxq'uin caj quim u mam. U beriri' m åna' u mam, quim u mam.
\v 37 Baje'rer y ån ochenta y cuatro yaxq'uin, m åna' u mam. Rajra' ti' y ån Ana ich carem naj. Rajra' caj u c'ujintaj C'uj caj u t' ånaj C'uj ti' u rac'ob. Su' su' caj u jamach p' åtaj u jan ån soc u qui' c'ujintic C'uj.
\v 38 Ana caj c'uchij ich carem naj ra' u q'uinin ti' y ån Sime√≥n tan u tsicbarob yejer Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a. Caj ts'oc yiric u chan ochir Mar√≠a caj u t' ånaj C'uj caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj quire' caj in wiraj chan ochir.
\p Ana caj tsicban åj yejer u rac'ob bic tabar u chan ochir Mar√≠a. Caj ya'araj ti' a mac tan u pajicob u tar Cristo ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Ana caj u tsicb åtaj ti'ob ti' Cristo. Baxuc caj ara'b ten Ana.
\s1 Caj w åc' ås sutn åj ich u cajar Nazaret
\p 
\v 39 Ra' ts'oc u nup'sicob a ba' ya'araj ich u t' ån Mois√©s. Caj w åc' ås sutn åjob Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a ich u cajar Nazaret quire' ra' u jach cajar. Ti' y ån tu ru'umin Galilea.
\v 40 Ti' y ånob ich u cajar Nazaret caj ch'ijij u parar. Caj u jach chichtar u muc'. U ne'er ya'aric tu cotor ba'. C'uj caj u qui' c ånantaj chan Jes√∫s xan.
\s1 Caj c'uchij chan Jes√∫s ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o
\p 
\v 41 An bic nanij u bin Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a cu yocar yaxq'uin cu bin ich u cajar Jerusal√©n, cu c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' jan ånob u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ra' u q'uinin cu c' å'oticob tu caj u potmastaj y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj uch.
\v 42 Rajen caj c'uchij ti' doce u yaxq'uinin ti' Jes√∫s yet binacob u n å' yejer Jos√© ich u cajar Jerusal√©n an ten bic nanij cu binob Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a quir u binob.
\v 43 Caj ts'oc u qui'qui' jan ånob caj sutn åjob Jos√© yejer Mar√≠a. Tiri' toc p'at Jes√∫s ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. M å' yerob u n å' wa tar bin Jes√∫s yejer u rac'ob p åybej. M å' yerob p'at tu junan ich u cajar Jerusal√©n.
\v 44 Cu tucricob tan u tar ich a pimo' a yet binacob, tu masajob turiri' u q'uinin ich bej. Caj binob c åxta'bir Jes√∫s ich u rac'ob bayiri' ich u b åjob.
\v 45 M å' yirob rajen w åc' ås ca' sutn åjob u c åxtej ich u cajar Jerusal√©n.
\p 
\v 46 Caj c'uchob ich Jerusal√©n caj u c åxtajob, tres u q'uinin tan u c åxta' Jes√∫s. Tres u q'uinin caj ir Jes√∫s. Ti' y ån ich carem naj caj irir curucbar yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Caj yubaj u tsicbarob. Caj u c'ataj Jes√∫s a ba' cu camsicob y åjcams åy åjirob.
\p 
\v 47 Jac'a'an yorob y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s quire' yubicob quet u nunquic Jes√∫s a ba' cu c'ata' ti' quire' yer u nunca'r Jes√∫s.
\v 48 Caj irir ten Jos√© ti' y ån Jes√∫s ich u y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj jaq'uij yorob u n å' yejer Jos√©. U n å' caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïIn pararech, biquinin caj a betaj to'on aro'? M å' wa ja toc er je' in wac'tiquech yejer a tet?
\p 
\v 49 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin caj tarechex a c åxtenex? A werex a teno' y ån in bin in betej a caj u ya'araj ten in Tet C'uj, rajen te' y ånena'.
\p 
\v 50 Robob m å' ju najticob ba' caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' u n å' yejer u tet.
\p 
\v 51 Quet caj w åc' ås sutn åjob ich u cajar Nazaret. Caj u quibaj u t ån u n å' Jes√∫s quet u quibic u t' ån Jos√©. Mar√≠a caj u caj tucraj ich yor a ba' caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'ob.
\v 52 A Jes√∫so' caj u jach ne qui' c ånaj quire' tan u jach ne ch'ijir quire' yajquinta'b ten C'uj. Bayiri' u rac'ob yajquinta'b Jes√∫s.
\c 3
\s1 A Juano' ra' cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac cu tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ3.1‚Äë12; Mr.‚ÄØ1.1‚Äë8; Jn.‚ÄØ1.19‚Äë28)
\p 
\v 1 Ra' u q'uinin ts'oc u m ån quince u yaxq'uinin Tiberio C√©sar tan u reyinticob u ru'umin Roma. Ti' y ån Poncio Pilato tan u ts'urinticob u ru'umin Judea. Bayiri' xan Herodes tan u ts'urinticob u ru'umin Galilea. Yits'in Herodes, Felipe, ra' u c'aba' tan u ts'urinticob u ru'umin Iturea yejer u ru'umin Traconite. Bayiri' xan Lisanias tan u ts'urinticob u ru'umin Abilinia.
\v 2 Bayiri' xan a ray u q'uinino' ti' y ån An√°s yejer Caif√°s tan u ts'urinticob carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Quire' u jach ts'urirob sacerdote. A ray u q'uinino' caj ts'a'b ti' Juan ten C'uj quir u tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj. Raji' u parar Zacar√≠as. Ti' c åja'an Juan ich t åcay ru'um caj tar u t' ån C'uj ti' ca' u tsec'tej.
\v 3 Rajen Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac bin u ts'ectej tu n åts'a'an u ya'arir Jord√°n. Caj u man ya'araj ti' a pim ca' u c'axejob tu yorob soc u p' åticob u c'asir quir u yacsic ja' tu jo'r soc u jaw årob u si'pirob.
\v 4 A ba' caj u tsec'taj Juan raji' quir u nup'ur u t' ån C'uj a caj u ts'ibtaj Isa√≠as uch.
\p Caj ya'araj Isa√≠as y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj bin Isa√≠as uch:
\q1 Quij cu'yic u t' ån, quij Isa√≠as. Quij cu'yic u t' ån mac, c'am cu tsec'tic ich t åcay ru'um. Aro' a cu tsec'tic quij cu'yic u ya'aric: Toc r åc ruc'sex a c'asirex, irej a mac cu tajquintic u ber soc u tar rey. Tu c'oc'ob cu tajquintic.
\v 5 Tu c'omc'om ca' u muquej soc u tajtar. Tu cotor u witsir a ca'anano' ca' u tajquintej, bayiri' u chan p'uc wits ca' u tajquintej. Tu roch u berir ca' u tajquintej xan.
\v 6 Abaywo' c'ucha'an yor yiric C'uj tan u p' åticob u man tu c'asir soc yer tu cotor mac bic tabar cu tocar ten C'uj.
\m Baxuc caj ya'araj Isa√≠as uch.
\p 
\v 7 Caj tarob a pimo' quir u yacsa'r ja' tu jo'rob ten Juan quire' caj u c'axob tu yorob. Caj ya'araj Juan ti' a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' jach c'asechex irechex can. M å' ja wirej, a cano' cu puts'ur yiric cu tar quinsbir. Rajen ca tar a taquiquex a b åj a werex sajaquechex a binex erarex. Arex ten mac caj u ya'araj techex quir a puts'urex ti' u ts'iquir C'uj?
\p Juan caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' caj a wac'tex a b åj quire' a werex y ån a si'pirex.
\v 8 Toc p' åtex a c'asirex tu caj a manex soc a manex tu tsoyir soc ch åca'an yiricob a rac'ob caj a jach c'axex a worex. M å' a chen bin a wa'ariquex ra' in nunquirob Abraham rajen cu bin taquiquenob soc m å' u ts'ab år a muc'yajex ten C'uj. Biquinin C'ujo' c'ucha'an yor u ric'sic a je' tunicha' quir u way år u parar a nunquirex Abraham.
\v 9 Chen a techexo' wa m å'ja betiquex a ba' cu qui'quintic yor C'uj cu p'eri'quintic techex ti' p åc'ar u che'er a m å' ju wich ånc år. Techex a werex, a mac a y ån u p åc'ar che' a m å' ju wich ånc år, cu r åc ch' åquic quir u puric ich c'ac'. Baxuquex xan wa techex m å' ca wesiquex caj a jach c'axex ta wor cu bin ts'ab år a muc'yajex munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 10 Caj c'ata'b ti' ten u winiquirob jud√≠o, a mac a caj u yubob u t' ån:
\p ‚ÄïBa' tsoyir y ån ic betic soc u taquico'onex C'uj?
\p 
\v 11 Caj u nunca Juan:
\p ‚ÄïA mac m åna' u noc' y ån a j åsiquex ti' wa y ån ca'tur techex. A mac y ån yo'och ca' u j åsej ti' a mac m åna' yo'och.
\p 
\v 12 Caj tarob ich Juan a mac a cu c' åmicob u taq'uin gobernador tar u purej acsabir ja' tu jo'rob caj c'ata'b ti' Juan:
\p ‚ÄïArej to'on ba' y ån ic betic soc u taquico'on C'uj ij c åjcams åy åjirech.
\p 
\v 13 Caj ya'araj Juan:
\p ‚ÄïA mun cu c'ata'r u bo'orir ti a rac'ob ten gobernador. M å' ja ne jach nacsiquex u bo'orir. Jach taj ca waquex ti'ob.
\p 
\v 14 Caj tarob jun yarob soldado ich Juan u c'atejob ti':
\p ‚ÄïBa' y ån ic betic soc u taquico'on C'uj, arej to'on.
\p Caj u nunca Juan:
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån ts' åriquex u pach mac quir u sijiquex a taq'uinex. M å' tsoy a p åq'uiquex u pach mac quir u ts'ic a taq'uinex. Cax mun cu bo'otiquechex gobernador qui'quintex a worex ti'.
\p 
\v 15 A pimo' a tan u pajicob ca' tac Cristo a tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj, u c'at seb u tar Cristo. Cu tucricob a pimo' a Juano', raji' wa Cristo a caj u ya'araj C'uj cu bin tuchi'bir. Raji' caj man u tsotsoc arob wa Juan Cristo ich tu cotor u rac'ob.
\v 16 Caj ya'araj Juan ti' u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer u winiquirob jud√≠o a saduceojo':
\p ‚ÄïA teno' taj quin wacsic ja' tu jo'r mac a caj u p' åtajob a c'aso' quire' caj u c'axajob tu yorob. Ca' bin tac Cristo, quire' tabar u tar, raji' Cristo cu bin u ts'ic techex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj soc u ruc'sic tu cotor a c'asirex. Ca' bin tac a Cristojo' jach no'j. A teno' ‚Äïquij Juan‚Äï, m å' no'jen. M å' ja wirej, a teno' m å' pataren in pitic u c'anir u pech' x ån åb cax u c'urewen.
\p 
\v 17 Caj ya'araj Juan:
\p ‚ÄïA ca' bin tac Cristojo' je' u j åsic techex, irechex ca ruc'siquex u sor u wich trigo. Chen a tsoyo' ra' cu p'at år. U wich trigo ca ric'siquex, chen u sorob ca r åc puriquex u sor a toquiquex. A baywo' ca' bin xuruc t' ån ca' bin u much'quintico'onex ic Tet C'uj, a c'aso' ra' cu bin u puric ich c'ac' tu m å' u tupur c'ac'. Chen a tsoyo' cu bin acsa'bir ich ca'anan.
\p 
\v 18 A baywo' caj u chich araj ti' u rac'ob. U jer jach ya'ab tan u chich ara' ti' ten Juan tan u tsec'tic u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj.
\v 19 A Juano' caj u q'ueyaj gobernador Herodes. M å' ja wirej, caj u ch'a'aj u mu' Herodes. U rac' yits'in Felipe caj u ch'aj, Herod√≠as u c'aba'. Y ån u jer ba' c'asir caj u betaj, rajen caj u q'ueyaj Juan.
\v 20 Jach manan c'as caj u ca' betaj Herodes quire' caj u chuca Juan caj u m åcaj.
\s1 Acsa'b ja' u jo'r Jes√∫s ten Juan
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ3.13‚Äë17; Mr.‚ÄØ1.9‚Äë11)
\p 
\v 21 M å' toy chucuc Juan caj tarob a pimo' quir yacsa'r ja' tu jo'rob ten Juan, bayiri' xan acsa'b ja' tu jo'r Jes√∫s. Caj ts'oc yacsic ja' tu jo'r Jes√∫s quire' caj u t' ånaj C'uj ca'anan. Caj bin u muyarir.
\v 22 Caj tar u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj oc yicn ån Jes√∫s. Caj yira yeman irej susuy caj emij. Caj yub u t' ån C'uj ich ca'anan. Caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA techo' a chen in pararech, in jach yaj. Atecho' ta qui'quintaj in wor ‚Äïbaxuc caj ara'b ten C'uj ich ca'anan.
\s1 U nunquirob Jes√∫s uch
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ1.1‚Äë17)
\p 
\v 23 Jes√∫s tabar u chucp åj år treinta u yaxq'uinin caj u y ånxchun u beyaj u camsic u t' ån C'uj. Raji' u parar Jos√©, baxuc u tucric u rac'ob. A Jos√©jo' ra' u c'aba' u tet El√≠.
\v 24 A El√≠jo' u c'aba' u tet Matat. A Matato' u c'aba' u tet Lev√≠. A Lev√≠jo' u c'aba' u tet Melqui. A Melquijo' u c'aba' u tet Jana. A Janajo' u c'aba' u tet Jos√©.
\v 25 A Jos√©jo' u c'aba' u tet Matat√≠as. A Matat√≠aso' u c'aba' u tet Am√≥s. A Am√≥so' u c'aba' u tet Nahum. A Nahumo' u c'aba' u tet Esli. A Eslijo' u c'aba' u tet Nagai.
\v 26 A Nagaijo' u c'aba' u tet Maat. A Maato' u c'aba' u tet Matat√≠as. A Matat√≠aso' u c'aba' u tet Semei. A Semeijo' u c'aba' u tet Jos√©. A Jos√©jo' u c'aba' u tet Jud√°.
\v 27 A Jud√°jo' u c'aba' u tet Joana. A Joanajo' u c'aba' u tet Resa. A Resajo' u c'aba' u tet Zorobabel. A Zorobabelo' u c'aba' u tet Salatiel. A Salatielo' u c'aba' u tet Neri.
\v 28 A Nerijo' u c'aba' u tet Melqui. A Melquijo' u c'aba' u tet Adi. A Adijo' u c'aba' u tet Cosam. A Cosamo' u c'aba' u tet Elmodam. A Elmodamoj u c'aba' u tet Er.
\v 29 A Ero' u c'aba' u tet Jos√∫e. A Josu√©jo' u c'aba' u tet Eliezer. A Eliezero' u c'aba' u tet Jorim. A Jorimo' u c'aba' u tet Matat.
\v 30 A Matato' u c'aba' u tet Lev√≠. A Lev√≠jo' u c'aba' u tet Sime√≥n. A Sime√≥no' u c'aba' u tet Jud√°. A Jud√°jo' u c'aba' u tet Jos√©. A Jos√©jo' u c'aba' u tet Jon√°n. A Jon√°no' u c'aba' u tet Eliaquim.
\v 31 A Eliaquimo' u c'aba' u tet Melea. Meleajo' u c'aba' u tet Main√°n. A Main√°no' u c'aba' u tet Matata. A Matatajo' u c'aba' u tet Nat√°n.
\v 32 A Nat√°no' u c'aba' u tet David. A Davido' u c'aba' u tet Isa√≠. A Isa√≠jo' u c'aba' u tet Obed. A Obedo' u c'aba' u tet Booz. A Boozo' u c'aba' u tet Salm√≥n. A Salm√≥no' u c'aba' u tet Naas√≥n.
\v 33 A Naas√≥no' u c'aba' u tet Aminadab. A Aminadabo' u c'aba' u tet Aram. A Aramo' u c'aba' u tet Esrom. A Esromo' u c'aba' u tet Fares. A Fareso' u c'aba' u tet Jud√°.
\v 34 A Jud√°jo' u c'aba' u tet Jacob. A Jacobo' u c'aba' u tet Isaac. A Isaaco' u c'aba' u tet Abraham. A Abrahamo' u c'aba' u tet Tar√©. A Tar√©jo' u c'aba' u tet Nacor.
\v 35 A Nacoro' u c'aba' u tet Serug. A Serugo' u c'aba' u tet Ragau. A Ragaujo' u c'aba' u tet Peleg. A Pelego' u c'aba' u Tet Heber. A Hebero' u c'aba' u tet Sala.
\v 36 A Salajo' u c'aba' u tet Cain√°n. A Cain√°no' u c'aba' u tet Arfaxad. A Arfaxado' u c'aba' u tet Sem. A Semo' u c'aba' u tet No√©. A No√©jo' u c'aba' u tet Lamec.
\v 37 A Lameco' u c'aba' u tet Matusal√©n. A Matusal√©n u c'aba' u tet Enoc. A Enoco' u c'aba' u tet Jared. A Jaredo' u c'aba' u tet Mahalaleel. A Mahalaleelo' u c'aba' u tet Cain√°n.
\v 38 A Cain√°no' u c'aba' u tet En√≥s. A En√≥s u c'aba' u tet Set. A Seto' u c'aba' u tet Ad√°n. A Ad√°no' beta'b ten C'uj.
\c 4
\s1 Caj tumta'b yor Jes√∫s ten quisin
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ4.1‚Äë11; Mr.‚ÄØ1.12‚Äë13)
\p 
\v 1 Caj joq'uij Jes√∫s ich u chi' ya'arir Jord√°n quir u bin ich Galilea, Jes√∫s jach ts'urinta'b ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. Caj pay u ber Jes√∫s ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quir u bin ich t åcay ru'um.
\v 2 Quir u tumta'r yor ten quisin quir yirir wa cu yacsic u si'pir. Ti' taro', ti' y ån ich t åcay ru'um cuarenta u q'uinin. Caj u jamach p' åtaj u jan ån u burur q'uin, u burur ac'bir. Caj ts'oc u jamach p' åtic u jan ån, Jes√∫s caj wich åjij.
\v 3 Caj tar quisin caj ya'araj quisin ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïWa jach taj u pararech C'uj waysej a je' tunicha' ca' wayac a woch waj, quir a jantic.
\p 
\v 4 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj:
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc tu ts'iba'an cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúM å' chen a woch cu cuxquintiquech. A xibo' cu cuxtar wa cu ya'aric C'uj.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' caj pay ten quisin caj bin purbir ich jo'r yajaw wits tu ca'anan. Caj tus r åc esa'b ti' ten quisin tu cotor u ru'umin tu cu reyinticob rey. Tabar caj ts'oc yesa'r ti' ten quisin.
\v 6 A quisino' caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïTu cotor a ba' ca wirique' a cu nequi'quintic u yor mac quire' caj u ts'aj ten C'uj, tu cotor wa jin c'at in ts'ic, c'ucha'an in wor in ts'ic. Bayiri' xan, tu cotor u muc' a caj a wiraje'.
\v 7 Wa ca xontar tub y ånen ca' a c'ujinten je' in r åc ts'ic tech tu cotor a ba' caj a wiraj sam, soc tech y ånin.
\p 
\v 8 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJoq'uen xen, Quisinech. Quire' u t' ån C'uj cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúC'ujintej a Jaj Ts'urir C'uj. Chen raji' ca beyaj ti'.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Caj pay Jes√∫s ten quisin ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Caj nac purbir Jes√∫s tu jach ca'anan u jo'r carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj ara'b ti' ten quisin:
\p ‚ÄïWa jach jaj u pararech C'uj, pur a b åj ca' rubuquech ich ru'um.
\v 10 Baxuc cu ya'aric tu ts'iba'an u t' ån C'uj:
\q1 Tu toc araj ti' y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj ca' u qui' c ånatech.
\v 11 Baxuc cu ya'aric tu ts'iba'an u t' ån C'uj, tu cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúJe' a ric'siquex yejer a c' åbex, cax m å' u ya' ch' åtic tunich soc m å' u yajtar u yoc ten tunich.‚Äù
\m Baxuc cu ya'aric u t' ån C'uj.
\p 
\v 12 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc tu ts'iba'an cu ya'aric xan: ‚ÄúM å' tsoy ic tumtic yor ic Jaj Ts'urir C'uj soc ij quirej wa taj a ba' caj u ya'araj.‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Caj ts'oc u y ån r åc tumta'r yor Jes√∫s ten quisin. Jamach p'at Jes√∫s ten quisin je' u ca'tar tumta'bir yor Jes√∫s u jer u q'uinin.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u beyaj ich ru'umin Galilea
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ4.12‚Äë17; Mr.‚ÄØ1.14‚Äë15)
\p 
\v 14 Jes√∫s caj sutn åj ich u ru'umin Galilea. Jach ts'urinta'b ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj Jes√∫s. Caj r åc man u jumintej ti' u rac'ob a ba' tsoyir caj u betaj Jes√∫s.
\v 15 Tu caj u camsaj Jes√∫s ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. U rac'ob caj ara'b ti' Jes√∫s ich u rac'ob caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJach tsoy Jes√∫s quire' cu tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj.
\s1 Jes√∫s ti' y ån ich u cajar Nazaret
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.53‚Äë58; Mr.‚ÄØ6.1‚Äë6)
\p 
\v 16 Caj urij Jes√∫s ich u cajar Nazaret tub ch'ijij Jes√∫s uch. An ten bic nanij u c'ujintic C'uj caj oquij ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Quire' ra' u q'uinin quir u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj ric' u ch'ictar u xaquej u t' ån C'uj Jes√∫s quir yubicob u rac'ob.
\v 17 Caj ts'a'b ti' u ju'unin a ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Isa√≠as uch. Caj ts'a'b ti' ten u ts'urir u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj u choraj u ju'unin Jes√∫s, m å' ja wirej, cats'a'an. Caj yiraj tu ts'iba'an ten Isa√≠as a cu ya'aric, caj u xacaj Jes√∫s:
\q1 
\v 18 A teno', quij Isa√≠as, tu ts'urinten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. Rajen caj u teten C'uj quir in bin in tsec'tic u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj ich a mac jach otsire'. Caj u tuchi'ten quir in wa'aric ti' a mac ts'urinta'b ten u si'pirob, caj u toc siptaj C'uj ti' u si'pirob. Caj aren in yamtic a mac cu manob tu c'asir soc u manob tu tsoyir, irej a mac ch'op u wich cu bin sasich åj år u wich. Caj taren in chichquintic yorob a mac tupsa'an yorob ten u yajirob.
\v 19 Caj taren in toc aric techex c'uchij tu q'uinin u tar ic Jaj Ts'urir quir u ta'quic tu cotor mac.
\p 
\v 20 Jes√∫s caj ts'oc u xaquic caj u ca' cats'aj u ju'unin caj u ts'aj ti' u c'urew u jach ts'urir u chan najir. Caj cura Jes√∫s. Tu cotor mac a ti' cura'anob tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj tan u qui' p åta'rob Jes√∫s quire' jac'a'an yorob.
\v 21 Caj u y ånxchun u tsicbar Jes√∫s, caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA caj in xacaj baje'rer toc nup'a'an a ba' ts'ibta'b.
\p 
\v 22 Tu cotor a mac ti' y ån tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïJach tsoy Jes√∫s.
\p Jac'a'an yorob quire' yubob jach tsoy u t' ån Jes√∫s. Caj u c'axajob u tucurob rajen caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïA je'ra' u chen parar Jos√©.
\p Caj u p'astob Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 23 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a mac a ti' y ån ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïIn wer techex ca' bin a wa'ariquenex: ‚ÄúWa ja c'at a yamtic u jer mac, a w åc' ås b åjiri' ca' a bat'an yamtej quire' yajech.‚Äù Ra' u c'at ya'aric: ‚ÄúBiquinin a teche', Jes√∫s, m å' a betaj carem beyaj ta cajar Nazaret tu chi'jech an ten bic caj a betaj carem beyaj ich u cajar Capernaum?‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJach taj quin waquex tech. M å' ju yacs år y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj a cu tar ich cajarire'.
\v 25 Taj quin bin in c'asej techex, soc a c' å'otiquex ba' u ber uch y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj, quire' caj u betaj carem beyaj ti' a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠ojo'. C'aj wa techex tu q'uinin y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj El√≠as uch. M å' ju tar ya'arir caj m ån tres yaxq'uin yejer u jer chumuc yaxq'uin. M å' ju tar ya'arir, caj u r åc wich åjob quire' m å' ju ch'ijir u p åc'ar.
\v 26 Chen a C'ujo' caj u tuchi'taj El√≠as tu ru'umin Sid√≥n tu y ån yatoch a xquic a quimen u mamo'. Sarepta u c'aba' u cajar. Caj bin jansbir El√≠as cax m å' u winiquir jud√≠o a xquico'. Biquinin m å' tu jansaj a ti' y ån ich u winiquirob jud√≠o a xquic a quimen u mam quire' y ån ya'ab? Quire' tuchi'ta'b El√≠as ich u jer cajar.
\v 27 C'ajtechex wa Eliseo caj jawsa'b iq'uer u ca' ti' Naam√°n a cu tar tu ru'umin Siria. Biquinin m å' tu jawsaj u winiquirob jud√≠o cax y ån ya'ab iq'uer u ca' ich u winiquirob jud√≠o? Quire' m å' ara'b ten C'uj u jawsej ich u winiquirob jud√≠o, rajen m å' ju jawsej.
\p 
\v 28 Caj yubob ya'aric Jes√∫s a ti' r åc much'a'anob tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj caj r åc p'ujob.
\v 29 Caj r åc ric'ob joc'sa'bir Jes√∫s caj bin purbir tu jo'r wits tu ch'ica'anin wits. B åyt åc yatochob tu c åja'an ich u j'or wits. U c'at u nech'inta'r Jes√∫s quir u quinsicob Jes√∫s.
\v 30 Chen Jes√∫s caj man chumuc tu r åc much'a'anob, chan ber caj man Jes√∫s chumuc caj bin.
\s1 Ti' y ån xib turiri' y ån u c'ac'as quisinin
\r (Mr.‚ÄØ1.21‚Äë28)
\p 
\v 31 Jes√∫s caj u p' åtaj u cajar Nazaret caj bin ich u cajar Capernaum tu ru'umin Galilea. Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o caj oc u camsej Jes√∫s tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\v 32 Caj jac'ob u yorob barej caj u yubob a pimo' u camsa'rob ten Jes√∫s, quire' raji' tsicban åjij an ten bic mac a y ån u muc'.
\p 
\v 33 Ti' y ån turiri' xib tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Raji' y ån u c'ac'as quisinin, a cu yawato'. Caj u y åwtaj Jes√∫s, caj ya'araj:
\p 
\v 34 ‚ÄïAy, ba' a c'at ti' a tenob, Jes√∫sech, a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret? Tara'anech quir a ch'esiquenob? In werob maquech, a techo', a mac a cu tar ich C'uj, a mac a caj u ric'saj u w åc' ås b åjiri' ti' C'uj.
\p 
\v 35 Jes√∫s caj u q'ueyaj c'ac'as quisin:
\p ‚ÄïNup' a chi', ca' joc'aquech, ca' a p' åtej a je' xiba'.
\p Caj pich'inta'b xib ten c'ac'as quisin caj rub ich ru'um  åc åtan u rac'ob. M å' yaj caj joc' u quisinin.
\v 36 Caj jac'ob yorob u rac'ob caj irir u joc'ar c'ac'as quisin. Caj tsicban åjob ich u rac'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBa' t' ånin a je' xiba' a m å' cax c'ac'as quisin cu quibir u t' ån ten c'ac'as quisin? Inan cu joc'arob.
\p 
\v 37 A ba' irir u betic Jes√∫s caj u r åc man u jumintej ich tu cotor u rac'ob ich u ru'umin Galilea.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u jawsaj yixquit Sim√≥n Pedro
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.14‚Äë15; Mr.‚ÄØ1.29‚Äë31)
\p 
\v 38 Caj joc' Jes√∫s tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj oc ich yatoch Sim√≥n. Yaj yixquit Sim√≥n, jach ar u jo'r. Caj c'ata'b ti' Jes√∫s quir u jawsic.
\v 39 Caj oc Jes√∫s tu chara'an yixquit Sim√≥n. Caj p'uxraj u t' ånej Jes√∫s, caj u jawsa u yajir u jo'r. Caj jawij, seb caj riq'uij quir u jansa'r Jes√∫s yejer a mac a ti' y ånob tu yatoch.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u jawsaj u yajir ya'ab mac
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.16‚Äë17; Mr.‚ÄØ1.32‚Äë34)
\p 
\v 40 A ray u q'uinino' tan u bin ic yum, caj tar purbir u yajir a mac c åja'an tu cajar Capernaum cax a ba' yajir y ån ti'ob Jes√∫s caj u r åc t åraj caj r åc jaw u yajir.
\v 41 Bayiri' xan, y ån mac aca'an ti' c'ac'as quisin. Caj joc'ob, caj q'ueya'b ten Jes√∫s caj aw åtn åjob caj joc'ob, caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïA techo', u pararech C'uj.
\p Jes√∫s caj u q'ueyaj ca' u nup'ob u chi' quire' a quisino' yer ti' u tar ich C'uj, rajij Cristo.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj ich u ru'umin tu c åja'anob u winiquirob jud√≠o
\r (Mr.‚ÄØ1.35‚Äë39)
\p 
\v 42 Caj sasij caj joc' Jes√∫s tar u wich u bin ich tacay ru'um. Chen a pimo' caj bin u c åxtejob hasta caj u yirajob Jes√∫s. Caj chich ara'b u p'at år Jes√∫s ich u cajar Capernaum.
\v 43 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïY ån in bin in tsec'tej u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj tu cu bin u reyintejob C'uj, ich u jer u cajarob. Rajen caj u tuchi'ten C'uj quir in tsec'tic u jach tsoyir u t' ån.
\p 
\v 44 Rajen ti' rajra' cu man Jes√∫s u tsec'tej tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o ich u ru'umin tu c åja'anob u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\c 5
\s1 Caj u puraj u chim ich c'ac'nab caj ara'b ten Jes√∫s caj oc u c åyir quire' jach carem u beyaj Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ4.18‚Äë22; Mr.‚ÄØ1.16‚Äë20)
\p 
\v 1 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u man u tsec'tej Jes√∫s ich u chi' c'ac'nab u c'aba' Geneseret. Caj c'uchob jach pim, caj u r åc n åctantajob u b åj ich Jes√∫s quire' u c'at yubicob u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj.
\v 2 Jes√∫s caj yiraj ti' y ån chem ich chi' c'ac'nab, b åyt åc u sa'amin u chi' c'ac'nab. Ca'tur caj yiraj chem. Chen u chem y ån. Ti' y ån u winiquirir u chem tan u p'o'icob u chim.
\v 3 Jes√∫s caj oc cutar ich chem, turiri', ra' u chemin Sim√≥n caj c'ata'b ti' ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJoc'sej u chemin n ån åchir.
\p Jes√∫s caj cur åj u camsej a pimo'.
\v 4 Caj ts'oc u camsic Jes√∫s a pimo' caj ara'b ti' Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïCh'aj a chem ca' xiquech ca' a purej a chim tub tam. Je' a chuquic ya'ab c åy yejer a wet beyajob.
\p 
\v 5 Caj u nunca Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, u bur u ac'bir caj chich beyan åjenob tan in puric in chimob. M å' tin c' ås chuc u c åyirob. Chen wa tech aric tenob, je' in w åc' ås bin in purejob in chimob.
\p 
\v 6 Caj ts'oc u puricob u chimin caj u jach chucajob u c åyir ya'ab. Caj u y ånxchun u jat år u chimin quire' jach manan chup u c åyir u chimin.
\v 7 A mac ti' y ånob ich chem yejer Sim√≥n caj u babach c' å'tajob u yet chucob c åyob, a ti' y ån juntur chem quir u yamta'r u jitic u chimin. Caj tarob yamtabir Sim√≥n. Caj u jitob caj u but'ajob ich chemob caj chup u c åyir ich chemob tabar u jurur u chemob.
\v 8 Caj yiraj Sim√≥n Pedro jach ya'ab caj u chucajob u c åyir caj xonraj  åc åtan ich Jes√∫s. Caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïChan xen Jaj Ts'urir p' åten quire' a teno' jach manen y ån in si'pir.
\p 
\v 9 Caj u ya'araj aro' quire' jach jaq'uij yor Sim√≥n. Quet caj jaq'uij yorob xan a yejer yet chuc c åyo' Sim√≥n. Quire' yirob jach chup u c åyir caj u but'ob ich chem caj u chucajob.
\v 10 Baxuc xan u c'aba' Jacobo yejer Juan yet chucob c åy Sim√≥n, a p'eri' u beyajob. Ra' u teto' Zebedeo, caj jac' yorob xan. Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïM å' u jac' år a wor an ten bic caj a chucaj c åy. Quire' ra' a beyaj, ca' bin a camsej in t' ån ich a rac'ob soc u quibicob in t' ån. Ra' a beyaj baje'rer ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 11 Caj u jitob u chem ich chi' c'ac'nab caj u r åc p' åtob u beyajob u chuc c åy caj r åc binob tu pach Jes√∫s quir u c ånicob u t' ån Jes√∫s.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a ju c ånm ån iq'uer u ca'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.1‚Äë4; Mr.‚ÄØ1.40‚Äë45)
\p 
\v 12 Caj c'uchi tu q'uinin ti' y ån Jes√∫s ich turiri' cajarob carem. Caj c'uchi turiri' xib yaj, u c ånm ån iq'uer u ca'. Caj xonraj ich Jes√∫s caj u chich c'ataj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïIn wer c'ucha'an a wor a jawsiquen Jaj Ts'urir wa ja c'at a jawsiquen ‚Äïquij, a iq'uer u ca' teno'.
\p 
\v 13 Jes√∫s caj u tich'aj u c' åb caj u t åraj caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïIn c'at in wiric a jaw år ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p Caj ya'araj aro' seb caj jawij iq'uer u ca' ti'.
\v 14 Jes√∫s caj u chich araj ti' a jawe':
\p ‚ÄïM å' a bin a wa'aric tu ca man bic jawech. Chen tar a bin ich u sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o quir a sijic ti' a ba' ya'araj Mois√©s uch. Soc yerob tu cotor mac jawsa'bech ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 15 Quire' a pimo' yubaj u juminta'r jach chich u muc' Jes√∫s, jach manan caj u r åc juminta'r ti' u rac'ob. Rajen r åc tarob pim quir u much'quinticob u b åj quir yubicob u tsec'ticob u t' ån C'uj Jes√∫s, quir u jaws år u yajirir xan.
\v 16 Jes√∫s caj u jamach p' åtaj a pimo' quir u bin u t' ånej C'uj tu junan ich t åcay ru'um.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a m å' u ch'ictare'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.1‚Äë8; Mr.‚ÄØ2.1‚Äë12)
\p 
\v 17 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin, tan u camsic Jes√∫s. Chen jun yarob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s curucbarob yubejob. A pimob ti' u tarob ich u ru'umin Galilea. Ti' u tarob u jerob ich u ru'umin Judea. Ti' u tarob u jerob ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Jach ts'urinta'b Jes√∫s ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj quir u jawsic u yajirir mac.
\v 18 Jun yarob xib caj tarob purbir a m å' u ch'ictare'. Caj u c'ochob yejer u ch'ac. U c'at yacsa'r ich yatocho' tu y ån Jes√∫s ca' u chaquintob ich Jes√∫s.
\v 19 Chen m å' tu cu yacsicob quire' ti' y ånob jach pim. Rajen caj nacob ich u pach yatoch quir u r åcob u pach yatoch quir u yensa'r yejer u ch'ac, a m å' u ch'ictaro' ich Jes√∫s. Caj u patajob u jo'r yatoch quire' taj u jo'r yatoch.
\v 20 Caj u yiraj Jes√∫s bic tabar cu yacsicob tu yor ti' Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a m å' u ch'ictare':
\p ‚ÄïJe' in toc jawsic a si'pire' baje'rer.
\p 
\v 21 U winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer u y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj u y ånxchun u tucricob tu yor: ‚ÄúMac winic a je'ra' cu tucric c'ucha'an yor u jawsic u si'pir mac? Tan u pach'ic C'uj Jes√∫s, chen a C'ujo' c'ucha'an yor u jawsic u si'pir mac.‚Äù
\p 
\v 22 Jes√∫s yer ba' cu tucricob u winiquirob jud√≠o rajen caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin tan a waquex tan in pach'ic C'uj?
\v 23 Wa quin wa'aric ti' a je' xiba': ‚ÄúJe' in toc jawsic a si'pire'‚Äù, a techexo' m å' a werex wa y ån ten u muc' C'uj, chen wa quin wa'aric ti': ‚ÄúRiq'uen ca' xiquech‚Äù, ca bin a werex y ån ten u muc' C'uj.
\v 24 Baje'rer je' in toc esic techex in muq'ue' quir in jawsic u si'pir a je' xiba', quire' quin bin in jawsic u yajir a mac m å' u ch'ictare' soc a werex jach y ån in muc' quir in jawsic u si'pir mac, quire' a teno' baxuquenechexo'.
\p Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj a mac a m å' u riq'uire':
\p ‚ÄïRiq'uen ca' xiquech ta woc, toc ch'aj a ch'ac, xen ich a watoch.
\p 
\v 25 Seb caj riq'uij a m å' u ch'ictare'  åc åtan u rac'ob caj yirajob u ch'ic u ch'ac yejer u tas caj bin ich yatoch caj u ya'araj ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj, ta jawsajen.
\p 
\v 26 Caj jaq'uij yorob a ti' much'a'anob, caj u ch'aj sajaquirob caj u ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj quire' m å' biq'uin ij quiram åni' u jawsic mac hasta baje'rer caj ij quiraj.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u p åyaj Lev√≠ ca' tac u c ånej u t' ån
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.9‚Äë13; Mr.‚ÄØ2.13‚Äë17)
\p 
\v 27 Caj joc' Jes√∫s tub u jawsaj a m å' u ch'ictar ca'ch. Caj u yiraj y åjc' åmin u taq'uin gobernador, raji' u c'aba' Lev√≠, curucbar tu cu c' åmic u taq'uin gobernador. Caj ara'b ti':
\p ‚ÄïCojen tin pach ca' a c ånej in camsiquech soc in cams åwiniquech.
\p 
\v 28 Lev√≠, caj riq'uij caj u r åc p' åtaj u beyaj caj say tu pach Jes√∫s quir u c ånic u t' ån Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 29 Lev√≠, caj u much'quintaj u rac'ob quir u qui' jan ånob quir u s åjticob Jes√∫s. Caj r åc tarob ich yatoch Lev√≠, ti' y ån u jerob y åjc' åminob, u taq'uin gobernador jach pim. Bayiri' ti' y ån u jerob u rac'ob xan. P'eri' curicob jan ånob.
\v 30 Caj yirob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer u y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s a fariseojo'. Caj choquij yorob, caj u y ånxchun ya'ara' ti' u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin p'eri' a jan ånex ca wuc'urex xan yejer a mac cu c' åmicob u taq'uin gobernador yejer a mac jach y ån u si'pirob?
\p 
\v 31 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc a yer ts'aco' m å' u ts' åquic a m å' yaje', cu chen ts'ac år a y ån u yajire'.
\v 32 Baxuc a teno' taren in p åyic a mac a y ån u si'pirob ca' u c'axej tu yorob soc u p' åticob a c'aso'. M å' taren in yamtic a mac cu ya'aric m åna' u si'pir ‚Äïbaxuc caj ya'araj Jes√∫s.
\s1 Caj c'ata'b ti' Jes√∫s ten u winiquirob jud√≠o: Biquinin m å' u jamach p' åticob u jan ån u cams åwinicob?
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.14‚Äë17; Mr.‚ÄØ2.18‚Äë22)
\p 
\v 33 A mac ti' y ån caj u c'atob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïArej to'on biquinin m å' u jamach p' åticob u jan ånob a cams åwiniquirob quire' rajra' tan u qui' jan ånob. Chen u cams åwinicob Juan cu jamach p' åticob u jan ån, quir u t' ånicob C'uj ‚Äïbaxuc u cams åwinicob a fariseojo'.
\p 
\v 34 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj:
\p ‚ÄïM å' ba' u ber ca' u jamach p' åticob u jan ån a yet mano' cu bin u ch'ic u rac' quire' qui' yorob.
\v 35 Barej ca' bin ruc'sac a cu bin u ch'ic u rac' ten a mac a cu p'actic ti'. Raxben tsoy u jamach p' åticob u jan ån u cams åwinicob quire' tan yac'ta'rob a mac ruc'sa'b.
\p 
\v 36 Jes√∫s caj u camsaj ti'ob tan ya'aric:
\p ‚ÄïM å' tsoy ic xac'tic a ba' caj u camsajo'on ic nunquirex quire' jach uchben yejer a ba' ric'ben ca wu'yiquex. An ten bic mac m å' ju j åtic ric'ben quir u p åq'uic u rabir u noc'. Quire' a ric'beno' cu mosar. Chen wa cu p åq'uic u rabir yejer a ric'beno', chen a rabo', raji' cu bin jat år. Sat a ric'beno' a caj u j åtaj quir u p åq'uic ich u rabir. M å' ju bin quet tarob.
\v 37 Baxuc xan, m åna' mac cu t'ajic u c'ab uva ric'ben ich u rabir yot'er y år åc' chivo, quire' je' u paj u c'ab uva ich u rabir u yot'er chivo, je' u bujure', cu bin u sat år u c'ab uva yejer yot'er xan.
\v 38 Rajen y ån u t'ajic u c'ab uva a ric'beno' ich u yot'er chivo a ric'beno'.
\v 39 M å' ja wirej, a mac toc naj yuq'uic u c'ab uva a p åje', qui' yubic. M å' ju yuq'uic ric'ben u c'ab uva quire' toc na'sa'b yuq'uic p åj u c'ab uva. Rajen, a techexo' m å' a c'at a p' åtiquex a ba' tu na'satechex a nunquirex. Baxuc m å' ja c' åmiquex a ric'beno' quin camsiquechex.
\c 6
\s1 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s cu jo'sticob u wich trigo u q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.1‚Äë8; Mr.‚ÄØ2.23‚Äë28)
\p 
\v 1 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o, ray u q'uinin caj bin Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob caj u ch' åctajob u corir trigo. U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj u jo'stajob u wich trigo caj u j åx åc' å'tajob ca' ruc'uc u sor ca' u jantejob.
\v 2 Caj irir tenob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo', jun yarob a fariseojo'. Caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin a cams åwinicob tech tan u jo'sticob u wich trigo u jantejob. Tu ts'iba'an u t' ån Mois√©s cu ya'aric m å' tsoy u beyaj u q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\p 
\v 3 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj:
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa ja xacm ånex ba' caj u jantaj David uch, caj wich åj quet yejer u nupob caj wich åjob uch.
\v 4 Caj oc tu t'ina'an u noq'uir naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o uch. Caj u jantaj pan a ti' y ånob ich yoc'or pojche' ti'  åc åtan C'uj. Caj u c'asquintaj u t' ån C'uj David, quire' raji' David yejer u nupob caj u jantajob. Quire' C'uj, caj ya'araj, chen a sacerdotejo' cu janticob.
\v 5 M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, a teno' baxuquenechex, quin ts'urintic tu cotor ba', inan a ba' cu yiric mac tu q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\s1 A xibo' a m å' u jitir u c' åbe'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.9‚Äë14; Mr.‚ÄØ3.1‚Äë6)
\p 
\v 6 Caj c'uchij u jer u q'uinin tu q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Jes√∫s caj oc tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj u y ånxchun u camsicob Jes√∫s. Ti' y ån xib a m å' u jitir u c' åb ich u noje'.
\v 7 Ti' y ån y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s yejer u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo'. Tan u qui' p åcticob Jes√∫s quir yiricob wa m åna' u jawsic u yajir ray u q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o, quire' u c'at u taquicob u jo'r Jes√∫s.
\v 8 Jes√∫s yer ba' cu tucricob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Caj ara'b ti' xib, a m å' u jitir u c' åb:
\p ‚ÄïRiq'uen ta ch'ictar ca' taquech chumuc tu y åno'onex soc ch åca'an yiriquech tu cotor mac.
\p Caj ric' tu ch'ictar.
\v 9 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïY ån ba' quir in c'atic techex. Tu q'uinin quic jesic ic b åj. C'ucha'an yor mac u betic a ba' jach tsoy, wa c'ucha'an yor mac u betic a ba' c'as? C'ucha'an yor mac u yamtic mac u jer wa c'ucha'an yor u quinsic mac?
\p 
\v 10 Jes√∫s caj u r åc p åctaj yirej jujuntur, Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' xib:
\p ‚ÄïTich' a c' åb ca'anan.
\p A xibo' caj u tich'aj u c' åb, seb caj toc qui' jawij.
\v 11 Chen raji'ob, caj yirob aro' caj jach p'ujob caj u p'erinquintajob u tucurob ba' cu bin u beticob ti' Jes√∫s.
\s1 Teta'b ten Jes√∫s a mac a cu bin u tsec'ticob u t' ån
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ10.1‚Äë4; Mr.‚ÄØ3.13‚Äë19)
\p 
\v 12 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin Jes√∫s caj bin u t' ånej C'uj ich jo'r wits. U burur ac'bir caj u t' ånaj C'uj Jes√∫s.
\v 13 Caj sasij caj u much'quintajob u cams åwinicob quir u tetic doce, raji' caj u p åcha u cams åwinicob: ‚ÄúA mac a quin tuchi'ticob quir u tsec'ticob in t' ån.‚Äù
\v 14 Jera' u c'aba' a mac a cu bin tuchi'bir ten Jes√∫s quir u tsec'ta'r u t' ån. Jeroj Sim√≥n caj pach u jer u c'aba' Pedro. U jer caj u tetaj Andr√©s, raji' u b åjob Sim√≥n. U jer caj u tetaj Jacobo. U jer caj u tetaj Juan. U jer caj u tetaj Felipe. U jer caj u tetaj Bartolom√©.
\v 15 U jer caj u tetaj Mateo. U jer caj u tetaj Tom√°s. U jer caj u tetaj Jacobo, ra' u tet Alfeo. U jer caj u tetaj Sim√≥n, raji' tan u qui' c'ujintic C'uj, a tan u say år u pach cananista.
\v 16 U jer caj u tetaj Judas, ra' u tet Jacobo. U jer caj u tetaj Judas Iscariote, raji' cu bin c'ubic Jes√∫s.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic a pim winiquirob
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ4.23‚Äë25)
\p 
\v 17 Caj ts'oc u tetic a docejo' caj w åc' ås emij ti' u jo'r wits. Jes√∫s caj ch'icr åj tu tajir ru'um. Ti' y ån jach pim u cams åwinicob. Ti' y ån u jerob pim a cu tar ich u ru'umin Judea, bayiri' ti' u tar ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Ti' u tarob ich u cajar Tiro, ra' u chi' c'ac'nab. Ti' u tarob ich u cajar Sid√≥n ra' u chi' c'ac'nab xan. R åc tarob yubicob u t' ån Jes√∫s quire' u c'at u jawsa'r u yajirob xan.
\v 18 A mac aca'an c'ac'as quisin jawsa'bob xan ten Jes√∫s.
\v 19 Tu cotor u c'at u tar år Jes√∫s quire' ca' bin tar åc cu jawar u yajirob quire' cu tar u muc' ti' Jes√∫s quir u jawar u yajirob.
\s1 A ba' cu jach qui'quintic yor mac
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ5.1‚Äë12)
\p 
\v 20 Caj yiraj Jes√∫s u cams åwinicob caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïQui'quint a worex quire' jach otsirch åjechex baje'rer quire' a C'ujo' cu bin u qui' acsiquechex ich ca'anan tu cu reyinticob Cuj.
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄôQui'quintej a worex quire' wich åjechex baje'rer, je' a najch åj årex ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin. A mac tan u yac'ticob u b åj baje'rer qui'quintej yorob quire' ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u qui'tar yorob, je' u che'ejobe', quire' C'uj cu bin u qui'quintic yorob.
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄôQui'quintej a worex wa ber cu p'actiquechex mac wa tan u joc'siquechex tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj. Wa tan u p'astiquechex, wa tan u ya'aricob c'asechex quire' ta wacsajex ta wor ti' ten, a teno' a baxuquenechexo'.
\v 23 Qui'quintej a worex cax wa ber cu p'actiquechex, jach manan y ån a qui'quintiquex a worex wa tan u p'astiquechex quire' tan a manex tu tsoyir. Rajen a C'ujo' cu bin u qui' acsiquechex ca'anan. M å' ja wirej, quetechex yejer y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj uch. Bayiri' caj p'acta'b ten u rac'ob uch.
\p 
\v 24 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a mac a m å' tan u manob tu tsoyir a mac ney ån u taq'uin baje'rer:
\p ‚ÄïYaj cu bin yubicob quire' toy qui'ij yorob tera' ich yoc'ocab.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄôM å' ja wirej, a mac jach bu'ut baje'rer jach yaj cu bin yubic u wich åj år. A baje'rer cu tus che'eticob chen a ray u q'uinino' cu bin u jach ac'ticob u b åj.
\p 
\v 26 ‚ÄôQui' irej ber cu ya'aricob: ‚ÄúJach tsoyech‚Äù, quire' baxuc caj ya'arob ti' u tus  åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj uch. Je' u yac'ticob u b åj xan.
\s1 Ca' a yajquintiquex a mac cu p'actiquechex
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ5.38‚Äë48; 7.12)
\p 
\v 27 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïU'yex ba' quin camsiquechex. Ca' a yajquintex a mac cu p'actiquechex. Yamtex a mac cu p'actiquechex.
\v 28 T' ånex C'uj ti' a mac cu t åm åchi'tiquechex soc u qui'tar yorob. Chich t' ånex C'uj ti' a mac cu tupsic a worex soc u yamta' ten C'uj.
\v 29 M å' a c åniquex a mac a cu c'asquintiquechex. Wa cu tac' j åts'ticob a p'uc, arex ti' ca' u tac' j åts'tej jumbuj a p'uc xan. Cax wa mac cu ta'quic a jo'rex quir u ch'ic a noq'uex, soc m å' a c åniquex aro', arej ti' ca' u toc ch'aj u ca'yarir a noq'uex.
\v 30 Cax wa mac cu tar u chich c'atej techex. Cax wa sijibar ti', cax wa m åj ånbar ti', ts'ajex ti'. Wa mac cu tar u ch'ic a ba'tac, m å' a y ån c'atiquex ti', ca' u sutextech.
\v 31 Yamtex a rac'ob an ten bic a c'atex u yamtiquexob xan.
\p 
\v 32 ‚ÄôA mac a cu chen pacran yajquinticob u b åj quire' u yajob u b åj, chen u b åjiri' cu tucric, m å' ti' C'uj cu tucric. Quire' baxuc a mac y ån u si'pir cu yajquinticob u b åj, quire' u yajob u b åj.
\v 33 A mac a cu chen yamtic u rac'ob quire' baxuc caj yamta'b uch xan. U b åjiri' tan u tucric, m å' ti' C'uj, quire' cu tucric baxuc u yamticob u b åj a mac y ån u si'pir xan.
\v 34 A mac a cu m åj åntic u taq'uin ti' u rac'ob cu ts'ic ti'ob quire' yer je' u sutur ti' u jer, bayiri' xan u b åjiri' tan u tucric. M å' ti' C'uj quire' bayiri' a mac y ån u si'pir, quet u m åj ånticob u taq'uin yer je' u sutur ti' xan.
\p 
\v 35 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïA teno' tan in camsic techex. Yajquintex a mac cu p'actiquechex. Yamtex a mac cu p'actiquechex. Ts'ajex ti' ba', a ba' u c'atic techex, cax m å' a pajic u sutic techex. Baxuc ca' bin c'uchuquechex ich ca'anan. A C'uj cu bin u qui' bo'otic techex quire' ta c ånajex C'uj, rajen u pararechex C'uj. M å' ja wirej, a C'ujo' xan cu yamtic a mac jach c'as cax m å' cu ya'aricob ti' C'uj: ‚ÄúBayo' C'uj.‚Äù
\v 36 C ånex a Tet C'uj, m å' ja wirej, a C'ujo' cu yajquintic mac. Baxuc techex ca' a yajquintex a rac'obex.
\s1 M å' a y ån ta'quiquex u jo'r a rac'obex
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ7.1‚Äë5)
\p 
\v 37 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob ich u jo'r p'uc wits:
\p ‚ÄïM å' a ta'quiquex u jo'r a rac'ob soc bayiri' m å' u ta'quic a jo'rex C'uj. An ten bic caj a chich ta'quex u jo'r a rac'ob. Bayiri' a C'ujo' u bin u chich ta'quic a jo'rex xan. A mac tu c'asquintajechex, jawsex u si'pir soc baxuc a rac'obex cu bin u jawsic a si'pirex. Baxuc a C'ujo' cu bin u jawsic a si'pirex xan.
\v 38 Ts'ajex ti' a rac'obex a ba' u c'at, quire' baxuc C'uj cu bin u ts'ic techex xan. An ten mun u p'is caj a ts'aj ti' a rac'obex baxuc u p'is techex cu bin u ts'ajex C'uj. Jach manan ya'abir cu bin u ts'ic techex C'uj, m å' ju bin u c'uchur a worex ca' bin u r åc ts'ajtechex.
\p 
\v 39 Jes√∫s caj u w åc' ås araj yej u jer u t' ån quir u camsic:
\p ‚ÄïIrej a mac ch'op u wich, m å' u p åyic u bej u jer ch'op u wich. Quire' wa y ån u jor ru'um ti' cu bin u p'itc' åjob quire' m å' yirob u bej. Quire' baxuc techex a mac a m å' yer C'uj, m å' tsoy quir u camsic u t' ån C'uj. Quire' tan u p åyicob a bej quir a bin ich u c'aq'uir.
\v 40 A mac cu camsiquechex baxuc ca bin a c ånex, irechex a mac caj u camsajechex ca' bin ts'ocac u camsiquechex.
\p 
\v 41 ‚ÄôWa tech, caj a p'astaj a rac'ob quire' m å' tan u man tu tsoyir, chen a b åjiri' xan, m å' tan a man tu tsoyir, chen ta man ta c'asir. Irech a mac a cu p'astic u rac'ob quire' bina'an robir chichin tu wich. Chen a b åjiri' m å' a wiric wa bina'an robir ta wich cax carem.
\v 42 Wa ca tsicbar ti' mac quire' caj man tu c'asir, chen a b åjiri' jach manan y ån a c'asir tech. Irech wa mac a cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúArej in joc'sej a chichin bina'an robir ta wich quire' in b åjobech.‚Äù Chen u b åjiri' jach ya'ab bina'an robir tu wich. M å' a y ån c åniquex u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer u y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s quire' irob ch'op u wich. M å' ja wirej, y åjtusarirech. Chen a b åjiri' m å' a y ån joc'sic robir a wich. A techo' y åjtusarirech. Y ån a toc p' åtic a man tu c'asir soc c'ucha'an a wor a wiric ca' u p' åt u man tu c'asir a rac'ob.
\s1 Ca c' å'otic u che'er wa ca c' å'otic u wich
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ7.17‚Äë20; 12.34‚Äë35)
\p 
\v 43 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s tu cu camsic a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïWa tsoy u che'er bayiri' tsoy u wich. Wa c'as u che'er, bayiri' c'as u wich xan. Rajen wa c'as u che'er m å' c'ucha'an yor u ts'ic u wich a tsoyo'. Bayiri' xan wa tsoy u che'er m å' c'ucha'an, yor u ts'ic u wich a c'aso'.
\v 44 Wa ca wiric u wich ca c' å'otic u che'er xan. An ten bic m å' a t'aquic u wich  år åxa' ich ab år, bayiri' xan, an ten bic m å' a t'aquic u wich pujam ich poch'ir.
\v 45 An ten bic a mac tsoy u tucur, tsoy cu bin joc'ar u t' ån tu chi'. A mac c'as u tucur c'as, cu bin joc'ar u t' ån tu chi'. M å' ja wirej, a ba' y ån tu tucur ra' cu bin joc'ar tu cu tsicbar.
\s1 Ca'tur u najob
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ7.24‚Äë27)
\p 
\v 46 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca chen t' åniquen, ‚ÄúJaj Ts'urir‚Äù, barej m å' ca quibic in t' ån?
\v 47 Tu cotor a mac cu yubic in camsic ca' u quibej a ba' tin wa'araj.
\v 48 Raji' irej a mac t'aj. Quire' ber caj u c' åxaj yatoch, tam caj u p åc'aj yoc yatoch soc m å' u riquir. Ca' bin tac u ch'icyum ic' ca' bin buruc, m å' u riquir quire' jach tam caj u p åc'aj yoc yatoch.
\v 49 Chen a mac cu yubic in camsic, chen m å' ju quibej a ba' caj in wa'araj ti', raji' irej a mac chich u jo'r. Quire' caj u c' åxaj yatoch turiri', chen m å' tam caj u p åc'aj yoc yatoch. Rajen caj riquij caj tar u ch'icyum ic' caj tar ya'arir, caj bu'urij. Quire' m å' tam caj u p åc'aj yoc yatochi'. Caj r åc sat yatoch, caj r åc cuch ten ic' yejer ja'.
\c 7
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic u c'urew y åjt' ånir cien u winiquirob soldado romano
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.5‚Äë13)
\p 
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj ts'oc u camsic a pimo' a je' t' åna', caj bin ich u cajar Capernaum.
\v 2 Ti' y ån ich u cajar Capernaum u capit√°n u soldado u winiquirob romano. Raji' y ån u c'urew, u yaj u c'urew, tabar u quimin u c'urew.
\v 3 Caj yubaj ya'ara' capit√°n, ti' y ån Jes√∫s. Caj tuchi'ta'b jun yarob u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o, a nuxibe', caj chich pa'ay Jes√∫s ca' tac jawsa'bir u c'urew capit√°n.
\v 4 Caj u juts'ob u b åj ich Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u chich p åyicob Jes√∫s, caj ya'arob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïCojen ca' a jawsej u c'urew capit√°n quire' jach tsoy a je' capit√°no'. Raji' tsoy ca' a yamtej ti'.
\v 5 Quire' a capit√°no' cu yajquintic u winiquirob jud√≠o. M å' ja wirej, u b åjiri' caj u bo'otaj y åjc' åxirob naj tu quij c'ujintic C'uj ‚Äïbaxuc caj ara'b y åjp åyirob Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 6 Jes√∫s caj bin yejerob. B åyt åc u c'uchurob Jes√∫s ich yatoch capit√°n caj tuchi'ta'b t' ånbir Jes√∫s u rac'ob capit√°n. Caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïTsire'ej, cax m å' a wocar tin watoch ti tar a xuro' ich tancab. A teno' m å' pataren quir in wacsiquech.
\v 7 Rajen m å' joq'uen in t' ånech quire' in wer m å' tsoyen. Chen arej ti' ca' jawac in c'urew.
\v 8 M å' ja wirej, quin chen quibic u t' ån in jach ts'urob. Bayiri' a teno' xan, quin ts'urintic soldado u winiquirob romano. Rajen wa quin wa'aric ti' mac ca' xic, cu bin. Quin wac ti' u jer, ca' tac, cu tar. Wa quin wac ti' in c'urew u betej, cu betic. Rajen in wer wa ca waric u jaw år in c'urew cu jaw år ‚Äïbaxuc caj ara'b ti' Jes√∫s ten capit√°n.
\p 
\v 9 Caj yuba Jes√∫s aro' caj jaq'uij yor caj yuba bic tabar caj u yacsaj tu yor capit√°n. Rajen Jes√∫s caj u sut u b åj tu pach soc u t' ånic a mac a cu tarob tu pach. Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA teno' quin wac techex, m å' biq'uin in wiram ån yacsic tu yor cax ich u winiquirob jud√≠o, an ten bic a je' xiba' caj u yacsaj tu yor ‚Äïbaxuc caj ara'b ten Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 10 Caj w åc' ås urob ich yatoch a tuchi'ta'bob ten capit√°n caj yirob jawij u c'urew capit√°n.
\s1 A Jes√∫se' caj u ric'saj u parar a quimen u mame'
\p 
\v 11 Caj ts'oc u jawsa'r u c'urew capit√°n caj bin Jes√∫s ich u chan cajar Na√≠n. Ra' u c'aba' Na√≠n. Yet binacob u cams åwinicob yejer a pimob.
\v 12 Tabar u c'uchur Jes√∫s ich u cajar Na√≠n, tu jo'rir u pa'te'ir tunich, tan u joc'sa'rob u baquer quir u mucur. Raji' u parar a xquico', a quimen u mamo'. Turiri' u parar. Yet taracob a pim u rac'ob.
\v 13 Jes√∫s caj yiraj a xquico', a quimen u mamo', caj yajquinta'b ten Jes√∫s. Caj ara'b ti':
\p ‚ÄïM å' a wac'tic a parar xib ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 14 Jes√∫s caj u juts' u b åj t årbir tu but'a'an u baquer tu c'ocha'an ten u rac'ob. Caj xurob y åjc'ochirob u baquer. Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a quimen a chichano':
\p ‚ÄïRiq'uen, quen.
\p 
\v 15 A quimen ca'che' caj riq'uij cutar, caj u y ånxchun u tsicbar yejer u rac'ob. Caj ts'a'b ti' u n å' ten Jes√∫s.
\v 16 Caj yirob aro' caj u jach ch'ajob sajaquirob, caj u y ånxchun ya'aricob ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj. Caj a tuchi'taj u jer y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj a mac jach carem. Caj tar C'uj quir u yamtic u winiquirob israel ‚Äïbaxuc caj ya'arob.
\p 
\v 17 Caj u jumintajob ich u rac'ob bic tabar caj u ric'saj Jes√∫s u chan parar xib a xquico', a quimen u mamo'. Caj u r åc jumintajob ich tu cotor u cajarob u ru'umin Judea. Baxuc tantanxer caj u r åc jumintajob.
\s1 A mac tuchi'ta'b ten Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ11.2‚Äë19)
\p 
\v 18 U cams åwinicob Juan caj u yubob u juminta' u carem beyajob Jes√∫s. Caj binob arbir ti' Juan.
\v 19 A Juano' caj u p åyaj ca'tur u cams åwinicob ca' u tuchi'tejob ich Jes√∫s quir u c'ata'r ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïWa jach taj raji' Cristo a cu bin tar ich C'uj? Wa y ån ic pajic u jer?
\p 
\v 20 Caj c'uchob u cams åwinicob Juan ich Jes√∫s. Caj ya'arob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTu tuchi'tenob Juan ra' cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac quir in c'atob tech. Wa jach Cristojech a cu tar ich C'uj wa ca' in pajob u jer? ‚Äïbaxuc caj ya'arob.
\p 
\v 21 Caj c'uchob ich Jes√∫s caj u jawsaj a mac y ån u yajirir cax a bar yajir y ånob ti'. A mac y ån u c'ac'as quisinin caj u joc'saj. A mac ch'op u wich caj u jawsa caj sasich åj u wich.
\v 22 Jes√∫s caj ts'oc yubic biquinin tarob u cams åwinicob Juan, caj u nuncaj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïXen arex ti' Juan bic tabar ta wirex in jawsic a ch'opo' caj sasich åj u wich, a mech yoc caj jawij caj ximbajn åj. Bayiri' caj jaw ti' a iq'uir u ca'o'. Bayiri' a macar u xiquin caj jawi caj sasich åj u xiquin. Bayiri' a mac quimen caj ric'. Bayiri' caj a wu'yex in tsec'tic ti' u t' ån C'uj a jach otsirob.
\v 23 Ca' bin xiquechex ich Juan: Arex ti' jach qui' yor a mac a yacsic tu yor wa tu tuchi'tajen C'uj ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 24 Caj binob u cams åwinic Juan. Caj w åc' ås bin Jes√∫s quir u tsicbar ti' a pimo'. Caj u tsicb åtaj bic tabar Juan. Caj u c'ataj ti'ob a pimo' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïMac binechex a wirex ich t åcay ru'um uch? M å' wa ta wirex Juan a seb cu quibic ba'? M å' binechex a wirex mac a seb cu quibic ba'.
\v 25 M å' binechex a wirex turiri' xib a ju buquim ån noc' irej wa ney ån u taq'uin a cu buquintic u noc'. M å' ja wirej, a mac cu nebuquintic u jach tsoyir u noc' ti' c åja'anob ich u palacio rey. Robob cu qui' jan ånob xan. M å' a bin a wirex irej wa Juan ich t åcay ru'um.
\v 26 Binechex a wirex y åjtseq'uir u t' ån. Rajen binechex soc a wirejex y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj. Caj binechex a wirex Juan m å' chen y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj, quire' raji' caj u payaj in ber. Raji' irej El√≠as.
\v 27 Raji' Juan a tsec'ta'b ich u t' ån C'uj tu ts'iba'an tu cu ya'aric:
\q1 Y ån in tuchi'tic, quij C'uj, a mac cu ya'aric in tar, raji' y åjtseq'uir in t' ån cu bin u p åyic in ber tu cu tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj.
\m Baxuc C'uj caj ya'araj ti' u y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj uch, caj u ts'ibtaj uch.
\v 28 Tu cotor a mac ti' y ån ich yoc'ocab m åna' mac jach carem chen jari' Juan jach carem. Raji' cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac. Chen a mac a cu cha'ic C'uj u ts'urintic, cax m å' no'j tera', ca' bin u c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u bin u qui' najtej u t' ån C'uj. Jach manan cu bin u najtej u t' ån C'uj. A Juano' c' ås ti' ti' cu najtic.
\p 
\v 29 Ch åc y ån y åjc'amirob u taq'uin gobernador yejer u jerob u rac'ob, a yacsa'b ja' tu jo'rob ten Juan, caj u c' å'otajob jach c'asob  åc åtan tu wich C'uj. Caj yubob u t' ån Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJach carem C'uj. Quire' acsa'b ja' tu jo'rob ten Juan.
\p 
\v 30 Chen u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s, raji'ob m å' acsa'b ja' tu jo'r ten Juan quire' caj u p'astob C'uj a ba' u c'at C'uj ti'ob.
\v 31 A Jaj Ts'ur caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBic tabar quin quetquintic quir in camsic a mac cuxa'an baje'rer? Bic tabar quin wa'aric ti'ob quire' chich u jo'rob?
\p 
\v 32 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBin in quetquintic techex irex a chichan cu yac'ticob cu jenjen t' ånticob u yet chichinin cu tus aricob quire' m åna' ba' cu qui'quinticob yorob: ‚ÄúCa' ic tus aric ic ch'ic ic rac'. Chen m å' a tus  år åc' ånc år Cojen ca'  år åc'n åco'on. Ca' ic tus arej ic muc u baquer mac. Cheno' m å' a tus  år åc' ånc år‚Äù, baxuc cu ya'aricob a chicano' tu cu m ånicob yoch u tet.
\v 33 M å' ja wirej, caj tar Juan ra' cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac, m å' nanij u nequi' jan ån, m å' ju yuq'uic u c'ab uva. Chen techex ca wa'ariquex ti' Juan y ån u c'ac'as quisinin.
\v 34 Caj taren a teno' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, a baxuquenechexo'. M å' wirej, a teno' ca wa'ariquex rajra' quin nejan ån bayiri' ca wa'ariquex quin ne uc'ur. Bayiri' ca waquex jach coch in n åc' ca waquex quin jach carch åj år. Ca waquex in wet man y åjc' åminob u taq'uin gobernador. Bayiri' ca waquex in wet man a ney ån u si'pirob.
\v 35 A mac caj u yacsaj tu yor ti' C'uj. Cu ts'ab år u t' ånin ten C'uj soc u jach er u camsa'r. Rajen ij quer taj yor C'uj.
\s1 Jes√∫s ti' y ån ich yatoch Sim√≥n, raji' turi' u winiquir jud√≠o a fariseojo'
\p 
\v 36 Turiri' u winiquir jud√≠o a fariseojo' caj pa'ay Jes√∫s quir u jan ån. Jes√∫s caj bin tu yatoch. Caj curaj jan ån ich u poche'ir yo'och.
\v 37 Caj u yubaj xquic ti' cu bin Jes√∫s ich yatoch u winiquir jud√≠o a fariseojo' quir u jan ån. A xquico' raji' y ån u si'pir. Caj tar purbir u cuchir ti' t'aja'an a qui' u boque'. U c'aba' u cuchir alabastro. Tunich u cuchir tu t'aja'an a qui' u boque'.
\v 38 Caj u juts'a u b åj a xquico' ich yoc Jes√∫s. Caj u y ånxchun u yac'tic u b åj a xquico' caj p'ob yoc Jes√∫s yejer u w åc' ås arir u wich tu cu yoc'ar. Caj u tisa yoc Jes√∫s yejer u w åc' ås tsotser u jo'r xquic. Tan u ts'u'ts'ar yoc Jes√∫s ten xquic. Caj u jic'taj ich yoc Jes√∫s a qui' u boque'.
\v 39 A winiquir jud√≠o a fariseojo' a mac caj u p åyaj Jes√∫s caj yiraj a ba' caj u betaj xquic. Tu yor caj u tucraj a fariseojo': ‚ÄúWa Jes√∫s u jach  åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj yer Jes√∫s y ån u si'pir a xquico'.‚Äù
\v 40 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u winiquir jud√≠o a fariseojo', u c'aba' Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïY ån ba' quin wac tech.
\p Caj u nunca Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïArej ten ba' ca bin a wa'arej in w åjcams åy åjirech.
\p 
\v 41 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïA ca'tur xibe' y ån u bo'or quire' caj u m åj åntajob taq'uin ti' a mac cu m åj åntic taq'uin. Turi' caj u p'axaj cincuenta denarios, ra' u c'aba' u s åc taq'uin. U rac'ob caj u p'axaj quinientos s åc taq'uin.
\v 42 A je' ca'tur xiba' m å' c'ucha'an yorob u bo'oticob u bo'orob. A tu m åj åntajob uch caj u ya'araj ti'ob: ‚ÄúTsire'ej, cax m å' a bo'otiquex.‚Äù
\p Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïArej ten mac jach manan cu bin yajquintej a ra' xibo'. A jach ya'ab u bo'or wa ja m å' neya'ab u bo'or cu bin u jach yajquintej?
\p 
\v 43 Caj u nuncaj Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïJaj ixt åcoj, a mac jach ya'ab u bo'or, raji' cu jach bin yajquinbir.
\p Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïTaj a ba' caj a wa'araj.
\p 
\v 44 Caj u sut u b åj quir u p åctic xquic Jes√∫s. Caj u ya'araj ti' Sim√≥n:
\p ‚ÄïCa wiric, a je' xquica' a ba' caj u betaj ten. Tech, caj a wacsajen ta watoch, m å' ta ts'ajten ja' quir in p'o'ic in woc. Chen a je' xquica' caj u p'oj in woc yejer u ya'arir u wich. Caj u tisaj yejer u tsotser u jo'r.
\v 45 A techo', m å' ta wuts'benteno', cax ra' nanij u betic u winiquirob jud√≠o a cu yacsic tu yatoch. Chen a je' xquica' rajra' cu yuts'bentic in woc. M å' ja wirej, cu qui' s åjtiquen.
\v 46 A techo', m å' ta jic'taj tsats tin jo'ri' an ten bic nanij u betic u winiquirob jud√≠o a cu yacsic tu yatoch. Chen a je' xquica' caj u jic'taj a qui' u boque' ich in woc.
\v 47 Rajen quin wa'aric tech cax ya'ab u si'pir caj in toc r åc jawsaj rajen ya'ab cu yajquintiquen. A mac a m å' neya'ab u si'pir cax jawsa'b u si'pir, m å' u qui' yajquinten.
\p 
\v 48 Caj ya'araj ti' xquic:
\p ‚ÄïA techo' r åc jawsa'b a si'pir.
\p 
\v 49 Ti' r åc cura'anob jan ånob caj y ånxchun ya'aricob ich u rac'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBa' winquirir a je'ra' c'ucha'an yor u jawsic u si'pir mac?
\p 
\v 50 Caj ya'araj ti' xquic Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïC'uj bin u tacajech quire' caj a wacsaj ta wor. Ca' xiquech ta watoch qui'quintej a wor ‚Äïbaxuc caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'.
\c 8
\s1 A je' xquica' a cu yamticob Jes√∫s uch
\p 
\v 1 Caj ts'oc u beyaj ti taro' Jes√∫s caj bin ich tu cotor u cajarob, cax ich u chan cajarob, cax ich u yajaw cajarob xan. Ti' caj u tsec'taj u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. U yet binacob u doce u cams åwinicob.
\v 2 Baxuc xquic yet manob uch a mac joc'sa'b u c'ac'as quisinin yejer a mac jawsa'b u yajirir. Baxuc ti' y ån Mar√≠a Magdalena, raji' joc'sa'b siete u quisinin.
\v 3 Baxuc Juana ra' u mam Chuza, ra' cu beyaj ich Herodes. Tan u c ånantic u ba'tac Herodes. Baxuc Susana, baxuc ti' r åc y ånob u jerob. Caj u yamtob Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob cax yejer u taq'uinob.
\s1 Cu camsic ti' y åjq'uich'in y åjir u yijir trigo ich cor
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.1‚Äë9; Mr.‚ÄØ4.1‚Äë9)
\p 
\v 4 Caj r åc joc'ob ich u cajarob quir yiricob Jes√∫s. Caj u r åc much'quintajob u b åj ich Jes√∫s quir u camsa' ten Jes√∫s. Caj u ya'araj tu cu camsa' bic tabar u t' ån C'uj:
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄïCaj binij mac quir u p åq'uic tu cor trigo, cu q'uich'intic u yijir. Caj u p åc'aj u cor trigo, jumbuj yijir caj rub ich tanbej. Caj tar mac caj u yajch' åctaj. Caj tar u ruq'uic ch'ich' xan.
\v 6 Jumbuj caj u q'uich'intaj yijir caj rub ich tunich. Caj ch'ijij, caj quimij quire' m å' ch'ur u ru'umin.
\v 7 Jumbuj caj u q'uich'intaj yijir caj rubij ich q'ui'ix, quet caj ch'ijij, caj bobasta'b rajen m å' ju ch'ijir.
\v 8 Jumbuj caj u q'uich'intaj yijir caj rub tub u nec'at u ru'umin caj ch'ijir caj u nets'aja u wich hasta tu ni'.
\p Caj ts'oc ya'aric Jes√∫s c'am caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïWa c'ucha'an a worex a wu'yiquex t' ån, u'yex a ba' caj in camsaquechex ti' u t' ån C'uj.
\s1 B å' wir Jes√∫s caj u camsaj u t' ån
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.10‚Äë17; Mr.‚ÄØ4.10‚Äë12)
\p 
\v 9 U cams åwinicob caj u c'atajob ba' caj u camsaj sam.
\v 10 Caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTsaja'antechex ten C'uj quir a najtiquex a ba' m å' yerob uch tu cu bin u reytinticob C'uj. Chen a mac m å' yerob C'uj a cu yubicob in camsicob tu quin p'eri'quintic in t' ån. Cu chen u'yicob, cax cu yubicob m å' ju najtejob. M å' ju bin u c' å'oticob soc u yacsicob tu yor soc u tocar ten C'uj.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' y åjq'uich'in y åjir yijir
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.18‚Äë23; Mr.‚ÄØ4.13‚Äë20)
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄôU'yex ba' u c'at ya'arej u t' ån a caj in camsajechex: Ra' u yijir caj u q'uich'intaj caj u q'uich'intaj irej u t' ån C'uj.
\v 12 A yijirob caj rub ich tanbej irob a mac a cu yubicob u t' ån C'uj caj tarij quisin quir u taquic u t' ån C'uj tu pixamob soc m å' u yacsicob tu yor soc m å' ju tocar ten C'uj.
\v 13 Caj rub yijir ich tunich irob a mac cu yubicob u t' ån C'uj. Qui' yor caj u c' åmajob u t' ån C'uj. Chen irob yijir a m åna' u motsob. Tabar u yacsicob tu yorob, ca' bin tumta'c yorob ten quisin cu p' åticob u t' ån C'uj.
\v 14 Caj rub yijir ich q'ui'ix irob a mac a cu yubicob u t' ån C'uj chen ti' toy cuxa'anob tera'. Cu tucricob ti' u b åjiri'ob, u c'atob u nejaricob u taq'uin yejer u ba'tac. Cu chen tucricob ti' a ba' cu bin u qui'quintic yorob. Raji' cu tupsic u t' ån C'uj, rajen m å' ju qui' quibob u t' ån C'uj.
\v 15 U yijir a rub ich tub u nec'at u ru'umin irob a mac a cu qui' yubicob u t' ån C'uj caj u nequi' quibob u t' ån C'uj. Caj u qui' acsob tu yorob. Caj u muc'tob ba' a cu tumticob yorob soc u qui'quinticob yor C'uj.
\s1 Quir u camsic ti' wa t' åba'an u quib
\r (Mr.‚ÄØ4.21‚Äë25)
\p 
\v 16 A ba' cu camsic ti'ob irej wa t' åba'an u quib, rajen Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA mac a cu t' åbic u quib cu ts'ocar u t' åbic m å' u b åric yejer ba'. M å' ju yacsic yaram u ch'ac. Y ån nacsic ca'anan soc u yerc'ac'tic tu cotor mac a cu yocar. Quire' ca' bin u yerc'ac'tej a quibo', ch åca'an ij quirej ic bej soc m å' jic sat år, baxuc ti' Jes√∫s cu camsico'on soc ic najtic ca' ij quer u t' ån C'uj.
\p 
\v 17 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTu cotor ba' a mucu taca'an tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. Baje'rer ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u joc'ar u tajire'. Baxuc tu cotor mac je' u c' å'otej ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u yubique'.
\p 
\v 18 ‚ÄôRajen qui' u'yex a ba' quin camsiquechex quire' wa ca quibiquex in t' ån je' in ca' camsiquechex ya'ab. Quire' wa m å' a quibiquex in t' ån a mun ya'abir ta c ånex cu bin u tubur techex cax ca tucriquex je' u tubur techex.
\s1 U n å' Jes√∫s yejer u yits'inob
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.46‚Äë50; Mr.‚ÄØ3.31‚Äë35)
\p 
\v 19 Caj tar u n å' Jes√∫s yejer yits'inob. Caj c'uchob ich Jes√∫s. M å' c'ucha'an yorob u c'uchurob ich Jes√∫s quire' ti' y ån a pimo', jach pech.
\v 20 Y ån mac caj u t' ånaj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTi' y ånob a n å' yejer a wits'inob tar y ånob tu xur a nepimo', u c'at yiriquechob.
\p 
\v 21 Caj ya'araj ti'ob Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïQuire' a mac a cu yacsic tu yor u t' ån C'uj a cu qui' quibicob u t' ån C'uj raji'ob in jach n å', ra' in wits'inob xan.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj yic'ar baxuc u yamin ca' ch'enac
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.23‚Äë27; Mr.‚ÄØ4.35‚Äë41)
\p 
\v 22 Turi' u q'uinin caj binij Jes√∫s. Caj oquij ich chem yejer u cams åwinicob. Caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïCuxex p åchij c'ac'nab.
\p Caj binob.
\v 23 Caj u ch' åctajob c'ac'nab Jes√∫s caj wenij ich chem. Caj u nup'ob c'am yic'ar rajen caj u burij u chem, orac u jurur u chem.
\v 24 Caj bin  åsbir Jes√∫s ten u cams åwinicob caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcamsay åjirechob, tan ic jurur.
\p Caj riq'uij Jes√∫s. Caj u t' ånaj yic'ar yejer u yamin caj ch'en u tar yic'ar yejer u yamin.
\v 25 Caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa ja qui' acsm ånex a wor ti' ten?
\p Quire' jach jaq'uij yorob caj u ch'ajob sajquirob. Caj ya'arajob ich u b åjob a ju cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïA mac a je'ra', cax ic', cax u yamin, cu yuba'r u t' ån?
\s1 Ti' y ån xib aca'an ti' quisin ich u ru'umin Gadara
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.28‚Äë34; Mr.‚ÄØ5.1‚Äë20)
\p 
\v 26 Caj c'uchob yejer chem ich u ru'umin Gadara. Ra'  åc åtan u ru'umin Galilea.
\v 27 Caj joq'uij Jes√∫s ich chem. Caj nats'ij turi' xib ich a ray cajaro', tar bin ich Jes√∫s. Manij ya'ab yaxq'uin aca'an ti' quisin. Rajen m å' u buquintic u noc', m å' ju c åjtar ich naj. Ti' cu c åjtar ich u quimirir tu y ån u japnin tunich. M å' ja wirej, a ucho' u rac'ob caj u chucajob u c' årejob yejer mascab. Caj u c' årob u yoc yejer u c' åb soc u c ånanticob, ya'ab u teni' caj u p'icaj u mascabirob u c' åb yejer u mascabirob u yoc caj puts'ij ich t åcay ru'um quire' aca'an ti' c'ac'as quisin.
\v 28 Rajen caj u yiraj Jes√∫s, c'am caj aw åtn åjij caj tar xontar ich Jes√∫s. Caj ya'araj u quisinin:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca pecsic in worob Jes√∫s u pararech C'uj, a C'ujo' a mac jach no'j? Quin chich c'aticob tech soc m å' a ts'ic in muc'yajob.
\p 
\v 29 Baxuc caj ya'arob u quisinin quire' sam arac ten Jes√∫s ca' jocac ti' a xibo'.
\v 30 Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïMac a c'aba'ex?
\p Caj u nuncajob:
\p ‚ÄïPimenob.
\p Baxuc caj u nuncajob ti' quire' jach pimob a quisino' a aca'an ti' a xibo'.
\v 31 A quisino' caj u chich c'atajob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïM å' a tuchi'tiquenob ich c'ac'.
\p 
\v 32 Caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïAre in binob ich cajir q'uec'an tu cu jan ånob ich n åc' wits.
\p Jes√∫s tu chaj u binob ich cajir q'uec'an.
\v 33 A quisino', caj joq'uij ich xib caj ocob ich cajir q'uec'an, caj u c' ånajob yacab caj pitc' åjob tu ch'ica'an, caj binob ich c'ac'nab, ti' r åc bint ja' r åc quimob.
\p 
\v 34 A mac a cu c ånanticob cajir q'uec'an caj yirob ba' u ber ti' u cajir q'uec'an caj u c' ånob yacab caj bin u jumbintajob ich u cajar cax ich u chan corob xan.
\v 35 U rac'ob caj binob yirejob ba' u ber. Caj c'uchob ich Jes√∫s caj yirob xib a mac aca'an ti' quisin ca'ch. Ti' cura'an tan yubic u t' ån Jes√∫s. Toc y ån u noc' caj jep yor rajen jaq'uij yor a mac tar yiricob.
\v 36 A mac caj u yirajob bic jawsa'b a xibo' ten Jes√∫s. Tu tsicb åtajob ich u rac'ob a tarob ich tu cotor u cajarob a ba' caj u betaj Jes√∫s, bic jawsa'b a xibo' a mac aca'an c'ac'as quisin ti' ca'ch.
\v 37 Tu cotor mac a ti' y ånob ich u ru'umin Gadara. Baxuc a mac a c åja'anob b åcris cajarob caj u chich c'atajob ti' Jes√∫s ca' xic tu pach quire' jaca'an yorob. Rajen Jes√∫s caj w åc' ås oc ich chem quir u bin.
\v 38 A mac joc' u c'ac'as quisinin ca'ch caj u chich c'ataj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïAr in tar ta pach.
\p Chen Jes√∫s caj yaraj ti':
\p ‚ÄïM å' ja tar ‚Äïquij‚Äï.
\v 39 Xen ta watoch, xen jumintej a ba' tu betech C'uj, a ba' tsoyir caj u betaj tech.
\p A xibo' caj bin u jumintej a ba' beta'b ten Jes√∫s ti'. Baxuc caj u jumintaj ich tu cotor u rac'ob.
\s1 U parar Jairo a chan xquico', yejer u jer xquic a tu t åraj u noc' Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.18‚Äë26; Mr.‚ÄØ5.21‚Äë43)
\p 
\v 40 Caj sutn åjij Jes√∫s ich p åchir c'ac'nab. A pimo' qui' yorob caj u yasajob Jes√∫s quire' tan u pajicob.
\v 41 Caj c'uchij turi' xib u c'aba' Jairo, u jach ts'urir u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj u pur u b åj ich yoc Jes√∫s caj u chich c'atej ca' xic tu yatoch.
\v 42 Quire' tu quimin u chan parar xquic quire' m åna' u jer u chan parar. Y ån doce u yaxq'uinin. Caj bin Jes√∫s yejer Jairo. A pimo' caj u r åc n åctantob u b åj ich Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 43 Ti' y ån ich a pimo' turi' xquic jach yaj quire' y ån doce u yaxq'uinin caj u c ånaj u yajir. M å' ju jaw år u p'o'ic u noc'. Caj u r åc xupaj u taq'uin tu cu bin tu cu ts'ac år. M åna' mac c'ucha'an yor u jawsic.
\v 44 A xquico' caj u n åts u b åj ich Jes√∫s caj c'uch ich u pach Jes√∫s caj u t åraj u xax u noc' Jes√∫s. Sep caj jawij u yajir. Caj tsits u q'uiq'uer.
\p 
\v 45 Caj u c'ataj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïMac caj u t åraj in noc'?
\p M åna' mac arej wa caj u t åraj u noc'. Caj ya'arob Pedro yejer u yetcams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirechob, a jach pimo' caj u n åctantob tech, caj u nech'intajechob. Biquinin ca c'atic mac caj u t åraj a noc'?
\p 
\v 46 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïY ån mac caj u t åraj in noc', tin wu'yaj bin in muc' caj u jawsa'b mac.
\p 
\v 47 A xquico' caj yubaj yer Jes√∫s caj tari, tu babac caj xonraj ich Jes√∫s caj u toc r åc araj  åc åtan tu cotor mac biquinin caj a t åraj u noc' Jes√∫s. Caj ya'araj biquinin seb caj jawij.
\v 48 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïIn chan ti'arech jawech quire' caj a wacsa ta wor ca' xiquech ta watoch, qui'quintej a wor.
\p 
\v 49 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s caj c'uchij turi' mac, tar u tar ich yatoch Jairo. Ra' u jach ts'urir u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujintic C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj ara'b ti' Jairo:
\p ‚ÄïQuimij a chan parar, xquic. M å' a pecsic yor y åjcams åy åjir, tsire'ej.
\p 
\v 50 Caj yuba Jes√∫s ba' ara'b ti' Jairo caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti':
\p ‚ÄïM å' a ch'ic sajaquir, chen acsej ta wor ten je' u jebar yore'.
\p 
\v 51 Caj c'uchij ich yatoch Jairo. Jes√∫s m å' ju chab år u yocar mac, chen Pedro yejer Juan yejer Jacobo, quet yejer u tet yejer u n å', a quimen, chan xquic.
\v 52 A mac ti' y åno' caj u yac'tajob a chan xquic baxuc caj oc'arn åjob. Chen Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïM å' a wac'tiquex quire' m å' quimen, chen wenen u ca'.
\p 
\v 53 Caj u p'astajob Jes√∫s quire' yirajob jach quimen.
\v 54 Caj u m åch u c' åb ten Jes√∫s caj u c'am ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïChan xquic riq'uen ch'icren.
\p 
\v 55 Caj u w åc' ås cuxr åj. Seb caj riq'uij. Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïTs'ajex yo'och.
\p 
\v 56 U tet yejer u n å' caj jaq'uij yorob. Chen Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån ariquex ti'ob mac a ba' u ber ti'.
\c 9
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u tuchi'taj u cams åwinicob quir u tsec'ticob u t' ån
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ10.5‚Äë15; Mr.‚ÄØ6.7‚Äë13)
\p 
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj u much'quintaj u cams åwinicob caj u j åsaj u muc' ti'ob quir u joc'sicob quisin, quir u jawsic u yajirir xan.
\v 2 Jes√∫s caj u tuchi'taj u cams åwinicob quir u tsec'ticob tu cu bin u reyintejob C'uj quir u jawsic u yajirir.
\v 3 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïM å' ja ch'iquex ba' tu ca binex. M å' ja ch'iquex a xonte'. M å' ja ch'iquex chim. M å' ja ch'iquex a woch. M å' ja ch'iquex taq'uin. Chen turirir' a noc' a ch'iquex.
\v 4 A mac a cu y ån acsiquechex ti' ca y ån p'at årexe' hasta a ca' binex.
\v 5 Cax a ba' cajar m å' u yacsiquechex ca' bin xiquechex, toc pustex u noy ru'um ich u cajar soc yerob c'as caj u betajob quire' m å' tu c' åmajob u t' ån C'uj.
\p 
\v 6 Caj ruc'ob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj binob ich tu cotor u cajarob caj u tsec'tajob u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj. Baxuc caj u jawsajob u yajir mac tu cu binob.
\s1 Quim Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ14.1‚Äë12; Mr.‚ÄØ6.14‚Äë29)
\p 
\v 7 Caj yubaj gobernador Herodes tu cotor ba' cu betic Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob quire' caj u cay tucric Herodes. M å' ja wirej, y ån mac caj u ya'arajo': ‚ÄúJuan w åc' ås ric' ich u quimrir. Rajen cu betic aro'.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Caj u yuba ya'ara' Herodes ten mac: ‚ÄúRaji' El√≠as urij, rajen tan u betic aro'.‚Äù Chen u jer mac caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúW åc' ås riq'uij turiri' y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj, rajen cu betic aro'.‚Äù
\v 9 Caj ya'araj Herodes:
\p ‚ÄïQuire' caj in tuchi'taj ch' åcbir u car Juan, rajen aro' m å' Juan. A mac a quin wu'yic ya'are' cu betic aro'? In c'at in wirej ‚Äïquij.
\p Caj u c åxtaj bic tabar cu bin yiric.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u jansaj cinco mil xib
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ14.13‚Äë21; Mr.‚ÄØ6.30‚Äë44; Jn.‚ÄØ6.1‚Äë14)
\p 
\v 10 Caj urob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s a tuchi'ta'b ca'ch caj u tsicb åtajob ba' caj u betajob tu tu tsec'tajob u t' ån. Caj payob ten Jes√∫s soc u binob tu junanob yejer Jes√∫s. Caj payob u ber ten Jes√∫s quir u binob ich u cajar Betsaida.
\v 11 Caj yubaj a pimo' tan u bin Jes√∫s caj binob tu pach Jes√∫s, caj u cha'a u tarob a pimo' caj tsec'ta'b ti'ob tu cu bin u reyintejob C'uj. Caj u jawsaj a mac y ån u yajire'.
\p 
\v 12 Tabar u bin q'uin, caj tarob a doce u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s. Caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïArej u bin a pimo' quir u c åxticob quir u wen ånob, quir u c åxticob yoch xan. Quire' a tera' m åna' mac.
\p 
\v 13 Caj ara'b ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïB å' wir cu binob, techex ts'ajex yo'ochob soc m å' u binob.
\p Caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïM åna' to'onex chen y ån cinco ij coch pan yejer ca'tur c åy. Arej ic bin ic m ånej yoch quir ic jansicob.
\p 
\v 14 Jaj ixt åco y ån cinco mil xib. Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïArej u r åc cutarob jun much' curicob cincuenta soc u r åc jujuntur cincuenta cu cutarob.
\p 
\v 15 Baxuc caj u r åc betajob u cams åwinicob caj r åc curajob a pimo'.
\v 16 Jes√∫s caj u chucaj a cinco pan yejer dos c åy caj u nacsaj u wich ca'anan. Caj u ya'araj ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj.
\p Caj ts'oc u t' ånic caj u xat'aj pan caj u ts'aj ti' u cams åwinicob caj u j åsejob ti' a pimo'. Baxuc yejer c åy.
\v 17 R åc janob qui' nach åjob. Caj ts'oc u jan ånob caj u marob u xet'er yoch pan yejer c åy. Caj chupij doce xac u xet'er yoch pan yejer c åy.
\s1 Pedro caj u ya'araj ti' Jes√∫s: Cristojech, caj u tuchi'tech C'uj
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ16.13‚Äë19; Mr.‚ÄØ8.27‚Äë29)
\p 
\v 18 Quire' ti' y ån tu junan tu cu t' ånic C'uj Jes√∫s, quire' caj u p' åtaj a pimo'. Chen ti' y ån yejer u cams åwinicob. Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïBic u yaquenob a pimo'?
\p 
\v 19 Caj u nuncajob caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJuanech, bin, a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac. U jerob cu yaquech El√≠asech, bin, chen u jerob u ca' aric y åjtseq'uirech u t' ån C'uj uch, bin, ca' riq'uech, bin.
\p 
\v 20 Caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA techexe' bic tabar a waquenex?
\p Pedro, caj u nuncaj, caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïCristojech a caj u tuchi'tech C'uj.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj: Bin in ca' quinsbir
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ16.20‚Äë28; Mr.‚ÄØ8.30‚Äï9.1)
\p 
\v 21 Caj u qui' ma'quintaj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån bin a wa'arex ti' m åna' mac wa Cristojen.
\p 
\v 22 Caj ara'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïA teno' baxuquenechexo' tu tuchi'ten C'uj, jach yaj quin bin muc'yajn åquen. Cu bin u xunp' åtiquenob u jach ts'urirob u cajar u winiquirob jud√≠o yejer u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Bin u quinsenob chen ca' bin tac m åna' u nup u q'uinin C'uj cu bin u ric'siquen.
\p 
\v 23 Pachir caj ya'araj ti' tu cotor mac:
\p ‚ÄïWa mac u c'at u tar tin pach soc u c ånic in t' ån. Arej u p' åtej a ba' cu pachtic tu yor tu cotor u nonob åjiri' soc u betic a ba' u c'at C'uj. Rajra' y ån u tar tin pach cax wa quimij ich cruz.
\v 24 A mac a cu tucric ti' u nonob åjiri' ti' toy cuxa'an cu bin u satar a ba' jach manan co'oj. Cu bin u satar u cuxtar munt q'uin. Chen a mac a u c'at u quimin ti' ten cu bin u c' åmic a ba' jach manan co'oj, cu bin u c' åmic u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\v 25 M å' u joc'ar tu tsoyir cax cu ts'urintic tu cotor ba' ich yoc'ocab wa cu sat år u pixam. Quire' je' u bo'otic u bo'orir u si'pir.
\v 26 Wa mac cu ch'ic suraquir ti' ten yejer a ba' quin tsec'tic, baxuc a ba' quin camsic. Baxuc ten, ca' bin in ch'a'aj suraquir ti' quire' a teno' baxuquenechexo'. Quin bin in ch'a'aj suraquir ti' ca' bin taquen ich u sasirir C'uj in Tet yejer u muc' u y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj.
\v 27 Chen jach taj quin wac techex. Ch åc y ån jun yarob mac a tera' m å' ju bin quimin hasta cu yiric bic C'uj cu bin u reyinticob.
\s1 Caj waysa'b Jes√∫s  åc åtan u cams åwinicob
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ17.1‚Äë8; Mr.‚ÄØ9.2‚Äë8)
\p 
\v 28 Caj man turi' semana caj ts'oc u camsic a ra' t' åno' ti' u cams åwinicob. Jes√∫s caj naquij ich jo'r wits quir u t' ånic C'uj. Yet binacob Pedro yejer Jacobo yejer Juan, quire' payob ten Jes√∫s.
\v 29 Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj C'uj caj waysa'b u wich caj way u noc' s åc, jach s åc t'ina'an.
\v 30 Ray u q'uinin caj c'uchob ixba' Mois√©s yejer ixba' El√≠as. Caj c'uchob ich Jes√∫s.
\v 31 Caj u tsicban åjob yejer Jes√∫s bic tabar u quimin Jes√∫s soc u nupsic u t' ån C'uj ca' bin quimic ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. U sasirir C'uj b åcrista'bob.
\v 32 A Pedrojo' yejer u yet cams åwinicob jach p'enc åch tar u wen ånob caj ajob caj yirob u way år Jes√∫s. Baxuc ti' y ånob ca'tur xib ich yicn ån Jes√∫s.
\v 33 Quire' tan u binob nanach ixba' Mois√©s yejer ixba' El√≠as, Pedro caj ya'araj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech ‚Äïquij‚Äï. Jach tsoy ti' y åno'on tera'. Are ca' in c' åxejob p åser. Turi' ti' tech. Turi' ti' ixba' Mois√©s. Turi' ti' ixba' El√≠as.
\p Caj ya'araj aro' quire' m å' tu qui' tucraj a ba' caj u ya'araj.
\v 34 Ti' toy u tsicbar Pedro caj tari turiri' u muyarir caj jaq'uij yorob u cams åwinicob caj ts'oc u binob ixba' Mois√©s yejer ixba' El√≠as ich u muyarir.
\v 35 Caj yubob u t' ån C'uj ich u muyarir. Caj yubob ya'ara' ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA je'ra' in jach parar a mac in jach yaj. Ca' u'yex a ba' cu camsiquechex.
\p 
\v 36 Caj ts'oc u yubicob u t' ån tu ca' irob Jes√∫s tu junan m åna' mac ti' y ån. A m åna' u nup u cams åwinicob a ba' caj u yirob tu cotor aro' tu m åcob u chi' m å' tu ya'arajob ti' mac a ba' caj u yirob.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu joc'sic u quisinin ti' chan xib
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ17.14‚Äë21; Mr.‚ÄØ9.14‚Äë29)
\p 
\v 37 Caj sasij, caj ts'oc u yemanob ich u jo'r wits Jes√∫s yejerob a m åna' u nupo'. Caj tar a pimo' quir u nup'icob Jes√∫s.
\v 38 Ti' y ån mac turi' ich a pimo' caj u puraj u t' ån ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech quin chich c'atic tech ca' a chan yamten ti' in parar quire' turi' ten.
\v 39 Ca' bin chucuc ten quisin in chan parar. Cu sepquintic yaw åt, cu y ån sat år yor hasta cu yom u chi'. Ca' bin p'at åc ten u quisinin in parar cu jach ts'ab år u muc'yaj ten quisin hasta m åna' yor.
\p 
\v 40 A xibo' caj u ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïCaj in chich araj ti'ob a cams åwinicob ca' u joc'sejob u quisinin chen m å' c'ucha'an yorob u joc'sicob.
\p 
\v 41 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' a mac cuxa'an u q'uinin baje'rer. Biquinin m å' a wacsm ånex ta wor ti' C'uj? Biquinin jach chichex a jo'r? Ya'ab u q'uinin ti' y ånen tera' m å' toy a wacsejex ta wor. A ber ca' bin a wacsex ta wor ten.
\p Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj a xibo':
\p ‚ÄïToc p åyej a parar a te'ra'.
\p 
\v 42 Tabar u nats' år ich Jes√∫s a quisino' caj rubsaj ich ru'um. Caj satij yor ten quisin. Chen Jes√∫s caj u q'ueyaj u quisinin. A baywo' caj joc' u quisinin. Caj ts'oc u joc'ar u quisin caj jawij, Jes√∫s caj u sutaj ti' u tet.
\v 43 Jach jaq'uij yorob a pimo' quire' caj yirajob carem u beyaj C'uj.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ca' aric bin in ca' quimin
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ17.22‚Äë23; Mr.‚ÄØ9.30‚Äë32)
\p Ti' toy jac'a'an yorob a pimo' ti' u carem beyaj Jes√∫s.
\v 44 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïQui' uyex a je'ra' a ba' quin camsiquechex baje'rer. M å' ju y ån tubur techex. Quire' bin u ca'ob u c'ubirenob a teno' ti' a mac a cu p'actiquenob a teno' bayxuquenechexo'.
\p 
\v 45 U cams åwinicob m å' ju najtajob a ba' ara'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s. M å' ju najtajob quire' m å' toc ara'b ten Jes√∫s ti'ob a ba' u c'at ya'aric. Quire' suracob quir u c'aticob a ba' ara'b ti'ob sam.
\s1 A mac a jach no'je'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ18.1‚Äë5; Mr.‚ÄØ9.33‚Äë37)
\p 
\v 46 U cams åwinicob quet u pacran acob soc yerob mac jach no'jo' ich u yet cams åwinicob.
\v 47 Jes√∫s caj u najtaj a ba' cu tucricob tu yorob rajen caj u p åyaj chichan quir u ch'iquintic yicn ån.
\v 48 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïWa tsoy ca betiquex ti' a je' chichana' cax ti' u jer xan quire' ca yajquintiquen. Tsoy ca betiquex ten xan. Baxuc tsoy caj a betex ti' C'uj a mac caj u tuchi'tajen. A mac a cu tucric ich u w åc' ås b åjiri': ‚ÄúM å' no'jen a teno'‚Äù, raji'o' toc no'j  åc åtan tu wich C'uj.
\s1 A mac a m å' u p'actic tech raji' a nup
\r (Mr.‚ÄØ9.38‚Äë40)
\p 
\v 49 Caj ya'araj Juan:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, tij quiraj turi' mac caj u joc'saj quisin ca'ch. Caj u t' ånaj a c'aba'. Tij caraj ti': ‚ÄúTsire'ej‚Äù quire' m å' u say år ta pach quir u c ånic a t' ån. An ten bic to'on quic say år ta pach.
\p 
\v 50 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTsire'ej, cax m å' ja wac ti' quire' a mac a m å' u p'actic to'on cu yamtico'on.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu q'ueyic Juan yejer Jacobo
\p 
\v 51 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin u ca' pay år Jes√∫s ten C'uj ca' xic ich ca'anan. Jes√∫s u c'at u jach bin ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Ts'ajan yor tar u bin.
\v 52 Rajen caj u tuchi'taj m å' ya'abir mac soc p åybejob cu binob. Robob caj binob caj c'uchob ich u cajar Samaria, caj u c åxtajob mac quir u yacsa'rob wen ånob.
\v 53 Chen ich u cajar Samaria m å' u c'at yacsa'robi' quire' ti' cu binob ich u cajar Jerusal√©n, Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob.
\v 54 Caj w åc' ås urob ich Jes√∫s a tuchi'ta'bob. Quire' yubob m å' u yacsa'rob a Juano' yejer Jacobo quire' yubob m å' acsa'bobi' caj ya'arob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïArej to'on in w åjcamsay åjirechob ca' tac u c'aq'uir ca'anan ca' r åc erac ara' cajaro' an bic caj u betaj El√≠as uch, a cu tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj uch.
\p 
\v 55 Jes√∫s caj u sut u b åj quir u p åctic a ca'tur u cams åwinicob. Caj u q'ueyaj caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' m å' a werex mac ca ts'urintiquex.
\v 56 A teno' baxuquenechexo' m å' taren in ch'esic u cajar mac, taren in ta'quic tu cotor mac quire' tu tuchi'ten C'uj.
\p Jeroj caj binob ich u jer cajar.
\s1 A mac a ju c'at u tarob tu pach Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.19‚Äë22)
\p 
\v 57 Ti' toy cu binob ich u berir Jerusal√©n. Turi' mac caj u ya'araj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïArej in tar ta pach cax tu ca bin.
\p 
\v 58 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA boboch pec'o' y ån u jor tu cu wen ån baxuc a ch'ich'o' y ån u c' åbir che' tu cu wen ån. Chen a teno' m åna' tu quin chatar in jesic in b åj a teno', baxuquenechexo'.
\p 
\v 59 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u jer mac:
\p ‚ÄïCojen tin pach ‚Äïquij‚Äï, quir a c ånic in t' ån.
\p Chen caj ya'araj ti' a mac pay ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïArej in p'at år ich yicn ån in tet hasta cu quimin in tet, je' in tar ta pache'.
\p 
\v 60 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ‚ÄïA mac a irej a quimeno', raji'ob cu bin u muquicob u quimirir. Chen tech xen tsec'tej u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj tu cu bin u reyintejob C'uj.
\p 
\v 61 Chen ti' y ån u jer caj ara'b ti':
\p ‚ÄïA teno' je' in tar ta pache'. Ar in bin in c'atej ti' in b åjob wa tsoy in tar ta pach.
\p 
\v 62 Chen Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïA mac a u c'at u jach tar tin pach chen m å' u jach p'is u b åj ca' tac tin pach. Wa cu chen tucric a ba' caj u p' åtaj je' u nacar yor ti' a ba' a cu tar ti'. Aro' m å' tsoy u beyaj tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj.
\c 10
\s1 Jes√∫s tu tuchi'tic ca' xicob a setentajo'
\p 
\v 1 Caj ts'oc u tsicbar ti' a mac a ju c'at u tarob tu pach Jes√∫s caj u tetaj u jerob setenta u cams åwinicob. Caj u tuchi'taj ca' ca'turob ich tu cotor u chan cajar. Baxuc ich tu cotor u yajaw cajar xan. Raji'ob cu y ån binob. Pachir cu c'uchur Jes√∫s.
\v 2 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTi' y ån mac pim u c'at yubicob u t' ån C'uj chen a cu beyajob, m å' nepimi' a cu tsec'ticob u t' ån C'uj ti'ob. Aro' irej wa ti' y ån jach ya'ab u trigo quir u w åtic. Chen m åna' mac quir u w åtic. Rajen ca' a t' ånex C'uj soc u tuchi'tic mac quir u bin u tsicb åtic u t' ån C'uj soc c'ucha'an yorob u yubicob u t' ån C'uj.
\v 3 Baje'rer ca' xiquechex tu caj in wa'araj a binex. Je' a wiricobexe' irob barum. Robob cu bin yiriquechexob irechex t åm ån yuc. An ten bic barum u c'at u chi'ic t åm ån yuc. Baxuc a xibo' u c'at quinsiquechexob.
\v 4 Ca' bin xiquechex m å' ja y ån ch'iquex a chimex, u boxer a taq'uinex m å' ca ch'iquex. M å' ja ch'iquex a pech' x ån åb, ts'ot a bin beyajex. M å' ja y ån wec' t' åniquex mac tu ca binex a tsec'tiquex u t' ån C'uj.
\v 5 Ca' bin y ån ocaquex ich yatoch mac, y ån arex ti' tu ca t' ånic: ‚ÄúIn c'at ca' qui'ac a worex ti' C'uj a mac ti' y ån ich yatoch tera'.‚Äù
\v 6 Wa ti' y ån mac a tabar u qui' tar yor ti' C'uj, je' u bin qui' tar yor ti' C'uj. An ten bic techex caj a c'atajex ti'. Chen wa ti' y ån mac m å' u qui'tar yor ti' C'uj. Aro' m å' ju bin qui' tar yor ti' C'uj. A b åjiri'ex ca bin a waquex ti': ‚ÄúJe' in w åc' ås ch'ic a ba' caj in wa'araj techex u qui'ir yor C'uj.‚Äù
\v 7 Tiri' ca p'at årex ich yatoch a tu yacsechex m å' a ca' cay binex ich u jer naj. Jan ånex uc'urnenex xan a ba' cu ts'ic techex an biquex a jan ånex ta watochex. Irechex a mac cu c' åmic u bo'orir u beyaj quire' ra' u bo'orir tu ca beyajex.
\v 8 Wa ca wocarex ich u chan cajar tu cu yacsiquechex, toc jantechex ba' cu ts'ictechex.
\v 9 Jawsex u yajir tu ca binex ich u chan cajar. Y ån arex ti': ‚ÄúToc ti' y ånechex baje'ra' quire' toc c'uchij tu q'uinin tu ca bin a reyintiquex C'uj.‚Äù
\v 10 Wa ca wocarex ich u chan cajar tu m å' u yacsiquex, toc ruq'uenex ich tan bej ich u cajar. Ca waquex ti'ob:
\v 11 ‚ÄúCax u ru'umin a cajarex a cu nich'ir tin woc quin toc pusticob tin wocob quire' c'as caj a betajex. A baywo' quin toc aric techex c'uchij tu q'uinin C'uj ca' bin a reyintiquex, chen m å' a c'at a reyintiquex C'uj.‚Äù Baxuc y ån a waquex ti' mac a m å' u yacsiquex.
\p 
\v 12 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob a setentajo':
\p ‚ÄïChen a teno' quin wac techex ca' bin xuruc t' ån a ra cajaro' a m å' tu yacsajechex, jach manan cu bin ts'ab år u muc'yajob ten C'uj. Chen u cajar Sodoma, m å' u nebin muc'yajob a ch'esa'b ten C'uj yejer c'ac' uch.
\s1 U cajarob a m å' tu c' åmajob u t' ån C'uj
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ11.20‚Äë24)
\p 
\v 13 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s ti' a setentajo' caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJach otsir techex ich u cajar Coraz√≠n. Baxuc otsirechex ich u cajar Betsaida. Jaj ixt åco' wa ti' y ån mac uch ich u cajar Tiro yejer u cajar Sid√≥n caj u yesej u carem beyajob. An ten bic caj in wesaj techex carem beyajob. Robob a ti' y ånob uch ich u cajar Tiro yejer Sid√≥n. Tabar ix ti' ucho' ca' bin u c'axicob yorob tan a p' åticob u manob tu c'asir. Jaj ix ti' caj u buquintajob u rabir u noc'. Baxuc caj u posta'antajob u jo'rob yejer c'uta'an soc yer mac tucur u ca'ob. An ten bic mac nanij cu beticob uch.
\v 14 Ca' bin xuruc t' ån a techex a c åja'anechex ich u cajar Coraz√≠n yejer Betsaida. Jach manan ca bin muc'yajex chen a mac a c åja'anob uch ich u cajar Tiro yejer Sid√≥n, m å' ju bin nemuc'yajob.
\v 15 A techex ca tucriquex ich a cajar Capernaum jach no'jechex yiriquechex C'uj. Chen C'uj m å' ju yiriquechex wa jach no'jechex cu bin u puriquechex ich c'ac' munt q'uin quire' m å' ta wacsajex ta wor ti' ten.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄôA mac a cu quibiquex a t' ånex baxuc ten cu quibob in t' ån xan. A maque' m å' ju c' åmic a ba' ca waquex ti'ob. Baxuc ten m å' u c' åmicob a ba' quin wac ti'ob. Baxuc a mac m å' ju c' åmicob a ba' quin wa'aric ti'. M å' tan u c' åmic a ba' cu ya'aric C'uj quire' raji' caj u tuchi'tajen.
\s1 Caj urob a setenta tuchi'ta'b ten Jes√∫s
\p 
\v 17 Caj urob a setentajo' tub binob u tsec'ticob u t' ån C'uj. Jach qui' yorob caj urob ich Jes√∫s, caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir, cax c'ac'as quisinob caj u yubob ic t' ånob caj ij caraj ti'ob: ‚ÄúQuisin, ich u c'aba' Jes√∫s, ca' xiquex‚Äù, jeroj joq'ui.
\p 
\v 18 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA teno' caj in wiraj a rubsiquex u muc' a quisino'. Seb caj in wiraj a rubsiquex u muc' a quisino'.
\v 19 M å' ja wirej, an ten bic c'ucha'an a worex ti' a joc'siquex quisin quire' a teno' caj in j åsatechex in muc'. Baxuc xan ca pech' åctiquex can a y åc u cojo', cax roroch m å' ja bin a wu'iquex yajir. Baxuc caj in j åsatechex in muc' soc m å' a s åjtiquex a quisin quire' c'ucha'an a worex ti'.
\v 20 M å' a chen qui'quintex a worex quire' a c'ac'as quisino' caj u yubajob a t' ånex, barej jach qui'quintex a worex quire' ti' ts'iba'an ich u ju'unin C'uj a c'aba' techex. Quire' ti' ts'iba'an a mac a caj u yacsajob tu yorob.
\s1 Caj qui'jij yor Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ11.25‚Äë27; 13.16‚Äë17)
\p 
\v 21 Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj qui'quinta'b yor Jes√∫s ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj, Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj, in tetech, cax ca'anano' cax yoc'ocabo'. U jach ts'urirech quire' tech ta r åc betaj tu cotor ba'. Jach caremech C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï. M å' ja wirej, caj a j åsa a muc' ti' a mac a m å' yerob ju'un soc u joc'sicob c'ac'as quisinob soc c'ucha'an yorob ti' a jach quisino'. M å' ta ts'aja u najtejob a ba' a c'at ti' a mac u ne'erob ba' quire' baxuc a c'at tech.
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄôJes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a mac ti' y ånob yejerob setenta. Tu cotor mac a teno' cu bin u ts'urintiquen quire' baxuc u c'at C'uj. M åna' mac yer u parareni' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, chen in Tet yer maqueni'. M åna' mac yer mac in Tet chen ten quire' u pararen. Rajen u jer mac c'ucha'an yor yer C'uj wa quin cha'ic u najtic.
\p 
\v 23 Caj binob tu junan Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob. Caj u p åctaj caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïQui'quintej a worex quire' a ba' ca wiriquex in camsic baxuc quire' ca wiriquenex.
\v 24 Quire' y ån ya'ab y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj uch. Baxuc reyob xan, quire' u c'at yiriquenob uch, chen m å' yirenob uch cax u c'atob yubicob a ba' quin camsic an bic techex ca wiriquenex in camsicob, chen m å' tu yubob.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic a mac u jach tsoy yiric u rac'ob
\p 
\v 25 C'uchij turiri' mac ich Jes√∫s. A cu camsic u t' ån Mois√©s. Tar u tumtic yor Jes√∫s tu cu camsic mac. Caj u c'ata ti':
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ba' quin bin in betej quir in cuxtar munt q'uin?
\p 
\v 26 Caj nunca' ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïBa' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj tu ca xaquic?
\p 
\v 27 Y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s caj u nunca:
\p ‚ÄïU t' ån C'uj cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúQuet ca' ic yajquintej ic Jaj Ts'urir yejer tu cotor ic pixam yejer tu cotor ic muc' yejer tu cotor ic tucur ich ic jo'r.‚Äù Baxuc ca' ic yajquintej ij quet cajar. An ten bic ic yajquintic ic w åc' ås b åjiri'.
\p 
\v 28 Caj ara'b ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTaj a ba' caj a nuncaj. Wa ca betic baxuc aro', y ån a cuxtar munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 29 Quire' cu tucric m å' qui' nunc'ab ten Jes√∫s. Rajen ca' u c'ataj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïMac in wet cajari' quir in yajquintic?
\p 
\v 30 A baywo' caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s soc u camsic:
\p ‚ÄïCaj binij turi' winic ich u cajar Jeric√≥. Ti' ruq'uij ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Caj u nup'aj mac a cu yac'r å' ba'. Caj chuc ten y åjac'r å' y åjirob ba' r åc ac'ra'b u ba'tac cax u buquim ån u noc' r åc ch'a'b ti', caj ts'oc u r åj j åts'ic, irej wa quimen caj u p' åtajob.
\v 31 Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj manij sacerdote ich bej tu chara'an a mac jats' irej quimen. Caj yiraj charique' nach caj man.
\v 32 Baxuc caj tar u winiquir jud√≠o u yo'nen Lev√≠, ra' cu beyaj ich carem naj. Caj yira charic a mac jats' caj u pot mastaj.
\v 33 Caj tar u winiquir u cajar Samaria nach u tar caj tarij tan u nats' år tu chara'an a mac j åts'a'an. Caj u yiraj charic caj u yajquintaj.
\v 34 U winiquir samaria caj c'uchij tu chara'an a xibo' a j åts'a'ano' caj u ts' åcaj tu c'orij tut jats' caj u jic'taj tsats yejer u c'ab u wich uva quir u jaw år. Caj u nacsaj tu pach u tsimin quire' ra' u tsimin caj bin u puric quir u c ånanta' ti' tu tu m åjantaj yatoch.
\v 35 Caj sasij quire' bin u ca' u winiquir samaria. Caj u ch åc jaraj u taq'uin ca' turur u s åc taq'uin caj u ts'aja ti' a mac y ånin yatoch. Caj ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúC ånantej a je' xiba' wa ca r åc xupic a taq'uin ti' a mac ca' bin uquen je' in bo'otiquech.‚Äù
\p Baxuc caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'.
\v 36 Caj ts'oc u tsicbar Jes√∫s ti' a j åts'a'an caj u c'ataj ti' y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s:
\p ‚ÄïArej ten ich a m åna' u nup xibo' a mac caj u yajquintaj?
\p 
\v 37 Caj ya'araj y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s. A mac a tu yiraj otsir a j åts'a'ano', raji' tu yajquintaj. Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc tech rajra' ca' a yajquintej mac.
\s1 C'uchij Jes√∫s ich yatochob Marta yejer Mar√≠a
\p 
\v 38 Ti' toy cu bin Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob ich u berir Jerusal√©n caj c'uchij tu cajar. Ti' y ån xquic u c'aba' Marta. Raji' caj u yacsaj ich yatoch.
\v 39 A Martajo' y ån u yits'in Mar√≠a u c'aba'. Caj cur åj Mar√≠a ich yoc Jes√∫s quire' u c'at yubic a ba' cu camsa'.
\v 40 Chen Marta cu tucric jach ya'ab u beyaj rajen tarij ich Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquen‚Äï, wa ca jach tucriquen ca wac ti' in wits'in ca' tac u yamten.
\p 
\v 41 Chen Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ‚ÄïMarta ‚Äïquen‚Äï, ca jach tucric a beyaj, rajen choc a wor quire' jach ya'ab.
\v 42 Mar√≠a caj u tetaj a ba' jach tsoy rajen cu tucric u tar yubej in t' ån. Rajen m åna' mac cu ma'quintic soc m å' u tar.
\c 11
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic bic tabar ic t' ånic C'uj
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ6.9‚Äë15; 7.7‚Äë11)
\p 
\v 1 Ti' y ån Jes√∫s tu cu t' ånic C'uj uch caj ts'oc u t' ånic C'uj caj c'uchob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s turi'. Caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïJach Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, camsenob bic in t' ånicob C'uj an ten bic Juan caj u camsaj u cams åwinicob.
\p 
\v 2 Caj nunca'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïCa' binex a t' åniquex C'uj. Baxuc a je'ra' ca waquex ti':
\q1 In Tetob a mac ti' y åno' ich ca'anan. Quin c'atob soc tu cotor mac cu c'ujintiquech. Quin c'aticob tech ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin ca' bin a reyintej ich yoc'ocab.
\v 3 Chan chuquej tenob in woch soc ti'bir y ån tenob ti' u q'uinin baje'rer.
\v 4 Jawsej tenob in si'pirob a ba' si'pir caj in betajob quire' quin jawsicob u si'pirob in rac'ob cax a ba' c'asir caj u betajob ten xan. M å' ja cha'ic in binob tu quin p åyicob in si'pirob. M å' ja cha'ic in ts'urinticob a ba' quin pachticob tin worob a c'aso'.
\p 
\v 5 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïQui' tucrej a ba' u ber wa ca' bin xiquech tu y ån a ju yajech cax chumuc ac'bir ti' ca bin a c'atic ti'. Ca wa'aric ti': ‚ÄúChan chuquej ten a woch pan quire' a yajen, cax m åna' u nup pan.
\v 6 M å' ja wirej, tan tu c'uchur a mac u yajen, nach u tar, caj tarij quire' m åna' ten quir in jansic.‚Äù
\v 7 A mac a ti' y ån ich yatoch a mac a ju jach yaj, a mac tar c'atbir yoch. Jaj ixt åco cu nunquic: ‚ÄúM å' a pecsic in wor quire' caj in toc m åcaj u jor in watoch. Toc ti' y ånen yejer in parar tin wen ånob. M å' jin riq'uir in ts'ic tech a ba' a c'at.‚Äù
\v 8 Quire' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, taj quin wa'aric techex. Cax m å' u riq'uir u ts'ic ti' yoch quire' jach yaj yiric. Chen je' u riq'uir u ts'ic ti' a ba' u c'at quire' rajra' cu jach p'isic u b åj u c'atic ti'.
\v 9 Baxuc ti' C'uj xan ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï: C'atej ti' C'uj, je' u ts'iquex tex. C åxtex a ba' a c'at, C'uj cu bin u cha'ic a wiriquex. C'atex ti' C'uj, irej a mac cu c'atic ich u jor naj, je' u ts'ab år techex an bic ca c'atic.
\v 10 A teno', quin wac techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, tu cotor mac a cu c'atic ti', je' u ts'ab år ti'. Tu cotor mac cu c åxtic a ba' u c'at, je' u yirique'. Tu cotor mac cu c'atic a ba' u c'at, an ten bic caj u c'ataj ti' xib ich u jor yatoch. Je' u ts'ab år ti'.
\p 
\v 11 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïWa mac ti' y ån ta wicn ånex a y ån u pararo' je' wa ju ts'ic ti' tunich wa caj u c'ataj yoch pan? M å' ju ts'ic tunich ti'. Je' wa ju ts'ic ti' can quir u ch'ic wa cu c'atic yoch c åy? M å' ju ts'ic ti'.
\v 12 Je' wa ju ts'ic ti' roroch quir u chi'ic wa cu c'atic yoch ye'er cax. M å' ju ts'ic ti'.
\v 13 A techexo' cax jach c'asechex a werex a ts'iquex ti' a parar a ba' jach tsoyo'. Jach manan tsoyir a ti' y ån ich ca'anano'. Baxuc a C'ujo' a ti' y ån ich ca'an åno' jach manan tsoyir cu ts'ab år ti' u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj ti' a mac a cu c'atic ti'e'.
\s1 Pac' u pach Jes√∫s aca'an quisin ti'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.22‚Äë30; Mr.‚ÄØ3.19‚Äë27)
\p 
\v 14 Caj u joc'saj quisin Jes√∫s ti' a xibo' a m å' ju joc'ar u t' åne'. Caj ts'oc u joc'sic caj y ånxchun u t' ån. Rajen jaq'uij yorob a pimo'.
\v 15 Chen y ån mac m å' ya'abir caj u ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïA je' xiba' cu joc'sic c'ac'as quisin quire' yamta'b ten Beelzeb√∫ quire' ra' u Jach Ts'urir u quisinin.
\p 
\v 16 Chen ti' y ånob u jerob u c'at u tus tumticob yor Jes√∫s quir u yesic carem beyaj soc yerob wa tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj wa m å'.
\v 17 Chen Jes√∫s yer ba' cu tucricob tu yorob tu p åc'ob u pach u jach ts'urir quisin Jes√∫s. Caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' ja wirej, tu cotor ru'um tu cu reyinticob rey. Wa ju jer junxot cu ts'ictarob yejer u jer junxot cu bin u r åc ch'esicob u yet cajarob m å' ju p'at mac. Baxuc xan a mac p'eri' c åjricob ich yatoch cax u w åc' ås u b åjob wa cu pacran ts'ictarob cu bin u ch'esicob u b åj.
\v 18 Baxuc xan a Satan√°so', wa ju winiquirob Satan√°s cu pacran ts'ictarob cu bin u r åc ch'esicob u b åj. M åna' mac cu bin u reyinticob Satan√°s. Quire' techex ta wa'arajex quin joc'sic in wet quisinin. Quire' caj u yamtajen Beelzeb√∫.
\v 19 Wa baxuc quin joc'sic quisin an ten bic ca tucriquex. Baxuc arex ten bic u cams åwinicobex, cu joc'sicob a quisinino'. M å' u joc'sicob quire' yamta'b ten Beelzeb√∫ quire' a werex yamta'bob ten C'uj quir u joc'sicob. M å' ja ta'quiquex in jo'r, tan in yamta'r ten Beelzeb√∫.
\v 20 M å' taj cu yamtiquen Beelzeb√∫ quir in joc'sic quisin. Chen u muc' C'uj quir in joc'sic a quisino'. Aro' cu yesic c'uchij tu q'uinin a reyintiquex C'uj.
\p 
\v 21 Ti' toy cu camsic Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA werex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, a mac jach chich u muc', irej a quisino', u m åchm ån u mascab quire' cu c ånantic a ba' y ån ti'.
\v 22 Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu tar a jach manan chich u muc', iren ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. Cu ts'ictar yejer a quisino', cu r åc to'car u mascab tu cu c ånantic a ba' y ån ti', cu ts'ocar u to'car ti', cu r åc ch'ic u j åsic ich u rac'ob.
\p 
\v 23 ‚ÄôQuire' a mac m å' ju yamtiquen cu yamtic a quisino' quire' a mac m å' ju yamtiquen irej, tan u joc'sic mac ca' xic erar ich c'ac'.
\s1 A c'ac'as quisino' caj urij a joc'sa'b cuche'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.43‚Äë45)
\p 
\v 24 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA ucho' joc'sa'b quisinin ten mac tar cu mano' u quisinin ich tacay ru'um tu y ån u yet quisinin. Caj u c åxtaj tu cu jesic u b åj. Chen m å' tu yiraj. A quisino' caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúJe' in ca' bin tu joq'uen a ucho' soc in w åc' ås ocar ti'.‚Äù
\v 25 Caj sutn åj a quisino' caj u yiraj a je' xiba', irej yatoch toc misa'an chen m åna' mac y ånin u pixam a xibo', toc qui' yor.
\v 26 Rajen caj bin u p åyej siete yet quisinin jach manan c'as u yet quisino'. A ti' ucho' m å' nejach c'asi'. Caj r åc ocob a quisino' quir u ts'urinta' a quisino' ten a xibo'. A xibo' a aca'an ti' quisin jach manan c'as baje'rer, a ucho' m å' nec'asi'.
\s1 A mac jach qui' yor jach jaj
\p 
\v 27 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s ti' a pimo'. Turi' xquic ich yicn ånob caj u puraj u t' ån ti' Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïMun tsoyir a n å'o' a tu ch'isajech a ta chuch a yim.
\p 
\v 28 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJaj ixt åc taj a ba' ca wac chen jach manan qui' yor a cu quibic u t' ån C'uj a tan u man tu tsoyir a ba' cu betic.
\s1 A mac jach c'aso' cu c'aticob yiricob carem beyaj
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.38‚Äë42; Mr.‚ÄØ8.12)
\p 
\v 29 Caj u r åc tar a pimo' uch quir u r åc b åcristicob Jes√∫s, caj u y ånxchun ya'aric uche':
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, a mac cuxa'an u q'uinin bajera' jach c'asechex quire' ca c'atiquex a wiriquex carem beyaj soc a werex wa tuchi'ten C'uj. Chen turi' cu bin ts'ab år techex soc a werex caj u tuchi'ten C'uj. Cu bin u betej C'uj an ten bic caj u betaj ti' y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj uch, u c'aba' Jon√°s.
\v 30 Soc yerob winiquirob uch ich u cajar N√≠nive tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj Jon√°s. Baxuc ten ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, soc a wer caj u tuchi'tajen C'uj xan.
\p 
\v 31 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s ti' a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïCa' bin c'uchuc ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, tu q'uinin cu xur t' ån, a ray u q'uinino', cu bin riq'uir mac a quimen a ucho'. Cu bin tar xquic u reina u winiquirob u cajar Seba. Aro' tar cu bin  åc åtan C'ujo', cu bin u ta'quic a jo'rex a mac cuxa'an u q'uinin bajera', quire' c'as caj a betaj techex. M å' ja wirej, a ray xquico' jach nach u tar uch quir yubic u t' ån Salom√≥n quire' u nejach er ba' Salom√≥n. Chen ti' y ånen baje'ra' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, jach no'jen a teno'. A Salom√≥n ucho' m å' nejach no'ji' chen techex m å' ja qui' quibiquex in t' ån.
\v 32 Ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t' ån, a ray u q'uinin ca' bin xic  åc åtan C'uj tu cotor mac. Quire' u winiquirob tu cajar N√≠nive ca' bin ts'ocac u riq'uir tu quimen a ucho'. Tar cu binob  åc åtan C'uj quir u ta'quiquex a jo'rob. Quire' c'as caj betajex. M å' ja wirej, robob caj u c'axajob yorob soc u p' åticob u c'asirob uch caj yubob caj u tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj Jon√°s. M å' jach no'j a Jon√°s a ucho'. Caj u c'axob u yor u winiquirob u cajar N√≠nive. A teno' jach no'jen chen m å' tan a c'axiquex a worex ti' in t' ån.
\s1 Ij quich irej quib
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ5.15; 6.22‚Äë23)
\p 
\v 33 U camsa'bar Jes√∫s, irej cu t' åbic quib quir u yerc'ac'tic mac. Rajen Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA mac a cu t' åbic u quib ca' bin ts'ocar u t' åbic m å' u b åric yejer xac. M å' ju ta'quic u quib tu yatoch soc m å' yiric mac. Ca' bin ts'ocar u t' åbic cu chen na'sic ca'anan quir yerc'ac'tic a mac a cu yocar. Baxuc ten ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. M å' tin mucric u t' ån C'uj ti' techex. Caj in chen tsec'taj techex u t' ån C'uj  åc åtan tu cotor mac soc u r åc u'wic.
\v 34 A quibo' quir u yerc'ac'tic mac. Rajen wa m å' p'ur buts' ti' u ras quib ch åca'an ic betic a ba' ij c'at. Wa p'ur buts' ti' u ras quib m å' u neyerc'ac'tic ba'. Rajen ac'bir ij c åjtoch soc m å' ch åca'an ic betej a ba' ij c'at. Baxuc techex yejer a wichex wa tsoy ta t' ån ca wiriquenex, je' u yocar in t' ån tu quin camsic techex. Wa m å' tsoy ta t' ån ca wiriquenex, m å' u yocar in t' ån ta pixamex tu quin camsic techex, rajen a pixamex cu bin tu yac'birir.
\v 35 Rajen qui' c ånantex a b åj soc m å' ja ruc'siquex in t' ån ich a pixamex quire' wa ca m å'quintic in t' ån cu bin yac'birch åj år a pixamex.
\v 36 Quire' wa ti' y ån in t' ån ta pixamex wa m å' a c' ås ruc'siquex in t' ån ta pixamex cu bin u qui' yamtic techex soc a manex tu tsoyir. M åna' yac'birir ta pixamex. Aro' an ten bic cu yerc'ac'tic tech quib.
\s1 Jes√∫s tan u ta'quic u jo'rob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer y åjcamsay åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ23.1‚Äë36; Mr.‚ÄØ12.38‚Äë40; Lc.‚ÄØ20.45‚Äë47)
\p 
\v 37 Caj ts'oc u tsicbar Jes√∫s a ba' caj u camsaj sam. Caj tari' turi' a fariseojo' caj payij quir u jan ån ich yatoch. Caj binij Jes√∫s caj oquij caj cur åj tu pojche'ir tu cu jan ån.
\v 38 Rajen jaq'uij yor a fariseojo' quire' m å' tu p'o'aj u c' åb Jes√∫s, m å' toy jan åqui'. M å' ja wirej, u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' nanij u p'o'ic u c' åb m å' toy jan åqui'. Quire' cu tucricob baxuc cu qui'quinticob yor C'uj.
\v 39 Jes√∫s yer jac'a'an yor a fariseojo', rajen caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' u winiquirechex jud√≠o a fariseojo', irechex ruch a ca p'o'iquex u pach chen tu japnin m å' a p'o'iquex. A techexo' u winiquirechex jud√≠o a fariseojo' irechex u r åquir a woch a ta qui' p'o'ajex tu pach chen u japnin m å' ta p'ojechexi', rajen ti' toy eq'ui'. A techex irex u ruchir a wochex chen p'o'a'an u pach, quire' ca qui' p'o'ic a c' åb soc mac yiric jach tsoyechex chen m å' a tucric wa p'o'a'an a pixamex. Jach ec' a pixamex quire' tu cotor a si'pirex.
\v 40 M å' ja wirej, C'uj caj u betaj ic winiquir baxuc ic pixam, rajen m å' u chen c'at ca' ichin åco'on ij winiquir, u c'at xan toc tsoy ic pixam xan.
\v 41 Soc y ån techex jach tsoy a pixamex chuquex a ba' y ån techex ti' a mac a m åna' ti'.
\p 
\v 42 ‚ÄôJach otsirechex u winiquirechex jud√≠o a fariseojo' caj a chuquiquex turiri' a ba' y ån techex ich a diezo' soc a ts'iquex ti' C'uj. Cax a ba' p åc'ar quir a ts' åquic a b åj, cax a ba' a ts'ac a woch, a turiri' ich a diezo'. Jot, cax m å' a ts'iquex ti', quire' m å' tan a yajquintic mac, m å' ca yajquintex C'uj. Ba' quiri' jach manan tsoyir ca' a yajquintex mac. Baxuc aro' ca' a yajquintiquex C'uj. Chen m å' a y ån p' åtiquex a ts'iquex ti' C'uj a ba' nani ca ts'iquex ti'.
\p 
\v 43 ‚ÄôJach otirechex u winiquirechex jud√≠o a fariseojo'. A c'at ca' u yiriquechexob jach no'jechex. Rajen a c'atex u cutan jach tsoy ich tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Baxuc a c'atex soc mac cu qui' t' åniquex tu cu najm ånicob yoch.
\p 
\v 44 ‚ÄôA techexo', jach otsirechex u winiquirechex jud√≠o a fariseojo'. A techexo', u winiquirechex jud√≠o a fariseojo' irechex u mucnaj mac tu cu najmuquic mac, chen m åna' u mucnaj, m å' ch åca'an. Rajen a mac a cu man tan u ch' åctic quire' m å' yer wa muca'an mac ti'.
\p 
\v 45 Ti' y ån turi' y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s caj u nuncaj caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïCax ca wa'aric ti'ob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' tan a p'astiquenob quire' p'eri'enob yejer u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo'.
\p 
\v 46 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s:
\p ‚ÄïA techexo', jach otsirechex y åjcams åy åjirechex u t' ån Mois√©s. M å' ja wirej, ca ts' åric u pach a rac'ob u betic a ba' jach yaj quire' ca jenmastic u t' ån Mois√©s. Aro' irej a mac cu ts' åric u pach ca' u cuchej a ba' jach ar, chen u b åjiri' m å' u yamtic u cuchej. M å' ju c'at u cuchej.
\p 
\v 47 ‚ÄôOtsirechex y åjcams åy åjirechex u t' ån Mois√©s, ca ts' åpquintiquex tunich tu mucnaj y åjtsequirob u t' ån C'uj soc tsoy yiric tu cotor mac. Ra'iri' y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj a quinsa'b ten a nunquirex uch.
\v 48 Cax ca ts' åpquintiquex tunich tu mucnaj soc a s åjtiquex y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj. Jach irex a nunquirex a mac tu quinsajob y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj quire' ich a tucurex a c'at a quinsenex.
\p 
\v 49 ‚ÄôRajen C'uj a yer tu cotor ba' caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúQuin tuchi'tic y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj tu y ånechex, y ån jun yar cu bin u quinsicob, y ån jun yar cu bin ts'ab år u muc'yajob‚Äù, baxuc caj ya'araj C'uj uch.
\v 50 Jach taj caj a betajex an ten bic caj u ya'araj C'uj. Rajen ca bin a bo'otiquex u bo'orir tu ta quinsajobex, cax tu y ånxchun tu cotor ba'.
\v 51 Quire' tu y ånxchun u quinsicob Abel a ucho' hasta u q'uinin baje'rer caj u quinsajob Zacar√≠as. Ti' caj u quinsajob Zacar√≠as n åts'a'an tu cu quinsicob wac åx quir u ts'ic ti' C'uj baxuc c' ås n åts'a'an carem naj. Je' a r åc bin a bo'otiquex u bo'orir tu r åc quinsa'b y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj. Ti' techex a mac cuxa'an u q'uinin baje'rer.
\p 
\v 52 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s:
\p ‚ÄïOtsirechex techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, ya'ab ca najtiquex ti' u t' ån Mois√©s. Ca camsic ti'ob xan, chen m å' a qui' camsej a ba' jach taje'. M å' ja quibiquex a ba' ti' y ån ich u t' ån Mois√©s. A mac a ju c'at u quibej m å' a cha'ic u quibic.
\p 
\v 53 Caj ts'oc u t' ån Jes√∫s yejerob a fariseojo' yejerob y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s, caj bin Jes√∫s, jach ts'icob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer y åjcamsay åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s robob u c'at na'sicob yor quinsac Jes√∫s.
\v 54 M å' ja wirej, caj u ch'uctajob yubejob ba' cu yac Jes√∫s soc u binob u ta'quicob u jo'r Jes√∫s quire' a ba' c'as caj u ya'araj.
\c 12
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u camsic soc m å' u c ånicob ca'tur yac'
\p 
\v 1 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s yejer u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Quire' caj u much'quintob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Jach ti' y ån miles quire' tan u yach' åticob u b åj. Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun ya'aric ti' u cams åwinicob quire' u c'at u y ån tsicbar yejer u cams åwinicob. Rajen caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantej a b åjex ti' u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' soc m å' u tusaricob techex ba'. Soc m å' a c ånicobex quire' a ba' cu tus aric u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo', irej u ts'ac yo'och pan cu sip.
\v 2 Rajen, m å' ja c ånicobex quire' tu cotor ba' cu mucricob mac je' u bin irbir ten mac. Quire' a ba' cu tucric mac, m åna' mac yer, chen je' u yerticobe'.
\v 3 Rajen tu cotor ba' ca mucu'ariquex ya'ab mac cu bin yubic. Quire' a wa ba' ca chan ber ariquex ich a watochex ta junanex ya'ab mac cu bin yertic.
\s1 A mac a y ån ic jach s åjtic
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ10.28‚Äë31)
\p 
\v 4 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïQuin wac techex a mac in jach yaj, m å' a ch'iquex sajaquir ti' a mac a cu bin u quinsiquechex. Quire' ca' bin ts'ocac u quinsiquechex quire' m å' c'ucha'an yor ba' quir u betic techex.
\v 5 A teno' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, quin chen bin in wa'aric techex mac y ån a jach s åjtiquex. Ca' a ch'iquex sajaquir ti' C'uj quire' ca' bin ts'ocac u taquic a cuxtarex c'ucha'an yor u puriquechex ich c'ac'. Jach jaj ra' a jach s åjtex.
\p 
\v 6 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTu cotor mac yer cu conan cinco chan ch'ich' ti' ca'tur chan majan taq'uin. Quire' cu yiric m å' coji'. Chen a chan ch'ich'o' m å' u tubur ti' C'uj, cax turiri'.
\v 7 Rajen m å' a ch'iquex sajaquir quire' jach cojechex a techexo'. M å' necoj, jach ya'ab a chan ch'ich'o'. M å' ja wirej, mun C'uj cu jach yajquintic techex cax yer mun y ån u tsotser a jo'rex.
\s1 A mac a cu toc aric ti' mac: A teno' caj in wacsaj tin wor ti' Cristo
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ10.32‚Äë33; 12.32; 10.19‚Äë20)
\p 
\v 8 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïA teno' quin wac techex a wa mac caj u toc araj caj u yacsaj tu yor ti' u rac'ob. Baxuc a teno' baxuquenechexo'. Quin bin in wa'aric ti' y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj: Aro' caj u yacsaj tu yor ten.
\v 9 A wa mac m å' u c'at ya'aric wa caj u yacsaj tu yor ti' u rac'ob, baxuc a teno' quin bin in wac ti' y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj: Aro' m å' u c'at ya'aric wa caj u yacsaj tu yor uch.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄôA wa mac a cu p'astic ten a tu tuchi'ten C'uj wa cu c'axic yor, je' u jawsa'r ten C'uj. Chen a wa mac a cu p'astic u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj, m å' ju bin jawsa'bir u si'pir ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄôCax cu bin u puriquechex  åc åtan u ts'urir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Cax ich gobernador cax ich presidente quire' caj a wacsex ta wor ten. M å' ja chen tucriquex bic tabar ca bin a nunquiquex ti'. M å' ja tucriquex a ba' ca bin waquex ti'.
\v 12 A ray u q'uinino' u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj, je' u yac techex ba' y ån a waquex ti'.
\s1 Qui' irej m å' u jach t'aj år a taq'uinex yejer a ba'taquex
\p 
\v 13 Turi' mac ich a pimo' caj u puraj u t' ån ti' Jes√∫s, caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, chan arej ti' in sucu'un ca' u ch åc j åse ten u ba'tac in tetob a caj u p' åt åtenob caj quimin in tetob.
\p 
\v 14 Caj u nunca Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïArej ten mac caj u tetajen ca' in wa'arej bic tabar a j åsiquex u ba'tac a tetex? Rajen m å' in wac techi'.
\p 
\v 15 Rajen Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantex a b åj soc m å' a yajquintiquex a taq'uinex, bayiri' ti' a ba'taquex xan. M å' ja wirej, cax a mac ney ån u taq'uin yejer u ba'tac, aro' m å' u ya'aric wa je' u cuxtar ya'ab q'uin.
\p 
\v 16 Soc u c ånicob a ba' caj u camsaj sam, rajen caj u ya'araj a je'ra':
\p ‚ÄïA ucho' ti' y ån mac jach neya'ab u taq'uin quire' u ru'um caj u nets'ajaj u wich u p åc'ar.
\v 17 A xibo' a mac jach neya'ab u taq'uin caj u tucraj ich yor caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúBa' quin bin in betej baje'rer quire' m å' tu quin wacsic in ts' åpquin tin wo'och quire' jach ya'ab ten?‚Äù
\v 18 Caj ts'oc u tucric a ba' cu bin u betic caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúIn wer ba' quin bin in betic. Je' in r åc pa'ic tu quin wacsic u canche'ir in woch ca' in jach cochquintej u jer soc jach carem. Soc ti' quin bin in wacsic in woch yejer a ba' y ån ten.‚Äù
\v 19 A mac jach neya'ab u taq'uin caj u tucraj tu yor, tan ya'aric ti' u w åc' ås b åjiri': ‚ÄúToc y ån ba' a c'at ti' ya'ab yaxq'uin. Tsire'ej a beyaj chen jes a b åj janen uc'urnen xan manen soc qui' a wor.‚Äù
\v 20 M å' toy ts'ocac u t' ån caj ara'b ten C'uj: ‚ÄúJach chich a jo'r, a je' ac'bira' c'uchij tu q'uinin a quimin. Tu cotor a ba' a caj a ric'saj mac cu bin u ch'ic?‚Äù
\v 21 Baxuc u bin u betic tu cotor mac a cu tucric u nono'j b åjiri' yejer u ba'tac a mun u q'uinin cuxa'an ich yoc'ocab. Chen m å' tu betaj a ba' cu bin u qui'quintic yor C'uj. Chen  åc åtan tu wich C'uj jach otsir.
\s1 C'uj cu c ånantic u pararob
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ6.25‚Äë34)
\p 
\v 22 Caj ts'oc u camsic Jes√∫s a pimo' caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïRajen quin wac tech: M å' ja y ån tucriquex ba' ca bin a jantex quir a cuxtarex. M å' ja y ån tucriquex a ba' ca bin a buquintex.
\v 23 M å' ja wirej, jach no'j a cuxtarex chen a wochex m å' no'ji'. Baxuc xan, jach no'j a winquirirex chen a noq'uex m å' no'ji'.
\v 24 Qui' tucrex a ba' quin bin in wac techex. A c'awojo', m å' ju p åq'uic ba' m å' ju jaq'uic yo'och, m å' c'ucha'an yor u ric'sic yoch ich c'anche' soc ca' bin c'uchur tu q'uinin y ån yoch. Chen m å' ju wich åj år quire' C'uj cu jansic. M å' wa jach manan cojechex a ch'ich'o', m å' necoji'.
\p 
\v 25 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïCax ya'ab ca tucriquex u sats' år a baquerex, m å' ju sats' år a baquerex, m å' chichin.
\v 26 A werechex m å' c'ucha'an a worex a s åts'iquex a baquerex quire' m å' neno'j aro'. Rajen m å' ba'wir ca jach tucriquex a ba' ca bin a jantex, a ba' ca bin a wuq'uex, a ba' ca bin a buquintiquex.
\p 
\v 27 ‚ÄôQui' tucriquex a ba' quin bin in wac techex. Caj a wirajex bic tabar u ch'ijir u top' ch åcm ånche' a jach tsoy u top'. Ca wiric wa cu beyaj, m å' ju c'uch. A teno' quin wac techex. A rey Salom√≥no', u buquim ån u noc' uch, jach tsoy chen m å' jach quet tsoyir yejer ch åcm ån che', cax rey.
\v 28 A C'ujo' cu ch'isic u top'che' a ti' y ån ich c'ax soc tsoy u top', chen tabar u ts'u'ts'ur u top'. Cu c'uchur mac cu maric quir u toquic ich c'ac'. Wa baxuc a C'ujo' cu c ånantic u top'che'. Baxuc a C'ujo' cu c ånantic techex, cax ca tucriquex m å' u c ånantiquechex.
\v 29 Quire' a mac yer c ånanta'an ten C'uj, m å' u y ån tucric a ba' cu bin u jantej. Baxuc a ba' cu bin yuq'uej. Baxuc m å' u y ån xaca'an tucur.
\v 30 Chen a mac a m å' yerob C'uj cu tus tucricob aro' quire' xaca'an u tucricob ba' cu bin u jantejob. Baxuc a ba' cu bin u yuc'urob chen ic Tet C'uj, jach yer a ba' a c'atex.
\v 31 Barej c'ajtex a ba' jach no'j tu cu bin u reyintic C'uj. Wa ca y ån c åxtiquex aro', tu cotor a ba' a c'atex, je' u ts'ic techex C'uj. Cax a noc', cax a woch, cax a wuc'ur.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic u cams åwinicob ca' u ric'sej a ba' jach co'oj soc y ån ich ca'anan
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ6.19‚Äë21)
\p 
\v 32 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' ja ch'iquex sajaquir quire' cax m å' pimechex. M å' ja wirej, jach tsoy caj u tucraj C'uj u yacsiquechex a reyintex tu cu reyintej C'uj.
\v 33 C ånex a ba'taquex soc y ån techex ca' a ts'ic ti' a mac otsirch åjij. Wa baxuc ca betiquex, aro' irej tan a ric'siquex a ba' jach co'oj soc y ån techex ich ca'anan. A ti taro' m å' u xupur quire' munt q'uin ti' y åno'. Quire' ti taro' m åna' mac cu yocar u muc u ac'ric. Baxuc a taro' m å' ju jantic c' åm ås.
\v 34 M å' ja wirej, a tu y ån a ric'sm ånex jach co'oj ti' ca pachiquex a bin xan.
\s1 Toc qui' pajenex ca' bin uruc Cristo
\p 
\v 35 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob bic tabar u q'uinin ca' bin uruc:
\p ‚ÄïToc pajenex ca' bin urquen ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, an ten bic mac cu c ånanticob yatoch u ts'urir quire'.
\v 36 Bin u ts'urir, bin yiric u ch'ic u rac' mac. U winiquirob a ts'uro' u toc buquim ånob u noc'. Toc t' åba'an u quib ca' bin c'uchuc t' ånbir. Seb cu q'ueyic u jor soc u yacsicob ti'.
\v 37 Qui' yor a mac a cu toc pajicob u tar u jach ts'urirob ca' bin uruc. Wa tu pajicob ca' bin uruc a ray u quinino', quin bin in wa'aric ti'ob ca' curacob tu jan ånob. Quin ts'ab åc ti'ob quir u jan ånob.
\v 38 Techex jach qui' a worex wa tan a toc pajiquenex ca' bin urquen. Cax chumuc ac'bir. Ca' bin urquen, cax wa tan u sastar ca' bin urquen.
\v 39 Uyex ba' quin waquex tech. Jaj ixt åcoj wa ra' u winquirir yatoch yer ixt åcoj u q'uinin u tar y åjac'ray åjir ba'tac caj u toc pajaj ca'ch soc m å' u cha'ic yocar u yac'ric.
\v 40 Baxuc techex ca' a toc pajiquex quire' wa ra' u q'uinin quin wu'ur m å' tan a tucriquex in wu'ur. A teno' a mac tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj baxuquenechexo'.
\s1 A winico' a m å' u quibic u t' ån u ts'urir baxuc a winico' a cu quibic u t' ån u ts'urir xan
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.45‚Äë51)
\p 
\v 41 Caj ya'araj Pedro:
\p ‚ÄïWa chen ti' tenob caj a wa'araj sam wa ti' tu cotor mac xan.
\p 
\v 42 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïCa' a c ånex u ca' ts'urir a mac jach t'aj, a cu quib u t' ån u Jach Ts'urir ts'a'b u c ånantej a mac ti' y ån tu yatoch. Tan u ts'ic ti'ob u jan ånob ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u jan ånob u winiquirob u Jach Ts'urir.
\v 43 Rajen u ca' ts'urir qui' yor quire' irir ten u Jach Ts'urir tu qui' quibaj u t' ån caj ur tu yatoch.
\p 
\v 44 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJach taj quin wa'aric techex. Je' u ts'ab år u c ånantej tu cotor ba' a ti' y ån ich yatoch.
\v 45 Chen wa ju ca' ts'urir cu tucric tu yor tan ya'aric: ‚ÄúIn jach ts'urir ama'an cu c'uch, tin t' ån.‚Äù Rajen tu y ånxchun u j åts'icob u winiquirob cax xib cax xquic. Tan u nejan ån tan u ne'uc'ur xan, tan u carch åj xan.
\v 46 U jach ts'urir je' u yu'ur tu q'uinin m å' tan u pajic u ca' ts'urir quire' m å' tu ya'araj ti' ber ca' bin uruc. Cu bin ts'ab år u muc'yaj ten u jach ts'urir. Quet cu bin u muc'yaj yejer a mac a m å' yerob C'uj quire' m å' tu betaj a ba' u c'at u jach ts'urir.
\p 
\v 47 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïChen a winico' a yer a ba' u c'at u jach ts'urir chen m å' tu quibaj a ba' ara'b ti'. Rajen ca' bin uruc u jach ts'urir ara' u q'uinin m å' tan u pajic. Je' u bin ts'ab år u muc'yaj. Jach yaj cu bin muc'yaj.
\v 48 Chen a winico', quire' caj u betaj ba', rajen bin u jats' år u pach ten u jach ts'urir cax m å' yer a ba' u c'at u jach ts'urir ca'ch. Barej m å' neyaj cu bin j åts'bir u pach ten u jach ts'urir. Ca' bin u ts'ab år u beyaj ten u jach ts'urir ti' u c'urew y ån u toc r åc betic. Cax m å' ya'ab u beyaj y ån u r åc ts'ocsic. Cax ya'ab u beyaj u ts'ab år ti' ten u ts'urir cu pajic u ts'ocsic ti' cax ya'ab ti'.
\s1 Jes√∫s m å' u bin u p'eri'quintic yor yejer mac ich yoc'ocab
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ10.34‚Äë36)
\p 
\v 49 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïQuire' taren a teno' ich yoc'ocab cu bin u p'ujur yor mac aro' irej c'ac'. An bic in c'at toc ts'aca'an in beyaj ich yoc'ocab.
\v 50 Chen y ån in muc'yaj ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, baxuc y ån in quimin soc toy ts'aca'an in beyaj. Bic jach yaj in wor hasta ca' bin y ånxchunuc in muc'yaj.
\v 51 Quire' taren ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, ca bin a tucrex a mac ti' y ån ich yoc'ocab m å' u bin u ts'ictarob. Chen a teno' quin wac techex m å' u bin sistar yor yejer u rac'ob mac cu bin u r åc pacran ts'ictarob.
\v 52 Cu y ånxchun baje'rer hasta cu xur t' ån wa ti' y ån cinco winic ich yatoch u tet. A m åna' u nupo' cu bin u ts'ictarob yejer a ca'turo'. A ca'turo' cu bin u ts'ictarob yejer a m åna' u nupo'.
\v 53 U tet cu ts'ictar yejer u parar xan. U parar cu ts'ictar yejer u tet xan. U n å' cu ts'ictar yejer xquic u parar. A xquico' u parar cu ts'ictar yejer u n å'. Yixquit cu ts'ictar yejer yixquit. Cu pacran ts'ictar yejer yixquit.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ya'aric ti' a pimo'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ16.1‚Äë4; Mr.‚ÄØ8.11‚Äë13)
\p 
\v 54 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïCa wiriquex u nacar u muyarir tu cu bin q'uin ca waquex je' u tar ya'rire'. Jach jaj cu tar ya'rir.
\v 55 Wa cu tar yic'ar ich nojar ca waquex bin u ca' ch åc årch åj år q'uin. Jach taj cu ch åc åch åj år q'uin.
\v 56 Ca chen tusariquex ca' bin a wirex biquira' a ca'anano'. Baxuc a ru'umo' a werex wa cu tar ja' wa cu bin ch åc åwch åj år. Biquinin m å' a werex ba' u c'at ya'arej a ba' quin betic baje'rer?
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ya'aric: Ca' a sisquintic yor a mac a cu p'actiquechex
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ5.25‚Äë26)
\p 
\v 57 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin m å' a b åjiri'ex ca tucriquex ta worex a ba' ca bin a betiquex?
\p 
\v 58 Caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïWa y ån mac cu bin u puriquech  åc åtan ich juez quir yiric wa y ån a bo'or ti'. Joq'uen sisquintej yor soc m å' u bin u puriquech ich juez. Wa m å' a bin a sisquintej yor, je' u bin u puriquech ich juez. Caj ts'oc yiric y ån a si'pir cu bin u c'ubiquech tu cu ma'c år winic.
\v 59 A teno' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, quin wac tech: M å' u bin u cha'ic tech hasta ca r åc bo'otic a bo'or.
\c 13
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj ca' u c'axej yor a pimo'
\p 
\v 1 Ra'iri' u q'uinin ti' y ån mac ich Jes√∫s. M å' ja wirej, tarob u toc arob ti' Jes√∫s a ba' u ber ti' u winiquirob jud√≠o a cu tarob ich u ru'umin Galilea. Quire' quinsa'b ten u soldado, Pilato, tu cu quinsicob wac åx quir u ts'ic ti' C'uj. Quire' ara'b ten Pilato.
\v 2 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti'ob, caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïCa tucriquex wa jach c'asob a cu tarob ich u ru'umin Galilea? Rajen quinsa'b tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj. Barej u rac'ob a cu tarob ich u ru'umin Galilea m å' nec'asi'.
\v 3 Rajen quin wac techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, m å' taj a ba' ca waquex. Baxuc techex wa m å' tan a c'axiquex a worex caj a p' åtex a c'aso' je' a r åc quiminex xan, irej ti'ob ca' quinsa'b.
\v 4 C'aj wa techex a mac pets'ta'b ten u tunichir tu ts' åpa'an? B åyt åc tu y ån u ts' åpa'an tunich ca'anan u c'aba' Silo√© soc nach cu yiric. Caj pets'ta'bob dieciocho. Arex ten wa jach c'asob rajen pets'ta'b chen a mac ich u cajar Jerusal√©n m å' nec'asobi'?
\v 5 Rajen quin wac techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, m å' taj a ba' ca waquex. Baxuc techex wa m å' tan a c'axiquex a worex ca' a p' åtex a c'aso'. Je' a r åc quiminex xan, irej caj pets'abob.
\s1 Quir u camsic ti' u p åc'ar higuera a m å' ju wich ånc år
\p 
\v 6 Jes√∫s caj u camsaj baxuc a je' t' åna' soc tabar u c'axicob u yorob. Rajen caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïTi' y ån u p åc'ar higuera ich corir u yaq'uir uva mac. Caj bin yiric wa y ån u wich. M å' tu yira u wich.
\v 7 Rajen ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, caj ara'b ten a mac y ånin u cor ti' a mac a cu c ånantic u cor: ‚ÄúY ån tres yaxq'uin, rajra' quin tar in wiric wa y ån u wich higuera. Chen m å' in wiric u wich. Toc ch' åquej u che'er, ba'wir cu c' ånic u ru'umin?‚Äù
\v 8 Caj ara'b ten a mac a cu c ånantic u cor: ‚ÄúTsire'ej, Jach Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, soc in juptic u ru'umin chen a je' yaxq'uina' quin bin in purej u ta' tsimin soc u ne'ichanc år.
\v 9 Jaj ixt åcoj, je' u wichanc år ca' bin tac tu q'uinin u wich ånc år. Jach Ts'urir, wa m å' u wichanc år, arej in ch' åquej.‚Äù
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a p'ux u bin xquic u q'uinin u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o
\p 
\v 10 U q'uinin u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o, Jes√∫s caj u camsaj u winiquirob jud√≠o tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj.
\v 11 Ti' y ån tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj uch xquic, a p'ux u bin, y ån dieciocho yaxq'uin caj u c ånaj u yajir. Quire' aca'an c'ac'as quisin ti', rajen m å' u tajtar u pach.
\v 12 Rajen Jes√∫s caj yiraj caj u t' åna caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïXquic ‚Äïquen‚Äï, toc jaw a yajir.
\p 
\v 13 Caj u ts'anc' åbtaj seb caj tajij xquic a p'ux u bin cuch. Caj u y ånxchun ya'aric ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, caj a jawsajen.
\p 
\v 14 Chen u jach ts'urir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o caj ts'iquij quire' yiraj u jawsic Jes√∫s xquic u q'uinin cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Rajen caj ya'araj ti' a mac ti' y ånob. Y ån seis u q'uinin quir a beyajex techex. A seis u q'uinino' tsoy a tarex quir a jawsic a yajirex, chen m å' ra' u q'uinin baje'ra'.
\p 
\v 15 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïCa' yarir a wac' a techexo' ca tus ets'iquex a c'ujintiquex C'uj. M å' wa ti' y ån mac a tera' a m å' ju siptic y år åc' wac åx yejer y år åc' tsimin tu cu jansic quir u ts'ic u yuc'ur cax ra' u q'uinin caj u jesob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o? Jach taj ca siptiquex ti' quir a ts'ic yo'och ja'.
\v 16 Irex a je' xquica', u parar u ca' parar Abraham uch. Y ån dieciocho yaxq'uin caj yajij quire' quisin. Jach jaj y ån u bin sipta'bir u yajirir cax tu q'uinin caj u jesob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\p 
\v 17 M å' toy ts'ocac Jes√∫s u tsicbar ti'ob tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj a mac tu p åc'ob u pach Jes√∫s caj u ch'ajob suraquir. Chen u jerob u rac'ob caj qui'jij yorob quire' yirob carem u beyajob Jes√∫s a caj u betaj ti' a xquico'.
\s1 Quir u camsic ti' u yijir mostaza
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.31‚Äë32; Mr.‚ÄØ4.30‚Äë32)
\p 
\v 18 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïBin in ca' in camsic techex soc a werex cu bin u reyintic C'uj soc a p'erquintiquex.
\v 19 Aro' irej u yijir mostaza jach mijin. Barej cu ch'ic u p åq'uic ich u chan cor. Cu ch'ijire' cu majan xit'ir u c' åbir. A ch'ich'o' cu tar u c' åxic u c'u' ich u c' åbir.
\s1 Quir u camsic ts'ac a cu sip'o'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.33)
\p 
\v 20 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s caj u ca' a'araj:
\p ‚ÄïBin in ca' in p'eri'quintic u ru'umin tu cu bin u reyintej C'uj.
\v 21 An bic ten cu sip' yoch pan wa cu puric ts'ac. M åna' u nup u puric u tenin u ts'ac ich harina cu ts'ocar u puric u ts'ac cu r åc sip' tu cotor.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic a pimo': P'is a b åj soc a wocarex tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj cax c'ax u jor tu cu yocar
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ7.13‚Äë14, 21‚Äë23)
\p 
\v 22 Ti' toy cu bin Jes√∫s ich u berir Jerusal√©n. Ti' cu man ich u chan cajar baxuc ich u yajaw cajar a ti' y ån ich bej. Ti' cu camsic mac ti taro'.
\v 23 Y ån mac tu c'ataj ti':
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, arej ten wa ya'ab cu bin tacbir ten C'uj wa m å' ya'ab cu bin tacbir?
\p Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïMun cu bin tacbir?
\v 24 Jach p'isex a b åjex quir a wocarex tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj cax yaj tu ca wocarex. Qui' tucriquex quire' m å' ya'ab cu bin yocar ti'.
\v 25 M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin a mac y ånin yatoch cu bin u c' åric u jor. Ca' bin taquechex ich tancab ca' bin a y ån t' åniquex: ‚ÄúQ'ueyej in jo'rob, Jaj Ts'urir, quir in wocarob.‚Äù Chen a ti'o' cu bin u nunquic: ‚ÄúM å' in wer maquechex, m å' in wer tub a tarex.‚Äù
\v 26 Ra'iri' u q'uinin ca bin a y ånxchun a wa'ariquex: ‚ÄúP'eri' ic jan ån uch, p'eri' ij cuc'ur xan uch. Baxuc caj a camsajenob tu berir uch tu c åja'anenob.‚Äù
\v 27 A Jaj Ts'uro' ca' bin u nunquej: ‚ÄúCaj in wa'araj ca'ch m å' in wer tub a tarex. Ca' xiquechex tu cotorex quire' nanex a manex ta c'asirex.‚Äù
\v 28 Ca' bin a wac'tiquex a b åj ca' bin a j åch'iquex a coj quire' ts'iquechex quire' caj a wiraj m å' u yacsiquechex. Quire' caj a wiraj u yacsa'rob Abraham yejer Isaac yejer Jacob yejer tu cotor y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj. Chen tancab p'atechex tu cu yocarob u reyinticob C'uj.
\v 29 A winico' tar cu bin tarob tu cu tar q'uin. Baxuc cu bin tarob tu cu bin ic yum. Baxuc cu bin tarob x åman ca'anan. Baxuc cu bin tarob ich nojar. Ti' cu r åc binob ich ca'anan tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. Ti' cu bin cutarob u jan ånob.
\v 30 U'yex ba' quin wac, y ån mac a tera' m å' no'ji' chen ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj jach no'j. Y ån mac a tera' jach no'j baje'ra' ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin tu cu reyintic C'uj. M å' no'ji'.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu toc aric: Tabar in quinsa' ich u cajar Jerusal√©n
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ23.37‚Äë39)
\p 
\v 31 Jes√∫s caj ts'oc u camsicob a ba' caj u ya'araj sam. Caj c'uchij m å' ya'ab u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo'. Caj ya'arob ti':
\p ‚ÄïCa' xiquech quire' Herodes u c'at u quinsiquech.
\p 
\v 32 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA Herodeso', raji' cu tusaric mac. Joq'uenex a wa'ariquex ti': ‚ÄúChen te' y ånena', m å' ya'ab u q'uinin soc in y ån joc'sic a mac aca'an c'ac'as quisin ti'. Soc in y ån jawsic u yajir mac xan. Tabar in ts'ocsic in beyaj a tera'.‚Äù
\v 33 Arex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, ti' Herodes a ba' quin betic baje'ra'. Baxuc xan in betic saman. Baxuc y ån in betic ca'bej xan hasta quin c'uchur ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Quire' ich u cajar Jerusal√©n tiri' cu quinsicob y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj, m å' a tera' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 34 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' ti' c åja'anechex ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Ca quinsiquex y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj uch. Ca r åc ch'iniquex u jo'rob a mac tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj ti' techex. Ya'ab u tenin in c'at in much'quintic techex an ten bic cax cu juquintic yar soc u c ånantic. Chen techex m å' ja c'atex in much'quintiquechex baxuc aro'.
\v 35 U'yex ba' quin wac techex. Caj in toc p' åtechex ta junanex. Quin wac techex m å' a bin a wiriquenex hasta cu c'uchur tu q'uinin a ray u q'uinino' ca waquex: ‚ÄúCa' ij c'ujintej a je' xiba' a cu tar quire' tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj.‚Äù
\c 14
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a chup u b åq'uero'
\p 
\v 1 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin caj bin tu jan ån Jes√∫s ich yatoch u ts'urir u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' quire' p åybir. Ray u q'uinin u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o. A ju yet jan ånob tan u ch'ucticob a ba' cu bin u betej Jes√∫s.
\v 2 Ti' y ån xib xan tu y ån Jes√∫s. A y ån u yajir chup u b åq'uer.
\v 3 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob a fariseojo' yejer y åjcamsay åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s a ju yet jan ånob, caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBa' cu ya'aric tu ts'iba'an u t' ån Mois√©s? Cu cha'ic wa jic jawsic u yajir mac wa m å' u cha'ic ic jawsic mac u q'uinin quir a jesiquex a b åjex?
\p 
\v 4 M åna' mac caj u nuncaj a ba' c'ata'b ti'ob. Rajen Jes√∫s caj u m åchaj u c' åb caj u jawsaj u yajir. Caj ts'oc u jaware' caj u cha' u bin a mac jawsa'b.
\v 5 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob a mac r åc ti' y ånob ich yatoch u ts'urir a fariseojo':
\p ‚ÄïWa y ån techex a w år åc' chan tsimin cax a w år åc' wac åx ton, wa pitc' åjij caj but' ich u jorir ru'um ich yic' ja', m å' wa seb ca jariquex cax u q'uinin a jesiquex a b åjex?
\p 
\v 6 M å' c'ucha'an yor u nunquicob ti' Jes√∫s.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u camsaj a mac ti' y ånob ich yatoch u ts'urir a fariseojo'
\p 
\v 7 Jes√∫s caj yiraj bic cu teticob u cutanob a payob tu jan ånob. U c'at u cutarob soc jach no'j tu cura'anob. Rajen Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄïWa ju p åyiquechex mac quir a jan ånex tu cu bin u ch'ic u rac'. M å' ja y ån cutarex tu cu cutar a mac jach no'j. Quire' wa ti' ca cutarex jaj ixt åcoj wa cu tar a mac jach no'jo' quire' techex m å' jach no'jechexi'.
\v 9 Wa ti' cura'anech cu bin tar yac tech a mac tu pay a jan ån: ‚ÄúChan joq'uen a techo' ‚Äïquij‚Äï ca' xiquech ti' taro' soc in wacsic a je' xiba' tera' ta cutan.‚Äù Rajen ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, ca' bin a ch'ic suraquir tu ca bin a cutar tu m å' no'j a cutan.
\v 10 Chen wa cu payiquechex mac quir a jan ånex tu cu bin u ch'ic u rac'. Tar a cutarex tu cura'an a mac m å' no'jo' soc wa cu tar a mac tu p åyechex cu bin yac techex: ‚ÄúIn jach yajech ‚Äïquij‚Äï, cojen a cutar tu jach no'j.‚Äù Ra'iri' u q'uinin cu bin s åjta'birechex ten a mac cura'anob jan ånob yejerech.
\v 11 M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, a mac a cu tucric: Jach no'jen, a C'ujo' cu bin yiric m å' no'ji'. A mac a cu tucric: M å' no'jen a teno', a C'ujo' cu bin yiric jach no'j.
\p 
\v 12 Jes√∫s ti' toy cu tsicbar ti' a mac caj u p åy tu jan ån. Caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïBarej ca p åyic mac quir u jan ånob cax cu qui' jan ånob? M å' ja chen p åyic a mac a jach yaj. M å' ja p åyic a wits'inob, m å' ja p åyic a b åjob, m å' ja p åyic a wet cajar a ney ån u taq'uinob quire' baxuc xan c'ucha'an yorob u w åc' ås p åyiquech ta jan ån xan. Baxuc aro' tu w åc' ås botechob.
\v 13 Chen wa ca p åyiquex mac quir u qui' jananob. P åyej a mac otsij, baxuc p åyej a xon c'upa'an yoco' wa ju c' åb xan. Baxuc p åyej a mech yoque'. Baxuc p åyej a ch'op u wiche' xan.
\v 14 Wa baxuc ca p åyicob jan ånob a C'ujo' cu bin u qui'quintic a wor quire' a ra' winiquirob m å' cucha'an yorob u w åc' ås bo'otiquech tu ta payajexob. Chen C'uj cu bin u bo'otiquex ca' bin riq'uic a mac quimeno' a mac cur åjij an ten bic C'uj u c'at uch.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' a mac a m å' u c'at u tarob u qui' jan ånob
\p 
\v 15 A mac a p'eri' curic jan ånob a caj u yubaj ya'aric Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJach qui' yorob a mac a cu bin jan ånob tu q'uinin cu bin u reyinticob C'uj a payob jan ånob. Ba'iri' cu c'uchur quir u jan ån.
\p 
\v 16 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïY ån mac caj u toc p åyaj ya'ab ca' tac u qui' jan ånob. Tar cu bin p åybir tu yatochob.
\v 17 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin toc ts'aca'an yo'och caj tuchi'ta'b ca' u t' ånej a mac payob jan ånob uch. U c'urewob a tu p åyaj ti' jan ånob: ‚ÄúCojen ‚Äïquij‚Äï, toc ts'aca'an a wochex.‚Äù
\v 18 Chen tu cotor a payob ca'ch caj u y ånxchun ya'arob. Biquinin m å' c'ucha'an yor u binob, a tu y ån c'uch, caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúA teno' caj in m ånaj in ru'um, y ån in bin in wiric biquira'. Toc chan arej ti' a jach ts'urir m å' c'ucha'an in wor in tar. Arej u jawsen a Jaj Ts'urir.‚Äù
\v 19 Caj c'uchij u c'urew ich u jer a mac payob ca'ch. Raji' caj u ya'araj: ‚ÄúA teno' caj in m ånaj cinco ca' ca'tur in w år åc' wac åx a ton, a cu jitic ba'. Bin in ca' in wirej wa cu beyajob. Toc chan arej ti' a Jach Ts'urir m å' c'ucha'an in wor in tar. Arej u jawsen.‚Äù
\v 20 Caj c'uchij u c'urew ich u jer a mac payob uch. Raji' caj u ya'araj: ‚ÄúM å' jin tar ‚Äïquij‚Äï, quire' tant in ch'ic in rac', rajen m å' c'ucha'an in wor in tar.‚Äù
\v 21 Caj ts'oc yu'ur u c'urew caj ya'araj ti' u Jach Ts'urir a ba' caj u ya'araj a mac payob uch. Rajen caj ts'iquij caj ya'araj ti' u c'urew: ‚ÄúSebquintej a bin ich tanbej ich u cajar, baxuc ich u berir u cor mac. Ca' a r åc p åyic a mac otsir. Baxuc a mac xonc'ub yoc wa c' åb. Baxuc a mac mech. Baxuc a mech yoque'. Baxuc a ch'op u wicho' xan.‚Äù
\v 22 Caj ts'oc u betic aro' caj w åc' ås bin ich u Jach Ts'urir caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúIn Jach Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, caj in toc betaj a ba' caj a wa'araj. Ti' toy y ån, m å' chupuc a watoch.‚Äù
\v 23 Caj ya'araj ti' u c'urew: ‚ÄúJoq'uen, r åc p åyej ich tancab u cajar cax tu cu manob ich bej. Chich p åyob ca' tacob tu jan ånob soc u r åc chupur in watoch.‚Äù
\v 24 Caj ya'araj u Jach Ts'urir: ‚ÄúTaj quin wac tech a mac a caj in y ån p åyajob, m å' ju bin u janticob in woch. A toc ts'aca'an, quire' m å' in cha'ic u tarob.‚Äù
\s1 A mac a c'ucha'an yor u say år tu pach Jes√∫s quir u c ånic u t' ån
\p 
\v 25 P'eri' cu binob Jes√∫s yejer a pimob. Caj u sut u b åj caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p 
\v 26 ‚ÄïWa mac ich techex u c'at u tar tin pach quir u c ånic in t' ån. Wa ju jach yajquintic u tet yejer u n å' yejer u rac' yejer u parar yejer u b åjob. Cax u w åc' ås b åjiri' chen m å' ten u qui' yajquintic ten ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, aro' m å' c'ucha'an yor u tar u c ånic in t' ån.
\v 27 Wa mac ich techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, m å' u c'at u muc'yaj, m å' u c'at u quimin, cax ich cruz wa ra' u c'at C'uj. Arej m å' c'ucha'an yor u tar u c ånic in t' ån.
\v 28 Wa mac ich techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, u c'at u ts' åpquintic tunich soc u c' åxic yatoch jach carem. Cu y ån tucric mun u bo'orir, m å' toy y ånchun u beyaj soc yiric wa c'ucha'an u ts'ocsic ti'.
\v 29 Wa m å' tu qui' tucraj mun u bo'orir quir u ts'ocsic ca' bin u ts' åpquintic tunich quir u nacsic u jo'r ca'anan. Ca' bin yirej m å' c'ucha'an yor u ts'ocsic. Tu cotor mac cu bin tar u che'ticob quire' caj u yirob m å' c'ucha'an yor u ts'ocsic.
\v 30 Cu bin u ya'aricob: ‚ÄúA je' xibo' caj u y ånxchun cu chen ts' åpquintic tunich m å' c'ucha'an yor u ts'ocsic.‚Äù Baxuc a mac a cu tar u c ånic in t' ån. Cu y ån tucric mun u bo'orir wa toy y ånxchun u tar tin pach.
\p 
\v 31 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a pimo', a mac tarob tu pach:
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc a reyo' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, wa cu bin u ts'ictar yejer u yet reyir quire' p'acta'b. Cu y ån qui' tucric wa c'ucha'an yor ti' quir u nup'ic yejer diez mil, cax yet reyir y ån veinte mil soldado.
\v 32 Wa cu yiric m å' c'ucha'an yor ti' yet reyir. Ti' toy y ån yet reyir nach, tan u tar quinsbir. Je' u tuchi'tic mac quir u sisquintic yor soc cu p'eri'quinticob yor soc m å' ju tar quir u quinsa'.
\v 33 A mac a cu bin u betic a ba' jach no'j, y ån u qui' tucric wa c'ucha'an yor u ts'ocsic. Baxuc techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, m å' c'ucha'an a worex a tar a c åniquex in t' ån, wa m å' a c'at a p' åtiquex tu cotor a ba' y ån techex.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' a xa'ano' a m å' tabta'ani'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ5.13; Mr.‚ÄØ9.50)
\p 
\v 34 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïA wochexo', m å' qui' wa m å' tabta'an yejer xa'an. Chen wa cu ruc'ur u xa'anin. Ba' y ån ic betej soc u w åc' ås tar u xa'anin?
\v 35 A ruc'a'an u xa'anino', m å' ba'wir ti', m å' ti' a cor quir u ch'isej ba' an ten bic u ta' tsimin, ca chen joc'sic a puric nach. Baxuc techex wa m å' a quibiquex in t' ån cu bin u joc'sic u puric techex. Qui' u'yex a ba' quin wac.
\c 15
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' t åm ån yuc a sat åro'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ18.10‚Äë14)
\p 
\v 1 Turi' u q'uinin caj tarob a mac cu c' åmicob u taq'uin gobierno yejer a mac y ån u si'pirob. Caj u much'quintajob u b åj ich Jes√∫s.
\v 2 Rajen u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer y åjcamsay åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïA je' xiba' cu man yejer a mac y ån u si'pirob, cu jan ån yejerob xan.
\p 
\v 3 Rajen Jes√∫s caj u camsaj baxuc a je'ra':
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄïWa turiri' techex y ån cien a w år åc' t åm ån yuc, cu sat år turiri', m å' wa cu jamach p' åtic u y år åc' t åm ån yuc a noventa y nueve tu cu jan ånob ca' xic u c åxtej a sa'ataro'? Cu qui' c åxtic hasta cu yiric.
\v 5 Caj ts'oc yiric caj qui'jij yor rajen caj u c'ocha.
\v 6 Ca' bin c'uchuc ich yatoch caj u p åyaj a mac u jach yajob yejer u yet cajarob caj ya'araj ti'ob: ‚ÄúCa' ij qui'quintej ij cor quire' caj in wiraj in w år åc' t åm ån yuc a cu sat år uch.‚Äù
\v 7 Baxuc xan, rajen quin wac techex: Jach manan cu bin u qui' tar yor C'uj ich ca'anan yejer y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj quire' caj u yiraj turi' caj u c'axaj yor, caj u p' åtaj u man tu c'asir. Cax m å' ba'wir aro' a noventa y nueve quir u c'axic yorob soc u p' åticob u c'asirob quire' jach tsoyob.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' taq'uin a sat åro'
\p 
\v 8 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa ti' y ån xquic a y ån diez u s åc taq'uin wa cu s åtic u taq'uin turiri'. Cu t' åbic u quib quir u mistic yatoch soc u qui' c åxtic u taq'uin hasta cu yiric. Jach taj cu bin u qui' c åxtic hasta cu yiric.
\v 9 Barej caj u yiraj u taq'uin cu p åyic a mac u jach yajob. Baxuc u yet cajarob, caj ya'araj ti'ob: ‚ÄúCa' ij qui'quintic ij cor quire' caj in wiraj in taq'uin a tin s åtaj uch.‚Äù
\v 10 Quin wac techex baxuc xan qui' yorob y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj ber cu yiricob u c'axic yor mac. Caj u p' åtaj u man tu c'asir, cax turiri'.
\s1 Jes√∫s camsic ti' u parar a cu sataro'
\p 
\v 11 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïTi' y ån turiri' xib y ån ca'tur u parar.
\v 12 A its'inbir u parar caj ya'araj ti' u tet: ‚ÄúTet ‚Äïquij‚Äï, j åse ten a ba' ca bin a p' åtej wa ca quimin.‚Äù Rajen u tet caj u j åsaj ti'ob u pararob a ba' cu bin u p' åtic ti'ob.
\v 13 Caj manij m å' ya'ab u q'uinin, u parar a its'inbiro' caj u r åc maraj u ba'tac caj u p' åtaj u tet caj bin ich tanxer u cajar nach. Caj u r åc xup u taq'uin tu cu man tu c'asir.
\v 14 Caj ts'oc u r åc xupic u taq'uin caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u tar wi'ij tu ru'umin. Caj u y ånxchun u masic otsir.
\v 15 Caj tar u chich c'ataj u beyaj a ti' c åja'an ich u ru'umin. Raji' caj u ts'aj u beyaj ich u cor quir u jansic y år åc' q'uec'an.
\v 16 Cu jach pachtic u najch åj år yejer yoch q'uec'an a cu ts'ab år ti'. Quire' m å' u ts'ab år ti' a mac a cu c ånanticob q'uec'an.
\v 17 Chen caj u c'axaj u tucur caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúMun u c'urew in tet cu beyaj. Toc y ån yo'och ya'ab. M å' u r åc janticob. Chen a teno' tan in quimin yejer wi'ij.
\v 18 Bin in ca' sut ich in tet ca' bin in wac ti' in tet: Tet, quen, a teno' y ån in si'pir ti' C'uj. Baxuc tech, m å' tin quibaj a t' ån.
\v 19 Ca' bin in wac ti' in tet: M å' tsoyen a waquen wa ja pararen. Chan cha' in beyaj tech an ten bic a c'urew.‚Äù
\v 20 A its'inbiro' caj riq'ui, caj sutn åjij ich yatoch u tet.
\p ‚ÄôTi' toy y ån nach caj irir ten u tet, tan u sut. Caj yajquinta'b ten u tet caj u c' ånaj u yacab quir u nup'ur caj c'uchij ich u parar. Caj u p åt åx mec'taj caj u ts'u'ts'aj u p'uc.
\v 21 Rajen u parar caj u ya'araj ti' u tet: ‚ÄúTet, quen, a teno' y ån in si'pir ti' C'uj. Baxuc tech quire' m å' tin quibaj a t' ån. Rajen m å' tsoyen a waquen wa ja pararen.‚Äù
\v 22 Caj c'uchob yejer u tet ich yatoch. U tet caj ya'araj ti' u c'urew: ‚ÄúChuquej u jer u noc' a tsoyo' ca' a t åquej u noc' ti'. Chuquej u c' åb ca' a c' årej tu c' åb. Chuquej u pech' x ån åb ca' a jupej ich yoc.
\v 23 Joq'uen chuque b åc' a tan ic tsentic ca' ij quinsej ca' ij qui' jan ånex ca' qui'ac ij corex.
\v 24 Quire' a je' in parara' in wer uche' quimen chen ti' y ån baje'rer cuxa'an quire' caj u p' åtenob uch chen baje'rer tan tu c'uchur.‚Äù Caj u y ånxchun u betic ti' u qui' jan ånob.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄôU parar a sucu'unbiro' ti' y ån ich u cor ca'ch caj ur u yits'in. Tan u yu'ur tabar u c'uchur ich yatoch. Caj yubaj u c'ayob tan yoc'atob xan.
\v 26 Rajen caj u t' ånaj turiri' u c'urew u tet caj u c'ata ti' ba' cu yiricob.
\v 27 Caj ara'b ti' ten u c'urew: ‚ÄúQuire' toc ur a wits'in rajen a tetex caj u ya'araj ca' quinsac b åc' a toc tsemta'an toc ti' y ån yor quire' urij.‚Äù
\v 28 A sucu'unbiro' caj ts'iquij, rajen m å' u c'at u yocar ich u tet. Caj joc' u tet caj u chich araj ti' ca' ocac.
\v 29 Caj u nuncaj ti' u tet: ‚ÄúU'yej ba' quin wac. Ya'ab yaxq'uin caj in beyaj tech. Ti' toy quin beyaj tech a ba' ta wa'araj ca'ch, caj in toc quibaj. M å' ta chuca b åc' teni', a ts'aten m å' chichin soc in qui' jan ån yejer a mac in jach yajob.
\v 30 Chen caj urij a parar a je'ra' a caj u r åc xupaj a taq'uin yejer xquic a cu manob. Biquinin caj a wa'araj u quinsa' yoch b åc' ya'ab a tsemta'an ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ti' u tet?‚Äù
\v 31 Chen u tet caj u ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúIn pararech. Rajra' ti' y ånech tin wicn ån. Tu cotor ba' a y ån ten, tech y ånin.
\v 32 M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij‚Äï, y ån ij qui'quintic ij cor. Y ån ij qui' jan ån xan quire' urij a wits'in. In wer quimij uch chen ti' y ån baje'rer cuxa'an quire' caj u p' åt ånenob uch chen baje'rer tant u c'uchur.‚Äù
\c 16
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' u ca' ts'urir a m å' tu qui' quibaj u t' ån u Jach Ts'urir
\p 
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob xan:
\p ‚ÄïTi' y ån mac u Jach Ts'urir, ney ån u taq'uin. Aro' y ån u ca' ts'urir. Caj ara'b ti' ten mac: ‚ÄúA ca' ts'urir tech caj u r åc xupur a ba' y ån tech.‚Äù
\v 2 Rajen u Jach Ts'urir caj u p åyaj ca' tac u ca' ts'urir caj c'uchij caj ara'b ti' ten u Jach Ts'urir: ‚ÄúArej ten ba' caj in wu'yaj u jumintic tech, a rac'ob? Toc ts'ibtej ten mun caj a r åc xupaj in ba'tac baxuc a mun caj a jaraj ten quire' baje'rer m å' a bin a beyaj ten.‚Äù
\v 3 Caj u tucraj u ca' ts'urir caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúBa' quin bin in betej quire' in jach ts'urir bin u joc'siquen ti' in beyaj tu quin c ånantic u ba'tac? M å' c'ucha'an in wor in chich beyaj. Je' in ch'ic suraquir wa quin man in c'atic ba' ti' in rac'ob.
\v 4 In toc er ba' quin bin in betej soc u yacsiquen mac ca' bin joc'saquen ti' in beyaj tu tin c ånantaj u ba'tac in jach ts'ur.‚Äù
\v 5 Caj u p åyaj jujuntur a mac y ån u bo'or ti' u jach ts'urir caj ara'b ti' a y ån c'uchij: ‚ÄúMun a bo'or ti' in jach ts'urir?‚Äù
\v 6 A mac y ån u bo'or caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúA teno' y ån in bo'or cuatro mil litros tsats.‚Äù Caj ara'b ti' ten a ca'ts'uro': ‚ÄúCuren ‚Äïquen‚Äï, a je' u ju'unin a bo'or ca' a ts'bitej a bo'or chen dos mil.‚Äù
\v 7 Caj c'uchij ich u jer caj u c'ataj ti': ‚ÄúMun a bo'or ti' in jach ts'urir?‚Äù Caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúA teno' y ån in bo'or turi' mil tzontle n år.‚Äù Caj ara'b ti': ‚ÄúA je' u ju'unin a bo'or ca' a ts'ibtej ocho cientos tzontle n år.‚Äù
\v 8 Caj u c' å'otaj u jach ts'urir ti' u ca' ts'urir a m å' tu qui' c ånantaj u ba'tac. ‚ÄúAro', jach t'aj ‚Äïquij jach ts'urir‚Äï, an bic tabar caj u tucraj soc u yacsa' ten a mac y ån u bo'or ten.‚Äù Quin wac techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, jach t'aj a mac a cu yajquinticob a ba' y ån ich yoc'ocab. M å' ja wirej, neyerob bic tabar cu c ånanticob u b åj. Chen ya'ab mac a yerob C'uj m å' u netucricob bic tabar cu bin u jaricob u taq'uin yejer u ba'tac.
\p 
\v 9 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA teno' quin wac techex a ba' y ån techex ich yoc'ocab. Je' u r åc xupur. Chen a ba' y ån techex c' ånex ti' mac soc tsoy yiriquechex. Ca' bin xuruc t' ån y ån mac ich ca'anan cu bin u yacsiquechex soc munt q'uin ti' y ånechex ich ca'anan.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄôWa mac cu qui' c ånantic a ba' m å' neno'ji', je' u qui' c ånantic a ba' jach no'jo'. A mac m å' u c ånantic a ba' m å' neno'ji', m å' ju bin u c ånantic a ba' jach no'jo'.
\v 11 Rajen wa m å' ta qui' c ånantex a ba' ts'a'b techex ich yoc'ocab, m å' ju bin ts'abir techex a ba' jach no'jo' ich ca'anan. A ti' taro', m å' u xupur.
\v 12 M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, a ba' y ån techex ich yoc'ocab C'uj y ånin, m å' techex y ånin. Wa m å' ta qui' c ånantex a ba' y ånin C'uj m å' u bin u ts'ic techex soc techex y ånin a ba' m å' u xupur ich ca'anan.
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄôM åna' mac c'ucha'an yor u c åjtar ich yatoch wa cu ts'urintic ca'tur u jach ts'urir quire' cu bin u p'actic turiri' chen cu bin u yajquinbir juntur u jach ts'urir. M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, cu bin u qui' beyaj ti' a mac cu jach s åtic. Chen u jer u jach ts'ur a m å' ju s åjtic, m å' ju qui' beyaj ti'. Baxuc techex. M å' c'ucha'an a worex a c'ujintiquex C'uj wa caj a qui' beyajex quire' a c'at a nejariquex a taq'uinex.
\p 
\v 14 C' ås b åyt åc ti' y ånob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo caj ts'oc yubicob ya'aric ti' u cams åwinicob caj u p'astajob Jes√∫s quire' cu nepachticob u taq'uin u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo'.
\v 15 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' a fariseojo':
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' ca tus ets'tiquex jach tsoyechex  åc åtan a rac'obex barej C'uj yer a pixamex. M å' ja wirej, y ån a ba' cu tucricob winic, jach no'jo'. Chen ya'ab ba' cu tucricob winic no'j, a C'ujo' cu p'actic.
\s1 U t' ån a caj u ts'ibtaj Mois√©s yejer u t' ån a caj u ts'ibtaj y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄôM å' toy tac Juan, ra' caj u p åyaj a berex a ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Mois√©s yejer a ba' caj u ts'ibtaj y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj. Pachir a Juano' caj u tsec'taj techex bic tabar cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. Baje'rer ya'ab mac u c'atob u yocar tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj.
\p 
\v 17 ‚ÄôCa wiric, a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj a chichino' a puntojo', m å' u bin ts'ocar ti'. Chen a ca'anano' yejer a ru'umo' cu bin r åc ts'ocar ti'. Tu cotor u t' ån C'uj cu bin nupsej.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic m å' tsoy u p' åtic u rac'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ19.1‚Äë12; Mr.‚ÄØ10.1‚Äë12)
\p 
\v 18 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïWa mac cu p' åtic u rac' quir u bin u ch'ic u jer. Caj ts'oc u ch'ic u jer y ån u si'pir, irej wa man u ca' yejer. Baxuc a mac a cu ch'ic u raq'uintej a p'ato'. Baxuc xan y ån u si'pir aro' irej wa man u ca' yejer mac a cu man.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' a mac ney ån u taq'uin yejer a mac jach otsir u c'aba' L√°zaro
\p 
\v 19 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïIj quer ti' y ån mac jach y ån u taq'uin, a ba' cu buquintic jach tsoy u noc', quire' jach co'oj. Rajra' cu qui' jan ån xan.
\v 20 Ti' y ån mac otsir u c'aba' L√°zaro p'achen t'uch u c ånm ån. Tar cu bin purbir ten u rac'ob ich u jor u pa'te' a mac ney ån u taq'uin.
\v 21 Cu pachtic u jantic u p'up'ir a cu pich'intic cu ts'ocar u janticob a ney ån u taq'uin. Cu tar a pec'o' cu rets'ic u p'achen t'uch.
\v 22 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin caj quimij a otsiro' caj bin purbir ten y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj ca'anan tu y ån u nunquir Abraham. Baxuc caj quimij a ney ån u taq'uin, caj bin mucbir.
\v 23 Caj binij tu cu bin mac a cu quimin a y ån u si'piro'. Tu cu muc'yaj, a ney ån u taq'uin caj u nacsaj u wich caj u p åctaj nach. Caj u yiraj ti' y ån Abraham yejer L√°zaro ich ca'anan.
\v 24 Caj u yaw åt t' åntaj caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúIn nunquirech Abraham ‚Äïquen‚Äï, yajquin ten ‚Äïquij‚Äï, arej ca' tac L√°zaro tu y ånena'. Arej ca' t åre ja' tu yar u c' åb ca' tac u t årej ja' tin wac' ca' sisac in wac' quire' tan in jach muc'yaj ich c'ac' tu quin werar.‚Äù
\v 25 Caj ara'b ten Abraham: ‚ÄúIn pararech ‚Äïquij Abraham‚Äï, c'aj tech a ucho' ti' toy cuxa'anech ich yoc'ocab quire' caj a qui'quintaj a wor a ba' y ån tech. Baxuc L√°zaro xan caj muc'yajn åjij ya'ab ca'che', ti' toy cuxa'an ich yoc'ocab. Chen baje'rer L√°zaro qui'quinta'b yor chen a techo' ts'a'b a muc'yaj.
\v 26 Ti' toy y ån ‚Äïquij Abraham‚Äï, m å' c'ucha'an yor L√°zaro u tar tu y ånech. Quire' toc beta'b ten C'uj, jach carem u ch'ic ca'ananin ich tech, baxuc ich ten xan. Soc a tenob m å' c'ucha'an in worob in tarob tu y ånech. Baxuc tech m å' c'ucha'an a wor a tar tub y ånenob.‚Äù
\v 27 Rajen caj u ya'araj a mac ney ån u taq'uin: ‚ÄúQuin chich c'atic tech in nunquirech Abraham ca' a tuchi'tej L√°zaro ich yatoch in tet.
\v 28 Quire' y ån cinco in b åjob. Ca' yarej ti'ob soc m å' u beticob xan an ten bic caj in betaj uch ich yoc'ocab soc ca' bin quimicob m å' u tarob yejeren tu quin muc'yajob.‚Äù
\v 29 Abraham caj u nuncaj ti': ‚ÄúA b åjob tech toc y ån a ts'ibta'b u t' ån C'uj a nanij cu xaquicob, baxuc cu tsec'tic ti'ob tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Chen y ån u quibejob a ba' cu yubicob, ya'ara' ti'ob.‚Äù
\v 30 Caj ya'araj a mac ney ån u taq'uin: ‚ÄúIn nunquirech Abraham ‚Äïquij‚Äï, m å' u bin u quibicob tu cu tsec'ta' ti'ob u t' ån C'uj. Jaj ixt åcoj wa cu riq'uir a quimeno' soc u bin u tsicbar ti'ob je' u c'axicob yor, tan u p' åticob u man tu c'asir.‚Äù
\v 31 Abraham caj ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúWa m å' u quibicob a ts'iba'an u t' ån C'uj cax wa riq'uir mac tu quimen m å' u bin u yacsejob tu yorob.‚Äù
\c 17
\s1 Jes√∫s cu tsicbar ti' u cams åwinicob
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ18.6‚Äë7, 21‚Äë22; Mr.‚ÄØ9.42)
\p 
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïRajra' y ån ba' quir u yacsic u si'pir chen jach otsir a mac cu tumtic yor soc u yacsic u si'pir u rac'ob.
\v 2 Wa cu jich'ir tu car a jach ar u ca'ir tu cu juch' ti' a ray xibob soc u juruc ich c'ac'nab ca' quimic. Aro' jach tsoy ca' juruc soc m å' c'ucha'an yor cu tumtic yor mac soc u yacsic tu si'pir quire' cu tucric: Jot mac aro'.
\p 
\v 3 Jes√∫s caj u chich ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantej a b åj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, wa ja wet acsa'orir caj u c år åxbetaj tech. Ca' bin ts'ocac a chich aric ti'. Soc u p' åtic u c'asir caj u betaj. Jaj ixt åcoj je' u c'axic u yor tan u p' åtic. Ca' a jawsej ti' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï.
\v 4 Cax ya'ab u tenin cu c år åxbetic tech a wet acsa'orir. Baxuc ya'ab u tenin cu tar yac tech: ‚ÄúM å' in y ån y ån betej aro'.‚Äù Ca' a jawsej ti'.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob: Taj y ån a wacsic ta wor
\p 
\v 5 A mac tuchi'ta'b ten Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, y åmtej a tenob soc in qui' acsicob tin worob a t' ån.
\p 
\v 6 A Jaj Ts'uro' caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïWa ca wacsiquex ta wor ti' C'uj cax an ten bic mijin u yijir mostaza, raji' jach mijin. Jeroj c'ucha'an a wor a wac ti' a je' che'a' carem: ‚ÄúJoq'uen che' ‚Äïquech ti'‚Äï. Ca' xiquech a p åc' a b åj ich c'ac'nab.‚Äù A che'o' cu bin yubic a t' ån.
\s1 U c'urew mac a ba' ara'b u betej raji' cu betic
\p 
\v 7 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïWa ja c'urewex cu beyaj ich a corex tan u muxic ru'umin a corex soc a paq'uiquex a trigojo'. Baxuc tan u c ånantic a w år åc' t åm ån yuc, ca' bin uruc beyaj. A techexo' m å' a wac ti': ‚ÄúSepquintej ca' curaquechex ta jan ån.‚Äù
\v 8 M å' wa ca waquex ti': ‚ÄúToc ts'ocsej in wo'och. Cu ts'ocar ca ts'icten. Cu ts'ocar in jan ån a teno' tsoy a bin janen tech xan.‚Äù
\v 9 Je' wa ja wac ti' a c'urew: ‚ÄúBayo'‚Äù ‚Äïquech ti'‚Äï, quire' qui' beyan åjij? M å' ja bin a wa'aric ti' baxuco' quire' caj u chen betaj a ba' caj a wa'ara ti'.
\v 10 Baxuc techex in w åjcams åy åjirechex ca' bin ts'ocac a r åc betiquex a ba' caj u ya'araj C'uj. Ca' a waquex ti' C'uj: ‚ÄúCaj in chen betajob a ba' y ån in beticob. M å' tsoyenob a wactenob bayo'.‚Äù
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic xibob u c ånm ån iq'uer u ca'ob
\p 
\v 11 Ti' toy cu bin Jes√∫s ich u berij Jerusal√©n. Ti' manij tu xurij u ru'umin Samaria. Baxuc ti' u xur u ru'umin Galilea.
\v 12 Caj c'uchij ich u chan cajar. Tabar u yocar caj u nup'ob xib diez, u c ånm ån iq'uer u ca'ob. Ti' xurob nach.
\v 13 Caj u c'am puraj u t' ånob caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïIn Jaj Ts'urirob Jes√∫s ‚Äïquij‚Äï, yajquin tenob ca' a jawsenob.
\p 
\v 14 Caj yiraj Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïXenex ich  åc åtan sacerdote soc u yiriquechob jawechex.
\p Caj binob jaw iq'uer u ca'ob ti'.
\v 15 Turiri' xib ich a diezo' caj yiraj toc jawij, rajen sutn åjij ich Jes√∫s. C'am caj aw åtn åjij:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, caj a jawsajen.
\p 
\v 16 Caj c'uchij ich Jes√∫s caj xonr åj caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' ‚Äïquij.
\p Raji' c åja'an ich u ru'umin Samaria uch.
\v 17 Rajen Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïCaj in jawsaj diez. Tu binob a nuevejo'?
\v 18 Chen a je' turi' xiba' a cu tar ich tanxer ru'um w åc' ås tarij ya'aric ti' C'uj: ‚ÄúBayo'.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' xib:
\p ‚ÄïRiq'uen ca' xiquech quire' jawech quire' caj a wacsaj ta wor ten.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu tsicbar ber ca' bin tac u reyinticob C'uj
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.23‚Äë28, 36‚Äë41)
\p 
\v 20 Caj c'uchob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' ich Jes√∫s. Caj u c'atob:
\p ‚ÄïBer ca' bin u reyintejob C'uj?
\p 
\v 21 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ‚ÄïM åna' ba' cu bin yesic techex soc c'ucha'an a worex a werex tabar u reyinticob C'uj. M åna' mac cu bin ya'aric: ‚ÄúIric te' y åna' tan reyinticob C'uj. Baxuc tar y åno' tan u reyinticob C'uj.‚Äù Quire' toc ti' y ån baje'rer tub y ånechex tan u reyinticob C'uj.
\p 
\v 22 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïCa' bin a pachtej a wirej a mac a cu bin tuchi'bir ten C'uj. Cax turiri' u q'uinin ca wiriquex, chen m å' a bin a wirexi'.
\v 23 Y ån mac cu bin u yac techex: ‚ÄúIric tan u reyinticob tera'‚Äù, wa cu bin ya'aricob: ‚ÄúTan u reyinticob taro'.‚Äù M å' ja say årex tu pachob tu cu payiquechex.
\v 24 An ten bic ca wiriquex u raram. Seb cu sasich åj år tu cotor ca'anan. Baxuc ca' bin taquen ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin quire' a teno' tu tuchi'tajen C'uj, baxuquenechexo'. Baxuc seb ca' bin raramn åc baxuc tu cotor mac cu bin yiriquen.
\v 25 Chen p åyber quin bin in jach muc'yaj. Bin u ca'ob u xump' åtiquenob u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Baxuc a mac a cu camsicob u t' ån Mois√©s. Baxuc u ts'urirob u cajar u winiquirob jud√≠o. Baxuc u winiquirob jud√≠o, m å' ya'ab. Bin u ca'ob xump' åtiquenob quire' m å' u yacsicob tu yorob ten.
\v 26 An ten bic u q'uinin, ti' y ån No√© uch, baxuc cu bin u betej u q'uinin ca' bin urquen quire' caj u tuchi'ten C'uj ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï.
\v 27 M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, a mac c åja'anob tu q'uinin No√©, rajra' tan u qui' jan ånob. Rajra' tan u ch'icob u yo'och. Rajra' tan u ts'icob u pararob quir u raq'uinticob mac. Hasta caj c'uchij tu q'uinin No√©, caj oc ich chem caj tari ya'arir, jach c'am. A mac m å' r åc ocob ich chem caj r åc bint ja'.
\v 28 Baxuc caj beta'b u q'uinin c åja'an Lot ich Sodomajo'. A mac c åja'anob ich u cajar Sodoma, rajra' tan u jan ånob. Rajra' tan u yuc'urob. Rajra' tan u canicob u ba'tac. Rajra' tan u m ånicob u ba'tac. Rajra' tan u p åq'uicob u nar. Rajra' tan u c' åxicob yatochob.
\v 29 Chen u q'uinin caj ruq'uij Lot tu cajar Sodoma C'uj caj u chaj u tar c'ac' ca'anan yejer tunich. Erar u ca' an ten bic cu tar ja' ca'anan, caj r åc quinsa'bij ten c'ac'.
\v 30 Baxuc ca' bin c'uchur tu q'uinin ca' bin urquen quire' a teno' caj u tuchi'ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 31 ‚ÄôCa' bin uruquen. Wa ti' y ån xib ich u jo'r yatoch tan u jesicob u b åjob. Quire' ti' taro' u jo'r yatoch taj, chen u ba'tac ti' y ån tu japnin yatoch. Arej m å' u yeman u maric u ba'tac. Arej u toc p' åtej. Baxuc a mac ti' y ån tu cor cax m å' u sut tu yatoch.
\v 32 M å' wa c'ajtechex ba' u ber ti' u rac' Lot?
\v 33 A maque' cu tucric u ta'quic u b åj soc m å' u muc'yaj soc m å' u quimin xan, aro' tar cu bin ich c'ac'. Chen a mac a cu yac te' y ånena' quir in muc'yaj quir in quimin xan, quir in yamtic Jes√∫s. Aro' bin u ca' cuxtar munt q'uin.
\p 
\v 34 ‚ÄôQuin wa'aric techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, soc a werex ba' u ber u q'uinin ca' bin uruquen. Waj oq'uin quin wur. Wa ti' y ån ca'tur xib p'eri' u wenenob. Turi' cu bin p åybir ten y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj. Turi' cu bin p' åtbir.
\v 35 Ra'iri' u q'uinin xan, wa ti' y ån ca' tur xquic tan u juch'ob turiri' cu bin p åybir ten y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj. Turiri' cu bin p' åtbir.
\v 36 Ra'iri' u q'uinin xan, wa ti' y ån ca'tur xib ich u cor. Turi' cu bin p åybir ten y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj. Turi' cu bin p' åtbir.
\p 
\v 37 U cams åwinicob caj ts'oc yubicob ya'aric Jes√∫s a je' t' åna', caj u c'atajob ti':
\p ‚ÄïTu cu bin u betej aro', Jaj Ts'urir?
\p Caj u nunca'b ti', caj u ya'araj tu cu camsic t' ån:
\p ‚ÄïA mac a m å' u c'at u quibicob u t' ån C'uj je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin cu bin tar u muc'yaj.
\c 18
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ya'aric ti'ob tu cu camsic ti' xquic a quimen u mam yejer juez
\p 
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob tu cu p'eriquintic u t' ån soc u c ånicob:
\p ‚ÄïCa' a t' ånex C'uj soc m å' u nacar a worex, tu ca t' åniquex C'uj.
\v 2 Ti' y ån u cajar ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, tu c åja'an juez. A juezo', m å' u s åjtic C'uj, m å' ju tucric mac xan.
\v 3 Tiri' ich u cajar xan, ti' y ån xquic, quimen u mam raji' caj bin  åc åtan juez. Su' su' cu bin ya'aric ti': ‚ÄúY åmtejen ti' a mac a cu p'actiquen.‚Äù
\v 4 Caj u y ånxchun u tar xquic a juezo', m å' ju quibaj u t' ån. Chen pachir caj u ya'araj tu yor: ‚ÄúCax m å' in s åjtic C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, cax m å' in tucric ti' mac.‚Äù
\v 5 Caj ya'araj a juezo': ‚ÄúBin in ca' in yamtej a je' xquica', a quimen u mam ra' cu p'acta' xquique' soc m å' u choquintic in wor quire' rajra' cu tar. Quire' ca'an in wor in wu'yic ya'aric.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Caj ya'araj Jaj Ts'ur:
\p ‚ÄïC ånex ti' a ba' cu ya'aric juez cax m å' taj yor.
\v 7 Chen m å' baxuc C'uj quire' taj yor. Wa rajra' ca c'atiquex tu ca t' åniquex C'uj u bur u q'uinin u bur u ac'bir soc u c ånantic a ba' a c'at. A techexo' a teta'b ten C'uj, je' u tar u tajir techex. A C'ujo' m å' u ts'ocar u yubic a t' ånex.
\v 8 A teno' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, quin wac techex. A C'ujo' seb cu ta'quic techex mac ti' a cu p'acti'echobo'. Chen ca' bin uruquen ich yoc'ocab a teno' caj u tuchi'ten C'uj, baxuquenechexo'. Je' wa jin wiric mac tan u yacsic tu yor ten. Tan u pajicob ten ca' in ta'quej ti' a mac a cu p'actic ti'e'.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic ti' a fariseojo' yejer y åjc' åmin u taq'uin gobierno
\p 
\v 9 Jes√∫s caj u ca' camsaj tu cu p'eri'quintic u t' ån. Y ån mac cu tucric chen jach tsoy a ti'ob  åc åtan tu wich C'uj quire' a ba' cu beticob. Chen cu tucric tu yor: ‚ÄúJot u rac'ob.‚Äù Rajen Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj baxuc aro', caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄïCa'tur xib binob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o quir u t' ånicob C'uj. Turiri' u winiquir jud√≠o a fariseojo', u jer y åjc' åmin u taq'uin gobierno.
\v 11 Caj ch'iraj u winiquir jud√≠o a fariseojo' soc yirir ten tu cotor mac caj u tus t' ånaj C'uj. Tu yor, caj u t' ånaj C'uj, caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúBayo' C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, m å' in betic an ten bic u jer winiquir jud√≠o cu betic. A teno', m å' in tus ch'ic a ba' y ån ti' winic. Baxuc m å' jin man tu c'asir, m å' jin man in wiric xquic, m å' c'as a teno'. M å' baxuquen a cu c' åmic u taq'uin gobierno a ti' y åno'.
\v 12 A teno', quin qui' c'ujintiquech, quin jamach p' åtic in jan ån ca'tur u q'uinin ich a turi' semana. Tu cotor in taq'uin tu quin jaric quin chuquic turiri' ich a diezo' soc in ts'ic ti' a mac a cu jach beyaj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj.‚Äù
\v 13 Chen y åjc' åmin u taq'uin gobierno, nach y ån. Ti' y ån tu pach u rac'ob tu cu t' ånicob C'uj. M å' ju c'at u nacsic u wich quir u t' ånic C'uj. Cu chen p åxic u tsem quire' yer y ån u si'pir. Quire' baxuc nanij cu betic u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj ya'araj ti' C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï: ‚ÄúChan yajquin ten quire' y ån in si'pir a teno'.‚Äù
\v 14 Quin wa'aric techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, C'uj caj u jawsaj u si'pir a cu c' åmic u taq'uin gobierno. Caj bin tu yatoch toc tsoyquinta'b yor ten C'uj. Chen a fariseojo', m å' tsoyquinta'b yor ten C'uj. A mac a cu yac jach no'jen ‚Äïquij‚Äï, chen a C'ujo' cu bin ya'aric: ‚ÄúJo'tech a techo'‚Äù, cu yiric m å' no'ji'. Chen a mac cu yac: ‚ÄúJo'ten a teno'.‚Äù Chen a C'ujo' cu yiric jach no'j.
\s1 Jes√∫s yejer a chichano'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ19.13‚Äë15; Mr.‚ÄØ10.13‚Äë16)
\p 
\v 15 Caj tarob u purej ti' Jes√∫s a mac yaje', baxuc yejer a chichano'. Caj tar purbir a chichano' soc u p åt åxmec'tic. Caj irir ten u cams åwinicob ba' u ber. Caj u q'uejajob:
\p ‚ÄïJoq'uen, xen ‚Äïquij.
\p Quire' m å' u c'at yiric u tarob ich Jes√∫s a chichano'.
\v 16 Jes√∫s caj u p åyaj ca' tacob. Caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïTs'ire'ej u tarob a chichano' tin wicn ån. M å' ja q'ueyic an ten bic a je' chichana'. Baxuco' a mac c'ucha'an yor yocor tu cu reyinticob C'uj. Y ån u c ånic irej wa ja chichano'.
\v 17 Jach taj quin wac techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. A mac a m å' ju c ånic a chichano' soc u chabar ten C'uj u reyinticob m å' u c'uchur yor, u c'uchur ich ca'anan tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj.
\s1 U ts'urir u winiquirob jud√≠o jach ney ån u taq'uin, tan u tsicbar yejer Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ19.16‚Äë30; Mr.‚ÄØ10.17‚Äë31)
\p 
\v 18 Caj tarij turi' u jach ts'urir u winiquirob jud√≠o ich Jes√∫s. Caj u c'ataj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJach tsoyech in w åjcams åy åjirech. Arej ten ba' y ån in betic soc in cuxtar munt q'uin?
\p 
\v 19 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca wac tsoyen? M åna' mac jach tsoy chen jari' C'uj.
\v 20 Tech a wer ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Mois√©s uch. Cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúM å' a y ån man yejer xquic baxuc xquic, m å' u y ån man yejer xib. M å' ja quinsic mac. M å' ja wac'ric ba'. M å' a y ån man tus, a caj a wiraj ba'. Y ån a s åjtic a tet, y ån a s åjtic a n å' xan.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 U jach ts'urir u winiquirob jud√≠o caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïTu cotor aro' ten caj in toc quibaj tin chichanin uch.
\p 
\v 22 Rajen caj ts'oc yubic Jes√∫s a ba' caj u ya'araj. Caj ara'b ti':
\p ‚ÄïY ån turi' ba' m å' ta quibaj ca' a betej aro'. Canej tu cotor a ba' y ån tech. Cu ts'ocar a r åc canic, ca' a j åsej a taq'uin ti' a mac otsir. Cu ts'ocar aro', ca' taquech tin pach quir a c ånic in t' ån. Ca' bin c'uchuquech ich ca'anan tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. Cu bin u ts'ab år tech a ba' jach co'oj.
\p 
\v 23 Caj ts'oc yubic a ba' caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' caj tucurn åjij quire' jach y ån u taq'uin.
\v 24 Jes√∫s caj yiraj tucur u ca' a xibo' caj u ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïJach yaj yocar mac a ney ån u taq'uin tu cu reyinticob C'uj quire' u yaj u taq'uin.
\v 25 Je' wa ju c'uchur yor yocar y år åc' tsimin ich u jor yit' puts'? M å' ju c'uchur u yor quire' chichin u jor yit' puts'. Je' wa ju c'uchur u yor yocar ich ca'anan a mac ney ån u taq'uin? M å' ju yocar quire' u yaj u taq'uin. Jaj ixt åcoj, je' u yocar y år åc' tsimin ich u jor yit' puts'. Chen a mac ney ån u taq'uin m å' yocar, tu cu bin u reyintejob C'uj, quire' u yaj u taq'uin.
\p 
\v 26 A mac a caj u yubaj u t' ån caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïA mac cu bin ta'cbir ten C'uj tun?
\p 
\v 27 Rajen Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA C'ujo' c'ucha'an yor ti' a ba' m å' c'ucha'an yor ti' mac.
\p 
\v 28 Pedro caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, caj in toc r åc p' åtajob a ba' y ån tenob quir in tarob ta pach soc in c ånicob a t' ån.
\p 
\v 29 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïJach taj quin wac techex. Wa mac cu p' åtic yatoch wa ju rac' wa ju tet. Wa ju b åjob wa ju pararob soc raji' cu reyinticob C'uj wa cu cha'icob.
\v 30 Cu bin u c' åmej ti' C'uj a ba' jach tsoy baje'rer. Jach manan cu bin ts'ab år ti'. Baxuc xan, ca' bin xuruc t' ån je' u ts'ab år ti' u cuxtar munt q'uin.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ca' a'aric: Bin in ca' quinsbir
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ20.17‚Äë19; Mr.‚ÄØ10.32‚Äë34)
\p 
\v 31 Jes√∫s caj u p åyaj u doce u cams åwinicob soc u tsicbar ti'ob tu junanob:
\p ‚ÄïBaje'rer ‚Äïquij‚Äï, quic w åc' ås bin ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Tu cotor a ba' caj u ts'ibtajob y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj ti' ten uch. Je' u tar ten quire' caj u tuchi'tajen C'uj baxuquenechexo'.
\v 32 Ti' cu bin u c'ubiquenob ti' a mac a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ti' cu bin u p'astiquenob. Ti' cu bin u c år åxbetiquenob. Ti' cu bin u tubiquenob xan.
\v 33 Ti' cu bin u chich j åts'icob in pach. Cu ts'ocar aro' cu bin u quinsiquenob. Chen ca' bin man åc m åna' u nup u q'uinin, je' in riq'uir tin quimirir.
\p 
\v 34 U cams åwinicob, m å' tu najtajob a ba' caj u yubajob ya'aric Jes√∫s quire' m å' yerob ba' u c'at ya'aric u t' ån.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a ch'op u wicho' ich u cajar Jeric√≥
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ20.29‚Äë34; Mr.‚ÄØ10.46‚Äë52)
\p 
\v 35 Tabar u c'uchur Jes√∫s ich u cajar Jeric√≥. Ti' cura'an a ch'op u wicho' ich n åc' bej. Tan u c'atic u taq'uin quir u jan ån.
\v 36 Caj u r åc u'yaj u manob a pimo' a ch'op u wicho' caj u c'ata ti' mac b åyt åc ba' u ber.
\v 37 Caj ara'b ti':
\p ‚ÄïJes√∫s a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret, raji' caj a wu'yaj u man  åc åtan tech.
\p 
\v 38 A ch'op u wicho' caj u puraj u t' ån ti':
\p ‚ÄïJes√∫s ‚Äïquij‚Äï, u pararech a nunquir u rey David, chan yajquin ten.
\p 
\v 39 Chen a mac a cu binob p åybej caj u ya'arajob ti':
\p ‚ÄïM åc a chi' ‚Äïquij.
\p Chen caj u jach c'amquintaj yaw åt t' ån:
\p ‚ÄïU pararech a nunquir u rey David, chan yajquint ten.
\p 
\v 40 Caj xurij Jes√∫s ich bej caj ya'araj ca' tac purbir ti'. Caj u juts' u b åj ich Jes√∫s caj c'ata'b ti':
\p 
\v 41 ‚ÄïBa' a c'at in betej tech?
\p A ch'op u wicho' caj u nuncaj:
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, in c'at u sasich åj år in wich.
\p 
\v 42 Caj ara'b ti' ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïCa' tac u sasirir a wich quire' caj a wacsaj ta wor ten.
\p 
\v 43 Rajen sasich åjij u wich. Rajen seb caj sasich åjij u wich caj say tu pach Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj.
\p Baxuc a mac a caj u yirob u jaw år u wich caj ya'arajob xan:
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj.
\c 19
\s1 Jes√∫s ti' y ån yejer Zaqueo
\p 
\v 1 Caj oc Jes√∫s ich u cajar Jeric√≥. Ti' man chumuc u cajar.
\v 2 Ti' y ån turi' xib ney ån u taq'uin u c'aba' Zaqueo, u jach ts'urir y åjc' åminob u taq'uin gobierno.
\v 3 Zaqueo u c'at u yiric Jes√∫s quir u c' å'otic, chen m å' c'ucha'an yirej quire' a pimob, cabar u baquer. M å' c'ucha'an yor yirej quire' ti' y ån a pimob.
\v 4 Rajen caj u c' ånaj yacab caj naquij ich c' åb che' quire' ti' y ån u berir quir u man Jes√∫s soc yiric. Rajen p åybej caj bin.
\v 5 Ti' manij Jes√∫s tu y ån Zaqueo. Jes√∫s caj u p åctaj ti', caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïZaqueo ‚Äïquen‚Äï, seb a wem ån quire' y ån in jamach p'at år ta watoch.
\p 
\v 6 Rajen Zaqueo seb caj emij ich ru'um, qui' yor caj u qui' acsaj tu yatoch.
\v 7 A mac a caj u yirajob yocar Jes√∫s ich yatoch Zaqueo caj u pacran arajob ich u rac'ob, tan u choctar yorob:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin cu y ån ocar aro' ich yatoch a mac y ån u si'pir quir u wen ån?
\p 
\v 8 Caj ch'icraj Zaqueo  åc åtan tu cotor mac soc ch åca'an yubicob. Caj ya'araj ti' Jaj Ts'urir:
\p ‚ÄïIric Jaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï. Y ån in ts'ic ti' in taq'uin ti' a otsiro'. Chumuc tu cotor a y ån teno' quin bin in ts'ic ti'. Wa caj in tus ch'aj u taq'uin mac uch, quin bin in sutej ti'. Cuatro u tenin quin sutic ti'.
\p 
\v 9 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïBaje'rer C'uj caj u ta'quech yejer tu cotor mac a ti' y ån ta watoch. Jach taj u pararech a nunquir Abraham, quire' caj a wacsaj ta wor ti' C'uj an ten bic ic nunquir Abraham uch, caj u yacsaj tu yor.
\v 10 M å' ja wirej, a baxuquenechexo' caj u tuchi'ten C'uj ca' in wesej quin yajquintic mac a tabar u bin ich c'ac' quir in ta'quic a mac a cu yacsic tu yor ten.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic quir u c ånic ti' diez taq'uin
\p 
\v 11 Ti' toy cu yubicob an ten bic Jes√∫s caj u tsicb åtaj ti' Zaqueo. Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u camsic ti'ob quire' tabar u c'uchur ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Rajen cu tucricob c'uchij tu q'uinin u reyinticob Jes√∫s u ru'umin u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\v 12 Rajen caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïA mac jach no'j u tet ‚Äïquij‚Äï, caj bin ich tanxer ru'um soc u yacsa' rey. Caj ts'oc yacsa' rey caj w åc' ås urij.
\v 13 Caj bin ich tanxer ru'um ca'ch caj u t' ånaj diez u c'urew caj u ts'aj jujuntur u c'urewob dos cientos pesos caj u ya'araj ti'ob: ‚ÄúC' ånej a je' taq'uina' ca' a jarex u jer taq'uin jach ya'ab hasta quin wu'ur.‚Äù
\v 14 Jeroj caj binij. Ti' y ån mac ich u cajar aro' caj p'acta'b ten u yet cajarob a cu bin yocar rey. Rajen caj u tuchi'taj mac tu pach aro' caj u ya'araj ti' rey: ‚ÄúM å' in c'atob u yocar quir in reyinticob. M å' a wacsic ti'.‚Äù
\v 15 Caj urij a je' xibo' caj u y ånxchun u reyinticob caj u p åyaj u c'urew a caj u ts'a ti' u taq'uin uch ca' tacob  åc åtan ich rey. Quire' u c'at yer mun t'aj u taq'uin jujunturob.
\v 16 A p åybejo' tarij caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúJach Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, a taq'uin a ta ts'aj ten, dos cientos pesos uch, jach net'ajij baje'rer y ån dos mil pesos.‚Äù
\v 17 U jach ts'urir caj ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúJach tsoy a beyaj, jach tsoy in c'urewech. In wer baje'rer ca qui' c ånantic a ba' m å' ya'ab tech. Rajen quin bin in ts'ic diez cajarob quir u reyintiquech.‚Äù
\v 18 A ca'tur u c'urew tarij caj ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúJach Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï. A taq'uin a caj a ts'aj ten dos cientos pesos, jach t'aj baje'rer y ån mil pesos.‚Äù
\v 19 U jach ts'urir caj ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúTech quin bin in ts'ic cinco cajarob quir u reyintiquech.‚Äù
\v 20 Caj tar u jer u c'urew caj ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, je' a taq'uina'. Caj in tapa caj in ric'saj,
\v 21 quire' caj in ch'aj sajaquir tech quire' ts'iquech. Quire' tech ca ch'ic a ba' m å' tech y ånin. Quire' tech ca jaq'uic u nar mac cax tech m å' ta p åc'aj.‚Äù
\v 22 U jach ts'urir caj u ya'araj ti': ‚ÄúJach c'as in c'urewech, a w åc' ås t' ån tech a caj a wa'araj. Raji' cu bin u ta'quic a jo'r quire' a wer jach ts'iquen quire' a teno' quin ch'ic u taq'uin mac a caj u jaraj. Quire' quin jaq'uic u nar mac a m å' tin p åc'aj.
\v 23 Rajen biquinin m å' ta majantaj in taq'uin ti' mac soc c' ås t'ajij in taq'uin ca' bin urquen. Ca' in ch'ic cax m å' ya'ab?‚Äù
\v 24 Caj ara'b ten u jach ts'urir ti' a mac ti' y ån tu yicn ån u c'urew a c'aso': ‚ÄúTaquej ti' u taq'uin a ti' y ån ti' a dos cientos ca' a ts'ic ti' a mac y ån ti' dos mil pesos.‚Äù
\v 25 U c'urewob caj ya'arajob ti': ‚ÄúJach Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, toc y ån ti' dos mil pesos a caj a p' åtaj ti'.‚Äù
\v 26 U jach ts'uric caj ya'araj ti'ob: ‚ÄúQuin wac techex a mac a cu betic tsoy yejer a ba' quin ts'ic ti'. Je' in ts'ic ti' jach ya'ab. A maque' a m å' u c' ånic a ba' quin ts'ic ti'. Je' in ta'quic ti', cax m å' ya'ab y ån ti'.
\v 27 Techex a werex a mac a cu p'actiquen ca'ch. Robob a m å' u c'at in wocar rey toc chuquejob ca' a quinsejob  åc åtan ten.‚Äù
\s1 Jes√∫s cu yocar ich u cajar Jerusal√©n
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.1‚Äë11; Mr.‚ÄØ11.1‚Äë11; Jn.‚ÄØ12.12‚Äë19)
\p 
\v 28 Caj ts'oc a ba' caj u camsa sam ich yatoch Zaqueo. Caj u p' åtaj u cajar Jeric√≥ quir u bin ich u cajar Jerusal√©n.
\v 29 Tabar u c'uchur ich u cajar Betfag√©, baxuc ti' y ån u cajar Betania, n åts'a'an ti'ob y ån u chan p'uc witsir u c'aba' Olivos. Quire' ra' u c'aba' u che'er a ti' y åno'. Jes√∫s caj u tuchi'taj ca'tur u cams åwinicob.
\v 30 Caj ara'b ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïXenex ich u chan cajar c' ås b åyt åc ca' bin ocaquechex ich u cajar. Je' a wirex chan tsimin ti' maca'an, m åna' mac u c åptanm ån u pach. Pitex ti' ca' a paytex tera'.
\v 31 Wa mac cu c'atic techex: ‚ÄúBiquinin ca pitiquex chan tsimin?‚Äù Caj a waquex ti' baxuc a je'ra': ‚ÄúQuire' ic Jaj Ts'urir u c'at u c åptar tu pach‚Äù, quech ti'.
\p 
\v 32 U cams åwinicob caj binob caj yirajob ti' maca'an chan tsimin an ten bic Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob.
\v 33 Caj u pitajob chan tsimin caj tarij a mac y ånin caj u c'ataj: ‚ÄúBiquinin ca pitiquex chan tsimin?‚Äù
\p 
\v 34 Raji'ob caj u nuncajob:
\p ‚ÄïQuire' ic Jaj Ts'ur u c'at u c åptar tu pach.
\p 
\v 35 A ca'tur u cams åwinicob caj u paytajob chan tsimin caj binob u purej ich Jes√∫s. Caj u j åyajob u noq'uir u pach chan tsimin. U cams åwinicob caj u yamtajob Jes√∫s quir u c åptar tu pach chan tsimin.
\v 36 Caj bin Jes√∫s tu berir Jerusal√©n. Ti' c åpa'an Jes√∫s tu pach chan tsimin ich u bej tu cu man Jes√∫s. A winiquir jud√≠ojo' caj u pitaj u ca' yarir u noc'ob quir u j åyicob tu ber Jes√∫s. Irej nanij cu yacsicob rey tu cajarob quire' qui' yorob yiricob.
\v 37 Tabar u c'uchur Jes√∫s ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Ti' y ån chan p'uc witsir Olivos tu cu bin yemantic Jes√∫s. U cams åwinicob a pimo' caj u y ånxchun u qui'quinticob yorob. C'am caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj quire' caj in wirob jach carem a beyaj.
\p 
\v 38 A pimo' caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïTan in c'ujinticob a je' reya' a c åp åcbar tu pach chan tsimin a caj u tuchi'taj C'uj. Ca' ij carej ti': Bayo' C'uj, ti' y ånech ich ca'anan quire' caj a quetquintaj ij corex yejerech ‚Äïbaxuc caj ya'arajob a pimo'.
\p 
\v 39 Ti' y ån m å' ya'ab u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' ich a pimo', caj ya'arajob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïArej u m åcob u chi' a cams åwinicob.
\p 
\v 40 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti'ob, caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïQuin wac techex, wa cu m åquicob u chi' a je' winica', jaj ixt åcoj, a je' tunicha' je' u joc'ar u t' ån, tan ya'aric: ‚ÄúQuin c'ujintiquechob.‚Äù
\p 
\v 41 Jes√∫s tabar u nats' år caj yiraj u cajar Jerusal√©n caj oc'n åjij Jes√∫s quire' otsir yiric, a mac ti' y ån tu cajar Jerusal√©n.
\v 42 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJaj ix t åcoj wa ja toc erex bic c'ucha'an a worex a quetquintiquex a worex yejer C'uj chen baje'rer C'uj m å' u cha'ic a wiriquex ba' a ber techex.
\v 43 Quire' ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin a mac a cu p'actiquechex cu bin u ts' åpquinticob tunich soc m å' tu ca puts'urex. Quire' caj u toc b åcris ts' åptajob tunich.
\v 44 Cu bin u quinsicob techex yejer a pararobex. Cu bin u r åc jubsicob u tunichir a cajarex cu bin u r åc pich'inticob tunich. Baxuc cu bin u beticob techex quire' m å' ta wacsajex ta worex ti' C'uj quire' caj u tuchi'tajen a teno' a baxuquenechexo' ti' techex quir in yamtic techex.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu joq'sic a mac ti' y ån ich carem naj a cu canicob ba'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.12‚Äë17; Mr.‚ÄØ11.15‚Äë19; Jn.‚ÄØ2.13‚Äë22)
\p 
\v 45 Caj oquij Jes√∫s ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj u y ånxchun u joc'sic a mac cu canicob u ba'tac tu japnin carem naj ba'iri' a mac a cu m ånicob ba'.
\v 46 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTi' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj, cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúIn watoch a je'ra' quir u tar mac u t' ånic C'uj‚Äù, chen techex caj a waysaj irej wa tu cu much'quinticob u b åj a cu yac'r å' ba'.
\p 
\v 47 Jes√∫s caj ts'oc u joc'sic a mac a cu canicob ba' ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Rajra' Jes√∫s cu camsic a mac a cu tar ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Chen u jach ts'urirob u sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s yejer u jach ts'urir u winiquirob jud√≠o u c'at u quinsicob Jes√∫s.
\v 48 Chen m å' yerob bic tabar cu bin u quinsicob ti' quire' a pimo' u jach c'at yubicob u t' ån Jes√∫s.
\c 20
\s1 Mac aric ti' Jes√∫s quir u camsic aro'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.23‚Äë27; Mr.‚ÄØ11.27‚Äë33)
\p 
\v 1 Jes√∫s ti' y ån turi' u q'uinin ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj u camsaj ti'ob. Baxuc caj u tsec'taj ti'ob u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj. Caj c'uchob u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s yejer u ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o a nuxibo'.
\v 2 Caj ya'arob ti':
\p ‚ÄïMac caj u ts'ajaj a muc' caj a c' åmaj? Mac arej tech quir a camsicob quir a tsec'ticob? Arej tenob mac caj u ya'araj tech ca' a camsej ti'ob?
\p 
\v 3 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc ten bin in ca' in c'atic techex. Nunquex ten.
\v 4 Arex ten mac tuchi'tej Juan quir yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac? C'uj wa tuchi'tej Juan wa xib tuchi'tej?
\p 
\v 5 Caj u tucrajob bic tabar cu bin u nunquicob ti'. Caj pacran arajob:
\p ‚ÄïWa quij aric ti', C'uj caj u tuchi'taj Juan quir u yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac, je' ya'aric to'on: ‚ÄúBiquinin m å' ta wacsajex ta worex ti'?‚Äù
\v 6 Wa quij aric xib caj u tuchi'taj, a pimo', je' u ch'inico'onob quire' yerob taj tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj Juan quir u tsec'tic t' ån.
\p 
\v 7 Caj u nuncob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' in werob mac tuchi'tej Juan quir u yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac.
\p 
\v 8 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc techex, m å' a wa'aric mac tuchi'tej Juan, baxuc ten ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, m å' in wac techex mac caj u ya'araj ten quir in camsic ti'ob.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic: Irej wa mac caj u majantaj u corir u wich uva
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.33‚Äë44; Mr.‚ÄØ12.1‚Äë11)
\p 
\v 9 Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u camsic a pimob caj u camsaj baxuc a je'ra' soc yerob a maque' a m å' u c'at u yacsicob tu yor ti' quire' bin u ca' ich c'ac'. Rajen caj u camsaj a je'ra':
\p ‚ÄïTi' y ån mac uch caj ts'oc u ch' åquic u che'er u cor caj u r åc tocaj u robirir caj u p åc'aj u yaq'uir u wich uva. Caj ts'oc u p åq'uic, caj u ts'aj ti' mac quir u c ånanticob. U bo'orir u cor ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u t'aquic u wich uva. Cu ts'icob ti' u ts'urir u cor jun xot' u wich. U ts'urir caj bin nach ama'an caj urij.
\v 10 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin cu t'ocar u wich uva. U ts'urir caj u tuchi'taj u c'urew tu y ån a mac a cu c ånanticob u corir uva quir u c'at junxot' u wich uva u bo'orir u cor. Chen a mac a cu c ånanticob u cor caj u raxajob u c'urew caj w åc' ås tuchi'ta'b m å' tu ts'ajajob ti' u wich uva.
\v 11 U jach ts'uriro' caj u ca' tuchi'taj u jer u c'urewo'. A mac cu c ånanticob u corir u wich uva caj u raxob u c'urew. Caj u p'astajob xan caj u puts'ob ca' xic m å' tu ts'ajajob ti'.
\v 12 U jach ts'urir ca' u w åc' ås ca' tuchi'taj u jer u c'urewo' chen a mac a cu c ånanticob u corir u wich uva, baxuc xan, caj u j åts'ajob hasta em u q'uiq'uer caj u pich'intajob tu n åc' c'axir u corob.
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄôU jach ts'urir u cor u wich uva caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúBa' quin bin in betej?‚Äù U b åjir cu t' ån tu junan: ‚ÄúJe' in tuchi'tic in parar in jach yaj, jaj ixt åcoj cu s åjticob y åjc ån åny åjirob u pach u corir uva.‚Äù
\v 14 Chen a mac a cu c ånanticob u pach u cor uva caj u yirob u tar u parar u ts'urir: ‚ÄúAra' cu tar u pararo', ra' cu bin u ch'ic u cor u tet ca' bin quimqui'.‚Äù Baxuc caj ya'arob ich u rac'ob: ‚ÄúCa' ij quinsej soc to'on ca' bin ic ch'ic u cor.‚Äù
\v 15 Ti' taro' caj u quinsajob u parar u ts'urir caj u joc'sajob u pich'intej ich n åc' c'ax. Ba' cu bin u betej u jach ts'urir ti' y åjc ånany åjirob u pach u corir uva?
\v 16 Je' u tar u jach ts'urir quir u joc'sic u quinsej quir u ts'ic u cor ti' u jer mac.
\p Caj yubob ya'aric u winiquirob jud√≠o caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïJaj ixt åcoj m å' u tar to'on.
\p 
\v 17 Jes√∫s caj u p åctaj u wichob caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïArex ten ajera' ba' cu ya'aric ich u t' ån C'uj tu ts'iba'an? Tan ya'aric:
\q1 A teno' iren a yoc najo' soc u chich tar u muc' naj, chen a ray yoc najo' pich'ita'b ten y åjc' åxirob naj uch. Quire' m å' u c'at, chen caj u w åc' ås chucajob quir u c' åxicob yatoch soc u chichtar u muc'.
\m 
\v 18 A mac a m å' u yacsic tu yor ten baje'rer. Raji' irej a mac cu nacch' åtic tunich caj yajij yoc. Chen ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t' ån, a mac a m å' tu yacsaj tu yor ti' C'uj, raji' irej mac cu rubur tunichir tu yoc'or cu max åre' toc ram ån ich ru'um.
\s1 Cax ic bo'otej u bo'orir u beyaj gobierno
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.45‚Äë46; 22.15‚Äë22; Mr.‚ÄØ12.12‚Äë17)
\p 
\v 19 Ra'iri' u q'uinin u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s u c'at u chuquicob Jes√∫s. Quire' yerob a ba' caj u camsaj sam quire' Jes√∫s yer m å' tu yacsicob tu yorob. M å' tu jach chucob Jes√∫s quire' cu ch'ic saquirob a pimob. M å' ja wirej, a pimob u nec'at yubic u tsicbar Jes√∫s.
\v 20 Tan u ch'ucticob u chuquej Jes√∫s, rajen caj u tuchi'tajob mac quir u tus waytarob u t' ån soc cu tus ta'quicob u jo'r ich gobernador. U c'at u ta'quic u jo'r ti' gobernador soc u quinsa'. Rajen yet tarob a mac a cu tus aric tsoy yorob. Soc u tus aric a ba' cu yubic u tsicbar Jes√∫s.
\v 21 Rajen caj u c'atob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech ‚Äïquij‚Äï, in werob taj a ba' ca wac. Baxuc taj a ba' ca camsic ti' u t' ån C'uj. M å' a coyen chich aric ti' mac quet ca wa'aric ti'. Quire' baxuc taj ca camsic tenob a ba' u c'at C'uj ti' tenob.
\v 22 In c'atob in wer wa tsoy in bo'oticob in ru'um ti' rey? Wa m å' tsoy in bo'oticob in ru'um?
\p 
\v 23 Jes√∫s caj u yubaj ba' c'as cu tucricob tu yorob, caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca tarex a tumtiquex in wor?
\v 24 Esej ten a taq'uin turiri' ca' in wirej.
\p Caj u yesob ti' Jes√∫s. Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïMac jot'a'an u yochiri'? Ba' quiri' u c'aba' ts'iba'an ti'?
\p Raji'ob caj u ya'arob ti':
\p ‚ÄïRa' u yochir u rey C√©sar, jot'a'an ich s åc taq'uin.
\p 
\v 25 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTaj a ba' ca waquex. Rajen ca' a quib åquex a ba' cu yac techex u rey, C√©sar, baxuc xan, ca' a quib åquex a ba' cu ya'aric C'uj techex.
\p 
\v 26 M å' c'ucha'an yor yubic ba' cu ya'aric Jes√∫s ich a pimo' soc u tus ta'quicob u jo'r Jes√∫s. Chen jaca'an yorob a ba' yubicob ya'aric Jes√∫s. Rajen ts'oc u t' ånob.
\s1 Cu tar u c'aticob saduceo, mac cu riq'uir tu quimen
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ22.23‚Äë33; Mr.‚ÄØ12.18‚Äë27)
\p 
\v 27 Baxuc xan, tarob u winiquirob jud√≠o a saduceojo'. Aro' cu ya'aric m å' u riq'uir mac tu quimirir. Caj tarob u c'atej ba' ti' Jes√∫s; caj ya'arajob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ic nunquir Mois√©s caj u ts'ibtaj to'on uch a ba' ca' ic betej. Caj ya'araj wa ju mam cu quimin, cu p'at år u rac', m åna' u parar yejer caj quimin u mam, tu junan. Caj ya'araj Mois√©s, ra' u yits'in u mam, raji' cu bin u ch'ic u raq'uintej a mu'. Soc yiric wa je' u pararanc år yejer soc u ch'isic u parar, irej waj u tus parar u sucu'un uch.
\v 29 A sucu'unbir y ån seis yits'inob. A sucu'unbir, raji' tu y ån ch'aj u rac' hasta quimin, m åna' u parar.
\v 30 A its'inbiro' raji' u ta'quic u chu'ch u sucu'un. Raji' caj u ch'aj u rac' u sucu'un, m åna' u parar xan.
\v 31 A jach ca' its'inbiro', raji' caj u ta'ca u chu'ch u ca' sucu'un. Raji' caj u ch'aj u rac' u ca' sucu'un. M åna' u parar xan. Hasta nup u r åc ch'ic u yits'inob u mam hasta r åc quimob, m åna' u parar.
\v 32 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u quimin a xquico' caj quimij.
\v 33 Ca' bin riq'uic tu quimen, mac cu bin u ch'ic u raq'uintej quire' siete caj u ch'aj u mam.
\p 
\v 34 Rajen Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti'ob, caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA te' ich yoc'ocab cu ch'ic u rac' mac, baxuc xquic cu ch'ic u mam xan. Baxuc a pararex xan cu ch'ic u rac', baxuc xquic a pararex xan, cu ch'ic u mam.
\v 35 Ca' bin ts'ocac u riq'uir mac tu quimen, a mac jach tsoyo' cu bin cha'bir yocar ten C'uj ich ca'anan. Munt q'uin ti' y ånob. M å' u ch'ic u rac' a ich C'ujo'. M å' ju bin u ch'ic u mam.
\v 36 Quire' a taro', m å' ju bin quimen, irob baxucob y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj. Quire' u pararob C'uj quire' ric'ob tu quimen ten C'uj uch.
\v 37 M å' wa c'aj techex a ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Mois√©s uch a caj u yiraj tu cu yerar c'ac' ich chan che'er uch. Caj ara'b ten C'uj ti' Mois√©s. ‚ÄúA teno' u C'ujirenob a nunquirex Abraham yejer a nunquirex Isaac yejer a nunquirex Jacob.‚Äù Rajen ij quer cu bin riq'uir mac tu quimirir.
\v 38 A C'ujo', raji' u C'uj tu cotor mac. Raji' u C'uj a mac cuxa'an. Baxuc xan, raji' u C'uj a mac quimen quire' a quimeno' cuxa'an  åc åtan ti' C'uj.
\p 
\v 39 M å' ya'ab ti' y ånob y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj ya'arob ti':
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, taj a ba' caj a wa'araj ti' u winiquirob jud√≠o a saduceojo'.
\p 
\v 40 Quire' sajaquir u ca' u c'atob ti' Jes√∫s. Rajen caj u p' åtajob u c'ata ba'.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti' y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s mac a Cristojo'?
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ22.41‚Äë46; Mr.‚ÄØ12.35‚Äë37)
\p 
\v 41 Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBic tabar cu ya'aricob a pimob yejer u ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o, u parar u nunquir David. Raji' Cristo a mac tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj?
\v 42 M å' ja wirej, u b åjiri' David, caj u ts'ibtaj ich u ju'unin Salmos ich a uchben u t' ån C'ujo'. Caj ya'araj:
\q1 Ic Jach Ts'ur C'uj, quij David, caj u ya'araj ti' in Jach Ts'ur: ‚ÄúTar a cutar, quij C'uj, tin noj soc p'eri' quic reyinticob mac.
\v 43 Soc p'eri' quic reyinticob mac hasta cu c'uchur tu q'uinin quin r åc ch'ersic a mac a cu p'actiquech.‚Äù
\m Baxuc caj ara'b ti' ic nunquir David ten C'uj.
\p 
\v 44 Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti'ob caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA je' u t' ån C'uj cu yesic to'on David caj u t' ånaj a Cristojo', in Jach Ts'ur, quij David. Rajen biquinin ca waquex u parar David a Cristojo' quire' wa raji' u Jach Ts'urir, quet ba'iri'?
\s1 Jes√∫s cu chich aric ti' u cams åwinicob, qui' c ånantej a b åj ti' y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ23.1‚Äë36; Mr.‚ÄØ12.38‚Äë40; Lc.‚ÄØ11.37‚Äë54)
\p 
\v 45-46 Jes√∫s cu tsicbar ti' u cams åwinicob p'eri caj yubajob a pimo':
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantajex a b åj soc m å' a c åniquex y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. M å' ja wirej, y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Jach tsoy u noc' cu manob soc u tus turicob u rac'ob, jach no'job aro'. Qui' yorob yiricob baxucob. Jach qui' yorob yiricob u t' ån ån ten u rac'ob tu cu naj bin u m ånicob yo'och quire' cu yiricob tus no'job aro'. Baxuc cu tetic u cutanob tu cu cutar a jach no'jo' tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj. Baxuc tu cu qui'qui' jan ånob soc u tus irir jach no'job.
\v 47 M å' ja wirej. y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s cu tus aricob ti' a u quimenob u mam. Soc u tus ch'ic yatoch yejer u ba'tac cax y ån tu yatoch. Jach ama'an u ts'ocar u t' ånicob C'uj soc u rac'ob cu tus tucricob cu qui' c'ujinticob C'uj. Jach manan cu bin ts'ab år u muc'yajob ten C'uj quire' cu beticob aro' cax yerob u t' ån C'uj. Chen u jerob mac m å' neyaj cu bin muc'yajob.
\c 21
\s1 Quire' Jes√∫s cu yiric cu but'ic taq'uin tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj a quimen u mamo'
\r (Mr.‚ÄØ12.41‚Äë44)
\p 
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj u yiraj tan u but'icob u taq'uin a mac ney ån u taq'uin tu cuchir tu cu naj but'icob u taq'uin tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ra' taq'uin ti' carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj.
\v 2 Caj u yiraj xan xquic a quimen u mamo' otsir caj u but'aj u majan taq'uin, ca'tur ch åc taq'uin a m å' coji'.
\v 3 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti':
\p ‚ÄïTaj quin wac techex. A je' xquica' a quimen u mamo' cax otsir. Chen caj u but'aj ca'tur u ch åc taq'uin a m å' coji' chen  åc åtan tu wich C'uj co'oj caj u but'aj. Chen u rac'ob cax ya'ab caj u but'ajob chen  åc åtan tu wich C'uj m å' co'oji'.
\v 4 A mac ney ån u taq'uinob caj u but'ob u taq'uin tu nanij cu but'icob u taq'uin tu cuchir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj. Quire' jach manan ya'ab caj u but'ob quire' jach manan t'aj u taq'uin chen ra' caj u but'ob quire' m å' u r åc c' ånicobe' u taq'uin. Chen a xquico' a otsiro' caj u toc r åc but'aj ti'o' u taq'uin cax m åna' tu cu m ånic yo'och.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ya'aric bin u ca' juburob carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.1‚Äë2; Mr.‚ÄØ13.1‚Äë2)
\p 
\v 5 Ti' y ån m å' ya'ab mac caj ya'araj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïIra wirej, jach tsoy tu ts' åpa'an u tunichir carem naj. Baxuc u tunichir ti' C'uj a ts'abij ten, m å' ya'ab u winiquirob jud√≠o, quire' cu s åjticob C'uj.
\p Chen Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄïA ca wiriquex carem naj ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u r åc jubsa' ten mac. Cu bin u r åc pipich'inticob, m å' ju bin p'at år ca'tur ts' åpric.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu tsicb åtic a ba' cu bin yesic ca' bin xuruc t' ån
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.3‚Äë28; Mr.‚ÄØ13.3‚Äë23)
\p 
\v 7 U cams åwinicob caj u c'atob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ber ca' bin jubuc a caj a wa'araj? Ba' cu bin u yesic to'on xan wa tabar u xur t' ån?
\p 
\v 8 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantex a b åj ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, quire' je' u tar mac u tusiquechex. M å' a quibiquex aro'. Quire' cu bin ya'aricob: ‚ÄúA teno' Cristojen, caj u tuchi'ten C'uj.‚Äù Tan ya'aric: ‚ÄúTabar u xur t' ån.‚Äù Chen m å' ja y ån say årex tu pach.
\v 9 M å' ja ch'iquex sajquir ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, wa tan a wu'yiquex tan u quinsicob u b åj. Cax wa cu wu'yiquex bin u ca' quinsicob u b åj. Raji' cu y ånxchun u tar u quinsicob u b åj chen m å' toy xuruc t' åni'.
\p 
\v 10 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' toy c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t' åni' A je' u ru'umin tu c åja'anob mac. Je' u ts'ictar mac ich u ru'umin tu c åja'anob mac. Baxuc xan, mac ich u chan cajar. Bin u caj ts'ictarob yejer mac ich u jerob u chan cajarob.
\v 11 M å' toy xuruc t' ån, cax cu chen pec u ru'umin. Jach c'am cu pec tu c åja'anob mac. Y ån a ru'umin m å' u pec juntur u cajar u ru'umin tu c åja'anob mac. Y ån u ru'umin je' u pec u ru'umin tu c åja'an mac. Y ån u q'uinin cu bin yubicob wi'ij. An bic cu c ånic u yajirir seb cu c ånicob. Ra' cu bin u r åc man tu cotor. Je' u ch'icob sajquir mac ca' bin yirob a ba' u ber ich ca'anan a ba' cu bin yesej C'uj.
\p 
\v 12 ‚ÄôM å' c'uchuc tu q'uinin aro' cu bin chuquex a pach quire' caj a wacsajex ta wor ten ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. Baxuc cu bin u c'ubiquechex yejer u ts'urirob tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Baxuc xan, quir u m åquiquexob tu cu ma'c år winic. Ti' cu bin u chop åytiquexob quir u bin u puriquechex  åc åtan rey yejer ich gobernador quir u taquiquex a jo'r.
\v 13 Wa ra' u q'uinin cu beticob techex aro', ra' u q'uinin c'ucha'an a wor a waquex ti'ob u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj.
\v 14 M å' a tucriquex wa cu tar u chuquex a pach. Baxuc m å' a tucriquex ba' ca bin a wa'arex ti'ob. M å' toy xiquex  åc åtan a mac a cu bin u ta'quic a jo'r.
\v 15 A teno' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, je' in ts'ic techex a t' ånex quire' a ne'er a nuquiquex u t' ånob. Je' a nunquiquex ti' soc m å' c'ucha'an yor u p åq'uiquex a pach a mac u p'ec yiriquechex.
\v 16 M å' chen a mac cu p'actiquechex cu bin u chuquiquex a pachex. A tet xan, yejer a n å', cax a b åjob xan, cax a mac a u jach yajechex xan, cu bin u chuquiquex a pachex, tan u c'ubicob techex. Baxuc je' u quinsiquechex xan, m å' ya'abi' ich techex.
\v 17 Quire' techex caj a wacsajex ta wor ten tu cotor mac cu bin u p'actiquechex.
\v 18 Qui' c ånex a je'ra'. M å' ja wirej, a C'ujo' cu c ånantic techex soc m åna' ba' u ber techex, m å' ja bin sat år turi' u tsotser a jo'r.
\v 19 Je' u ts'ab år techex a cuxtarex munt q'uin wa rajra' ca muc'tiquex a ba' cu tar techex tu cu chuquicob a pachex.
\p 
\v 20 ‚ÄôQuire' wa ca wiriquex y åjquinsirob mac jach pim tan u b åcristicob u cajar Jerusal√©n. A werex c'uchij tu q'uinin u r åc jubsicob u cajar Jerusal√©n.
\v 21 Barej ca wiriquex b åcrisa'an u cajar Jerusal√©n. Arej ti' a mac ti' y ån ich u ru'umin Judea ca' r åc puts'ucob ich wits. Arej ti' a mac ti' y ån ich u cajar Jerusal√©n ca' putsuc xan. Arej ti' a mac ti' y ån ich tancab u cajar Jerusal√©n. Arej ti'ob m å' u puts'urob ich u cajar Jerusal√©n.
\v 22 Ra'iri' u q'uinin c'uchij tu q'uinin u bo'oticob u bo'orir u si'pir ti' C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o ich u cajar Jerusal√©n quire' baxuc caj u ya'araj tu ts'iba'an u t' ån C'uj. Rajen cu bin u nupsej.
\v 23 Jach otsir a xquico', ra' u q'uinin jach na'aj. Baxuc xquic cu ts'ic u chu'ch u chan ti'ar. M å' ja wirej, tu cotor mac a ti' y ån tu ru'umin Judea, cu bin ts'abir u muc'yajob ten C'uj. Quire' ts'iquij a C'ujo' quire' caj u yiraj m å' quibob u t' ån.
\v 24 Y ån cu bin ch' åcbirob u car ten y åjquinsirob winiquirob ich u winiquirob jud√≠o. Y ån ya'ab xan cu bin purbirob ich u jer ru'umin quir u c'an ån beyajob tu cu binob ich tu cotor u cajarob ich yoc'ocab u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ti' cu bin ts'urinbir u cajar Jerusal√©n ten a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o hasta c'uchij tu q'uinin u ts'ocar u ts'urinticob u ts'urirob u ru'umob.
\s1 Y ån ba' cu bin yesej tabar u tar Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.29‚Äë35, 42‚Äë44; Mr.‚ÄØ13.24‚Äë37)
\p 
\v 25 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïRa' u q'uinin ca' bin ts'ocac u ts'urinticob a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o. A ba' u ber ich ic yum, baxuc ich ic n å'. Baxuc ich a sabo', cu bin u jac' år yor tu cotor mac. M å' yerob mac ba' cu bin u beticob. Ca' bin yubejob u jum c'ac'nab, jach c'am yejer u yamin xan. Cu bin u ch'icob sajquirob.
\v 26 Ra'iri' u q'uinin tu cotor mac a ti' y ån ich yoc'ocab cu bin u ch'ic sajquirob ca' bin jac' åcob yorob. Quire' a ba' u ber ich yoc'ocab. Quire' a C'ujo' cu bin u r åc siptic a sabo'.
\v 27 Ra'iri' u q'uinin mac ti' y ånob ich yoc'ocab cu bin yiricob in tar ich u muyarir ca' bin taquen yejer in muc' soc yer tu cotor mac jach no'jen a teno'. Quin bin in tar yejer jach manan u sasirir C'uj xan. A teno' baxuquenechexo'.
\v 28 Barej u q'uinin cu y ånxchun arayo' chichquintej a worex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, qui'quintex a worex quire' tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin in ca' ur quir in ta'quiquechex ti' a c'aso'.
\p 
\v 29 Jes√∫s caj u camsaj baxuc a je'ra' caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïC'aj techex ca' bin a wirex u che'er higuera yejer tu cotor che'.
\v 30 Cu ts'ocar u joc'ar u mumun re', tabar u yocar yaxq'uin.
\v 31 Baxuc xan, ca' bin a wirex a ba' u ber ich ic yum. Baxuc ich ic n å'. Baxuc ich a sabo', je' a werex c'uchij tu q'uinin u tar C'uj quir u reyinticob.
\p 
\v 32 ‚ÄôTaj quin wa'aric techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, cu y ån tar tu cotor ba' a caj in wa'araj techex. M å' toy quimiquechex a mac cuxa'an baje'rer.
\v 33 Je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin a ca'anano' cu bin ts'ocar baxuc cu bin ts'ocar u ru'umin. Chen in t' ån a caj in wa'araj techex a C'ujo' cu bin u nupsic.
\p 
\v 34 ‚ÄôQui' c ånantex a b åj. M å' a jen jan ånex, m å' ja wuq'uiquex quir a carch åj årex. M å' ja man a tucriquex bic tabar a jariquex a taq'uinex. M å' ja wirej, quire' a mac a cu jen jan ån yejer a cu yuq'uic quir u carch åj årob yejer mac a cu tucric u nejaric u taq'uin ca' bin taquen a teno' u q'uinin m å' tan u pajicob quir u bin ich ca'anan quire' seb quin bin ur.
\v 35 Baxuc a mac m å' yerob C'uj ich yoc'ocab cu bin u jac' år yorob ca' bin uruquen wa ra' u q'uinin m å' tan u pajicob in wur. Baxuc a b åc'o' ca rejiquex m å' yer.
\v 36 Chen techex rajra' ca c ånantiquex a b åj. Rajra' ca t' åniquex C'uj soc ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin tabar u xur t' ån cu bin u yamtiquechex C'uj quir a muc'tiquex a ba' u ber techex. Soc a tarex  åc åtan tu y ånen quire' a teno' baxuquenechexo'.
\p 
\v 37 U burur q'uin Jes√∫s caj u camsaj a pimo' ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Chen oq'uin rara' cu bin ich u jo'r p'uc wits u c'aba' Olivos. Ti' p'atij ich u jo'r wits.
\v 38 A'ac'bir tu cotor mac cu binob ich tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o quir yubic u tsicbar Jes√∫s.
\c 22
\s1 Judas u c'at u c'ubic Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.1‚Äë5, 14‚Äë16; Mr.‚ÄØ14.1‚Äë2, 10‚Äë11; Jn.‚ÄØ11.45‚Äë53)
\p 
\v 1 Tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' jan ånob u winiquirob jud√≠o ra' u q'uinin cu janticob yoch pan a m å' u sipe'. P åcha'an u c'aba' pascua quire' ra' u q'uinin caj u potmastaj y åjt' ånir C'uj uch soc m å' u quimin chan xib chichin.
\v 2 U ts'urirob sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s, u c'at u muc u chuquicob Jes√∫s. Baxuc u c'atob quire' cu s åjticob a pimob. Caj u c åxtajob mac quir u c'ubic quinsbir Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 3 A Judaso' caj u ts'urintaj quisin raji' p åcha'an u c'aba' Iscariote, raji' turi' ich u doce u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s.
\v 4 Judas caj u p' åtaj Jes√∫s yejer u yet cams åwinicob caj bin ich u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer u capit√°n polic√≠a caj pacran tsicban åjij yejerob soc yerob bic tabar cu c'ubic Jes√∫s ti'ob.
\v 5 Caj qui'jij yorob u jach ts'urirob sacerdote rajen caj u toc arob je' u boticob tu c'ubij Jes√∫s ten Judas.
\v 6 Judas caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïTsoy.
\p Caj u y ånxchun u chanber tucric u c'ubic Jes√∫s ra' u q'uinin m å' ti' y ån a pimo', soc m å' yerob wa bin u ca' chucbir Jes√∫s.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u tuchi'taj u cams åwinicob quir u chanber ch åquicob yoch quir u qui'qui' jan ånob u q'uinin pascua
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.17‚Äë29; Mr.‚ÄØ14.12‚Äë25; Jn.‚ÄØ13.21‚Äë30; 1 Co. 11.23‚Äë26)
\p 
\v 7 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin a cu janticob yoch pan a m å' u sipe'. Ra' u q'uinin xan cu quinsicob y år åc' t åm ån yuc u chan ar soc u c' å'otic bic C'uj caj u ta'caj u nunquir u winiquirob jud√≠o ich u ru'umin Egipto.
\v 8 Rajen Jes√∫s caj u tuchi'taj Pedro yejer Juan caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïJoq'uenex ca' a toc ch åquex ij cochex quir ij qui' jan ånex quir ij c' å'otic u q'uinin pascua.
\p 
\v 9 Robob caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïTub a c'at ic ch åquex? Arej to'on tuba?
\p 
\v 10 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïU'yex ba' quin waquex techex. Ca' bin oquechex ich u cajar, je' a wiriquex xib turiri', u c'ochm ån u p'urir yoch ja'. Sayenex tu pach hasta ca wiric tu cu yocar tu yatoch a ca' ts'ap yatocho'. Quet a wocarex yejer.
\v 11 Arej ti' mac y ånin yatoch: ‚ÄúIj c åjcams åy åjirex caj u ya'araj tenob ca' in c'atejob a watoch junxot' soc p'eri' quin jan ånob yejer in camsawinic quir in c' å'oticob u q'uinin pascua.‚Äù
\v 12 A mac y ånin yatoch ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, je' u yestic techex junxot' yatoch tu ca' ts'ap, toc y ån u pojche'ir tu cu jan ån. Toc y ån u cutan xan. Ti taro' ca ch åquiquex ij cochex.
\p 
\v 13 Caj binob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj yirob an ten bic Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob, caj u ch åcob yo'och quir u qui' jan ånob quir u c' å'oticob u q'uinin pascua.
\p 
\v 14 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u janticob yoch u q'uinin pascua caj curaj Jes√∫s baxuc u cams åwinicob.
\v 15 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïCaj in jach pachtaj in jantej yoch tu q'uinin pascua yejerechex. M å' toy muc'yajn åquen.
\v 16 Quin wac techex ca' bin ts'ocac in jantic a je'ra'. M å' jin y ån y ån ca' jantic hasta ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu reyinticob C'uj. A ra' u q'uinino' quin ca' jantic.
\p 
\v 17 Caj ts'a'b ti' Jes√∫s u c'ab uva ich ruch caj u pe'aj. Caj u ya'araj ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj.
\p Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' caj u ts'aj ti' u cams åwinicob, caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïCa' ca' xot' a wuq'uiquex.
\v 18 Quin wac techex tin toc uc'aj a je'ra'. M å' in y ån y ån uq'uej hasta ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u reyinticob C'uj. Je' in ca' uq'uique'.
\p 
\v 19 Caj u chuca yoch pan caj u m åchaj caj u ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj.
\p Caj ts'oc ya'aric aro' caj u xat'aj caj u j åsej ti'ob u cams åwinicob. Caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA je' a woch pana', raji' in winquirir quir in c'ub år techex soc in quinsa'. Baxuc y ån a jantiquex soc a c' å'otiquex u q'uinin tu quimen.
\p 
\v 20 Caj ts'oc u r åc jan ånob yoch u q'uinin pascua ca' u pe'aj a rucho' xan caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTucrex a je'ra' u c'ab uva, raji' in q'uiq'uer. Irej bin u ca' joc'ar in q'uiq'uir tu quin quinsa', u bo'orir a si'pirirex. Soc toc ric'ben an ten bic caj in toc araj techex. M å' ja wirej, u t' ån Mois√©s ruc'sabij soc y ån u jer ric'ben a jach manan tsoy.
\p 
\v 21 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTaj quin wac techex a mac cu bin u c'ubiquene' p'eri' cu jan ån yejero'on baje'rer. Raji' cu bin u c'ubiquen ti' mac quir in quinsa'.
\v 22 A teno', y ån in quinsa' a teno', baxuquenechexo'. An ten bic caj u toc araj C'uj uch. Chen jach otsir a mac a cu c'ubiquen.
\p 
\v 23 Caj u y ånxchun u pacran c'aticob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s. Caj ya'arajob mac cu bin c'ubic Jes√∫s.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic a mac jach no'j  åc åtan tu wich C'uj
\p 
\v 24 U cams åwinicob caj u pacran ts'ictarob soc yiricob a mac jach no'j ich u rac'ob.
\v 25 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïIch yoc'ocab a reyo' ti' jujuntur u ru'umin, cu ts'urintic u winiquirob. U c'at u winiquirob ca' ya'arejob ti' ca' yamtac a reyo'. Baxuc u ca' ts'urir u c'at yubejob xan.
\v 26 Aro' m å' baxuc ca betiquex. A mac jach no'j ich techex, arej m å' u pachtej yubej ya'ara' jach no'jech ten u rac'ob. Wa ca wocar techex a ts'urintic tu cu c'ujintic C'uj toc y ån a yamtiquex a rac'ob.
\v 27 Qui' tucrex a ba' quin wac techex. Mac jach no'je', wa ra' cu jan ån ich u pojche'ir u jan ån? Wa ra' jach no'j a cu beyaj ti'? M å' ja wirej, a mac a cu cutar tu pojche'ir u jan ån, raji' jach no'j. Chen a teno' cax a ts'urirenex ti' y ånen ich techex quir in beyaj techex.
\p 
\v 28 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïTechex rajra' ti' y ånechex tu y ånen m å' ja p' åtenexi' p'eri' quic muc'tiquex a ba' cu tar to'onex uch.
\v 29 An ten bic in Tet C'uj caj u teten quir in reyintic. Baxuc techex in tetiquechex quir a wocarex a reyintiquex.
\v 30 Baxuc quin tetic techex soc p'eri' quic jan ånex. Baxuc p'eri' ij cuc'urex tu pojche'ir ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin in reyintic. Quin bin in wacsiquechex a reyintiquex a wet winiquirob jud√≠o a doce u yo'nen u winiquirob Israel.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' Pedro: Je' a wa'aric m å' a c' å'oreni'
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.31‚Äë35; Mr.‚ÄØ14.27‚Äë31; Jn.‚ÄØ13.36‚Äë38)
\p 
\v 31 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' Pedro:
\p ‚ÄïWa mac cu chachtic yo'och cu p'at år u b åq'uer chen u soro' cu puric. Baxuquech Sim√≥n ‚Äïquen‚Äï, a quisino' caj u c'ataj ti' C'uj quir u tumtic a wor soc yiric wa taj caj a wacsaj ta wor.
\v 32 Chen a teno' caj in t' ånaj C'uj ti' tech soc m å' a p' åtic a wacsic ta wor ten. Ca' bin ts'ocac a c'axic a wor toc chichquintej yor a wet cams åwinicob a te' y åna'.
\p 
\v 33 Pedro caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, tin toc ch'uctic in bin yejerech tu cu ma'c år winic cax quet ij quimin.
\p 
\v 34 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' Pedro:
\p ‚ÄïTaj quin wa'aric tech. M å' toy c' åyn åc cax baje'rer ac'bir. M åna' u nup ca bin a wa'aric m å' a c' å'oreni'. Cu ts'ocor a wac m å' a c' å'oreni' cu bin u c'ay cax.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj: Tabar u q'uinin in muc'yaj
\p 
\v 35 Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïCaj in tuchi'techex ca'ch quir a tsec'tiquex in t' ån. Cax m åna' a chimex. Cax m åna' a taq'uinex cax m åna' a xanabex. Y ån wa ba' a c'atex ca'ch?
\p U cams åwinicob caj u nuncajob:
\p ‚ÄïM åna' ba' in c'atob.
\p 
\v 36 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïChen baje'rer, wa y ån a taq'uinex toc ch'a'ex. Baxuc wa y ån a chimex toc ch'a'ex. Wa m åna' techex a mascab canex u ca' yarir a noc' quir a m ånic turiri' a mascab.
\v 37 M å' ja wirej ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, ti' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj uch, caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúA winiquirob caj ya'araj chen c'as a ray xibo'.‚Äù Aro' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, quin wac techex. Y ån in nupsej quire' tabar in quinsa'.
\p 
\v 38 Caj ya'arob u cams åwinic:
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, a je' mascaba' ca'tura'.
\p Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTi' ti' a mascabex.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu t' ånic C'uj ich u p'uc witsir u c'aba' Olivos
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.36‚Äë46; Mr.‚ÄØ14.32‚Äë42)
\p 
\v 39 Jes√∫s caj joc' ich u cajar caj binij an ten bic nanij u bin ich u p'uc witsir u c'aba' Olivos. Yet binac u cams åwinicob.
\v 40 Caj c'uchij tu nanij u bin, caj ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob:
\p ‚ÄïT' ånex C'uj soc m å' u cha'ba' u tar tumbir a worex.
\p 
\v 41 Jes√∫s caj joc' nanach an ten bic mun nachir cu rubur tunich a cu ch'inin ten mac. Caj xonr åj quir u t' ånic C'uj.
\v 42 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïIn Tetech C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, wa ra' cu qui'quintic a wor quir a ts'icten a ba' in c'at, ruc'sej a je' muc'yaja' a cu bin tar ten. Wa ra' a c'at ca' muc'yajn åquen je' in muc'yaje' quire' in c'at in betic a ba' a c'at tech.
\p 
\v 43 Caj tar turiri' y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj ich Jes√∫s quir u ts'ab år u muc' ti'.
\v 44 Caj jach muc'yajn åjij Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u muc'yaj jach manan tu cu t' ånic C'uj. Tan u jach chichquintic u t' ånic C'uj hasta cu q'uicab. U q'uicabe' irej u q'uiq'uer cu ch'ojar ich ru'um. Jach carem u ch'ojar.
\p 
\v 45 Caj riq'uij tub xonr åj tu cu t' ånic C'uj. Caj bin ich u cams åwinicob caj yiraj tan u wen ånob quire' m å' qui' yorobi'.
\v 46 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån wen ånex. Ca' a ch'ictarex soc a y ån t' åniquex C'uj soc m å' u cha'b år u tar tumbir a worex.
\s1 Chuc Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.47‚Äë56; Mr.‚ÄØ14.43‚Äë50; Jn.‚ÄØ18.2‚Äë11)
\p 
\v 47 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s. Caj c'uchob a pimob quire' pay ten Judas. Raji' turiri' ich cams åwinicob a docejo'. Caj u n åts' u b åj Judas quir u ts'uts'ic u p'uc Jes√∫s.
\v 48 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' Judas:
\p ‚ÄïTan wa ja ts'uts'ic in p'uc quir a c'ubiquen ti' a mac a cu p'actiquenob? A teno' baxuquenechexo' C'uj.
\p 
\v 49 U cams åwinicob a ti' y ån yicnan Jes√∫s caj u yirob ba' u ber ti', caj u ya'arob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïArej to'on Jaj Ts'urir ca' ts'icaco'on yejerob ca' ic ch' åquej u car yejer mascab.
\p 
\v 50 Turiri' u cams åwinicob caj u ch' åcaj u xiquin, raji' u c'urew u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Caj u rac ch' åctaj u xiquin, tu noj.
\v 51 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïTsire'ej, m å' a ch' åquiquex.
\p Jes√∫s caj u t åra u xiquin u c'urew u jach ts'urir sacerdote caj jawij u xiquin tu ch'aquij.
\v 52 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer u y åjt' ånin polic√≠a ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, yejer u jach ts'urirob u cajar u winiquirob jud√≠o. Quire' tarob u chuquejob Jes√∫s. Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïTarechex a chuquiquenex yejer a mascabex yejer che'. Irej wa y åja'cr åy åjiren ba', ca chuquiquenex.
\v 53 Rajra' ti' y ånen ich carem naj uch. Tan in camsicob, chen m å' ta chuquenex. Chen tarechex a chuquenex quire' c'uchij tin q'uin. An ten bic C'uj caj ya'araj uch. C'uchij tin q'uin xan, quire' baxuc u c'at a quisino' a mac a cu ts'urintic a mac a cu man ich yac'birir quire' ra' u si'pirob.
\s1 Pedro cu ya'aric m å' u c' å'otic Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.57‚Äë58, 69‚Äë75; Mr.‚ÄØ14.53‚Äë54, 66‚Äë72; Jn.‚ÄØ18.12‚Äë18, 25‚Äë27)
\p 
\v 54 Caj u chucob Jes√∫s caj u m åchob u c' åb caj binob u purej ich yatoch u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Chen Pedro caj tar tu pach Jes√∫s chen nach cu xur.
\v 55 Caj c'uchob caj ocob tu re'a'an u chi' naj. Ti' tu t' åbaj u q'uich chumuc. Caj curajob tu q'uich. P'eri' yejer Pedro.
\v 56 Ti' y ån xquic u c'urew u jach ts'urir sacerdote caj irir Pedro ti' cura'an q'uich ich chi' c'ac'. Caj u qui' p åctaj caj u ya'araj ti' a mac ti' y ånob:
\p ‚ÄïA je' xiba' u yet man Jes√∫s uch.
\p 
\v 57 Pedro caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïXquic ‚Äïquen‚Äï, m å' in c' å'orm åni'.
\p 
\v 58 Sasam caj irir Pedro ten u jer caj ara'b ten xib ti' Pedro:
\p ‚ÄïA techo' ‚Äïquij‚Äï, caj a chaj nupintej Jes√∫s ca'ch, ti' y ånech yejer Jes√∫s uch.
\p Chen Pedro caj ya'araj ti' xib:
\p ‚ÄïM å' teni'.
\p 
\v 59 Caj manij turiri' hora caj c'uch u jer xib caj chich ara'b ti' u rac'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTaj a je' xiba' ti' y ån ich Jes√∫s uch. Quire' ti' u tar ich u ru'umin Galilea quire' baxuc u t' ånobob.
\p 
\v 60 Chen Pedro caj ya'araj ti' xib:
\p ‚ÄïM å' in wer mac a ca wa'arico'.
\p Ti' toy cu tsicbar Pedro, seb caj c'ayn åj cax.
\v 61 A Jaj Ts'uro' caj u sut u b åj u p åcaj Pedro. Pedro caj c'aj ti' a ba' ara'b ti' ten Jes√∫s ca'ch. An bic caj ya'araj Jes√∫s: ‚ÄúM å' toy c'ayn åc a caxo' m åna' u nup ca bin a wac m å' a c' å'oreni'.‚Äù
\v 62 Caj joc' Pedro ich yatoch u jach ts'urir sacerdote caj chich oc'n åjij quire' tucur u ca'.
\s1 P'asta'b Jes√∫s jats' xan
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.67‚Äë68; Mr.‚ÄØ14.65)
\p 
\v 63 A polic√≠ajo' a cu beyajob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj a ju chucm ånob Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u p'asticob Jes√∫s tan u j åts'icob xan.
\v 64 Robob tu pixob u wich Jes√∫s caj u raxob caj u ya'arob ti':
\p ‚ÄïQuire' y åjtseq'uirech u t' ån C'uj, arej tenob mac tu raxech?
\p 
\v 65 Caj ya'arob ya'ab ba' tu cu p'asticob Jes√∫s.
\s1 Tu cotorob u ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o cu ta'quicob u jo'r Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.59‚Äë66; Mr.‚ÄØ14.55‚Äë64; Jn.‚ÄØ18.19‚Äë24)
\p 
\v 66 Caj sasij caj u much'quintajob u b åj u ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o. Quet baxucob u ts'urirob sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Caj u much'quintajob u b åj quir u ta'quicob u jo'r Jes√∫s. Robob caj u p åyob ca' tac Jes√∫s. Caj c'uchij Jes√∫s caj u c'atob ti' Jes√∫s:
\p 
\v 67 ‚ÄïWa Cristojech caj u tuchi'tech C'uj, arej tenob?
\p Chen Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti'ob, caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïWa quin wa'aric Cristojen caj u tuchi'ten C'uj, m å' ja bin a wacsiquex ta worex ten.
\v 68 Wa quin c'atiquex techex ba', m å' a bin a nunquiquex ten.
\v 69 Ca' bin ts'ocac in riq'uir tin quimirir ti' quin bin in cutar tu noj C'uj soc ten cu bin u ts'urintiquen tu cotor mac. P'eri' quin ts'urintic yejer C'uj a caj u tuchi'tajen C'uj.
\p 
\v 70 Tu cotor u ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o caj u c'atajob:
\p ‚ÄïArej tenob wa ju jach pararech C'uj?
\p Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïAn ten bic caj a wa'arex sam, raji'en.
\p 
\v 71 Caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïBa' wir u jer y åjta'quic u jo'r. Tic toc u'yaj. Poch' u ca' quire' u b åjiri' caj u ya'araj.
\c 23
\s1 Ti' cu bin Jes√∫s  åc åtan Pilato
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.1‚Äë2, 11‚Äë14; Mr.‚ÄØ15.1‚Äë5; Jn.‚ÄØ18.28‚Äë38)
\p 
\v 1 P'eri' caj r åc ric'ob caj binob purej Jes√∫s  åc åtan Pilato.
\v 2 U ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o caj u y ånxchun u ta'quicob u jo'r Jes√∫s caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïTs'oc in wiricob soc u quinsa' Jes√∫s. M å' ja wirej, caj u p'usaj yorob u winiquirob jud√≠o. Quire' cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúM å' tsoy a bo'otiquex u taq'uin a ru'umex ti' u rey C√©sar.‚Äù Baxuc xan, u b åjiri' cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúCristojen, a caj u tuchi'ten C'uj quir u reyintiquen mac.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Pilato, caj u c'ata' ti':
\p ‚ÄïArej ten wa ju reyech u winiquirob jud√≠o?
\p Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti':
\p ‚ÄïAn ten bic tech caj a wa'araj sam, raji'en.
\p 
\v 4 Pilato caj u ya'araj ti' u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer a pimob caj u much'quintob u b åj:
\p ‚ÄïM å' jin wiraj u si'pir a je' xiba'.
\p 
\v 5 Caj u p'enc åch arob ba' u winiquirob jud√≠o:
\p ‚ÄïCaj u jach p'usaj yorob u winiquirob jud√≠o tu cu camsic ti'ob. Caj u y ånxchun u camsic ich u ru'umin Galilea. Baxuc ich tu cotor u cajar Judea hasta c'uchij tera' xan.
\s1 Ti' y ån Jes√∫s  åc åtan Herodes
\p 
\v 6 Pilato caj yubaj a ba' caj u ya'arajob y åjta'quirob u jo'r Jes√∫s. Caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTi' wa ju tar a je' xiba' ich u ru'umin Galilea?
\p 
\v 7 Caj u yuba ya'ara' ti' u tar ich u ru'umin Galilea. Caj ya'araj ca' xic purbir Jes√∫s ich Herodes quir u ta'quicob u jo'r. Quire' raji' gobernador ich u ru'umin Galilea. Quire' ti' c'uchij Herodes ich u cajar Jerusal√©n.
\v 8 Caj c'uchij Jes√∫s ich Herodes, jach qui' yor Herodes quire' uch u chen c'at yiric Jes√∫s quire' cu pachtic yirej ca' esac ti' carem beyaj Herodes. Quire' cu yubic u tsib åticob a pimob a ba' cu betic Jes√∫s.
\v 9 Cax ya'ab ba' caj u c'ataj Herodes ti' Jes√∫s. M å' baj c' ås nunca'b ti'.
\v 10 U jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj tarob ch'ictarob  åc åtan Herodes quir u ta'quicob u jo'r Jes√∫s. C'am u t' ånob.
\v 11 Herodes, caj u p'astaj Jes√∫s yejer tu cotor u ts'urirob soldadojo' caj u chejtajob ti'. Caj u t åcajob u noc' a tsoyo' soc irej rey. Caj ts'oc u t åquicob u noc' caj w åc' ås tuchi'ta'b Jes√∫s ich Pilato.
\v 12 Ra'iri' u q'uinin Pilato yejer Herodes caj u yajquintajob u b åj quire' a ucho' cu p'acticob u b åj.
\s1 Pilato cu ya'aric: Jes√∫s y ån u quimin
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.15‚Äë26; Mr.‚ÄØ15.6‚Äë15; Jn.‚ÄØ18.39‚Äï19.16)
\p 
\v 13 Pilato caj u much'quintaj u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer u jach ts'urirob u cajar u winiquirob jud√≠o yejer a pimob. Tu cu ta'quicob u jo'r Jes√∫s uch.
\v 14 Pilato caj u ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïTarex a puric a je' xiba'  åc åtan ten. Caj a wa'arajex caj u p'usaj yor u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj ts'oc in c åxtic in wirej wa y ån u si'pir, m å' tin wiraj u si'pir turiri' a ca ta'quiquex u jo'r.
\v 15 A m å' Herodeso' caj u yiraj u si'pir xan. Rajen caj u w åc' ås tuchi'taj to'onex. M åna' ba' caj u betaj quir u quinsa'.
\v 16 Baje'rer quin bin in wac u j åts'ob u pach. Cu ts'ocar u jats' år ca' sipac ca' xic Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 17 Caj ya'araj baxuco' quire' nanij u sipic mac Herodes, rajra' cu c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui'qui' jan ån, ra' u q'uinin pascua.
\v 18 Chen tu cotor mac caj u c'amquintajob u t' ån, caj ya'arajob:
\p ‚ÄïQuinsej a ra xibo'. Ij c'at ca' a siptej Barrab√°s.
\p 
\v 19 A je' Barrab√°sa' caj chuquij caj maquij tu cu ma'c år winic uch quire' caj u p'usaj yorob mac ich u cajar quir u joc'sicob u ts'urir u cajar. Bayiri' caj u quinsaj mac xan.
\v 20 Pilato u c'at u siptic ca' xic Jes√∫s, rajen tu ca' t' ånaj a pimo'.
\v 21 A pimo' caj u ca' purajob u t' ån. C'am caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïSinej ich cruz.
\p Ca' ten caj u ca' arob:
\p ‚ÄïSinej ich cruz ‚Äïquij.
\p 
\v 22 M åna' u nup u tenin caj ya'araj Pilato:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin y ån in sinic ich cruz? Arex ten ba' c'asir caj u betaj? A teno' m å' jin wiraj u si'pir quir u quinsa'. Rajen quin bin in wa'aric u jats' år u pach. Cu ts'ocar u jats' år u pach, cu chab år ca' xic.
\p 
\v 23 Chen a pimo' caj u ts' åraj u pach Pilato, caj u chich araj ti' Pilato:
\p ‚ÄïSinej ich cruz.
\p Quire' c'am yaw åt t' ånob.
\v 24 Pilato caj u quibaj u t' ån. Rajen Pilato caj u ya'araj ca' quinsac Jes√∫s soc u betic a ba' u c'atob u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\v 25 Pilato caj u siptaj Barrab√°s, a mac chuca'an uch cax ra' caj u p'usaj yorob u rac'ob quir u joc'sicob u ts'urir u cajar cax caj u quinsaj mac. Chen Jes√∫s caj u c'ubaj ca' quinsa' ten u soldado quire' baxuc u c'at u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\s1 A soldadojo' u winiquirob romano, raji'ob caj u b åjajob Jes√∫s ich cruz
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.32‚Äë44; Mr.‚ÄØ15.21‚Äë32; Jn.‚ÄØ19.17‚Äë27)
\p 
\v 26 U soldado u winiquirob romano, caj u joc'sajob Jes√∫s quir u quinsicob. Caj u chucob turiri' xib u c'aba' Sim√≥n. Ti' u tar caj urij tancab tu cajar. Ti' u tar uch ich u cajar Cirene uch. Caj ts'ar u pach u c'ochej u cruz Jes√∫s. Pachir u bin a Sim√≥no'. Jes√∫s p åyber.
\p 
\v 27 Baxuc xan, ya'ab mac caj binob tu pach Jes√∫s. Ti' y ån xquic ich a pimob a cu tarob tu pach Jes√∫s. Aw åt oc'ar u ca'ob quire' cu tucricob Jes√∫s.
\v 28 Jes√∫s caj u sut u b åj u p åctic u pach quir u t' ånic a xquico':
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' u xquiquirechex u cajar Jerusal√©n. M å' a wac'tiquenex. Ca' a wactex a w åc' ås b åjiri'ex yejer a pararex.
\v 29 Taj quin wac techex je' u c'uchur tu q'uinin cu bin ya'aric mac: ‚ÄúJach tsoy a xquico' a m å' pararn åjij. Quire' m å' c'ucha'an yor ti'. Bayiri' a m å' tu rochaj u parar. Bayiri' jach tsoy a xquico' a m åna' u chan och quir u ts'ic chu'ch.‚Äù
\v 30 Ra'iri' u q'uinin cu bin u chich aric ca' quimic, irej a cu ya'aricob mac. Ca' rubuc a witso' ich yoc'orob ca' max åcob. Bayiri' cu t' ånicob p'uc witso' ca' mucucob, ten p'uc wits.
\v 31 Wa cu quinsiquenob cax m åna' in si'pir chen jach manan cu bin u muc'yajob ich u winiquirob jud√≠o quire' c'as caj u betajob.
\p 
\v 32 Caj bin purbir Jes√∫s quir u quinsa', yet binacob ca'tur xib a cu yacr å ba' quir u quinsa'ob xan.
\v 33 Caj r åc c'uchob tu p åcha'an u c'aba' u baquer u jo'r mac quire' a ru'umo' irej u baquer u jo'r mac. Ti' caj u b åjob ich cruz, Jes√∫s a baxuc a cu yacr å ba' ca'turo' caj sinob ich u cruzob. Turi' tu noj Jes√∫s, turi' tu ts'ic Jes√∫s.
\v 34 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti' C'uj wa ber tan u bajarob ich cruz:
\p ‚ÄïIn Tetech ‚Äïquij‚Äï, jawse u si'pirob a mac a cu p'actiquenob quire' m å' yerob ba' cu beticob ten ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p U soldado u winiquirob romano caj u j åsob u noc' Jes√∫s caj u y år åc'tajob chan tunich quir yiric mac cu bin u ch'ic u noc' Jes√∫s, baxuc nanij u beticob uch.
\v 35 Tarob ya'ab mac quir u chen p åcticob u quimin Jes√∫s. U ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o caj u yuts'ajob u ni' quire' tan u p'asticob Jes√∫s, caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïU jer caj u tacaj; chen u b åjiri' m å' tu tacaj u b åj, wa jach jaj a Cristojo', a tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj quir u taquic tu cotor mac ca' u w åc' ås tac u b åj xan.
\p 
\v 36 U soldado u winiquirob romano, caj u chejtajob Jes√∫s quire' caj n åts'ob u b åj ich Jes√∫s caj u ts'ajob ti' Jes√∫s u c'ab uva a p åje' ca' u yuq'uej.
\v 37 Caj ya'arob ti':
\p ‚ÄïWa ju jach u reyech u winiquirob jud√≠o, toc tac a b åj baje'rer.
\p 
\v 38 Ti' ts'iba'an a je' t' åna' ich c' ås chumuc u cruz u jo'r Jes√∫s soc yer biquinin sinij ich cruz. Caj ts'ibta'b: ‚ÄúA je' xiba' u rey u winiquirob jud√≠o.‚Äù
\p 
\v 39 Turiri' cu yacr å ba' ti' sina'an ich Jes√∫s caj u p'astaj Jes√∫s tan ya'aric:
\p ‚ÄïWa jach taj Cristojech toc tac a b åj yejerenob baje'rer.
\p 
\v 40 Chen u jer u yet b åja'an Jes√∫s caj u q'ueyaj u yet acr å ba' caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïM å' tan a ch'ic saj åquir ti' C'uj. M å' wa quet caj b åjo'on yejer Jes√∫s quir ij quimin xan?
\v 41 A to'ono' ‚Äïquij ya'ara' ti'‚Äï, taj caj u tacaj ic jo'rob, rajen tan ic jach muc'yaj quire' ra' u bo'orir ic si'pir. Chen a je' xiba' m åna' ba' caj u betaj quir u quinsa'.
\p 
\v 42 Caj ya'araj ti' Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïJes√∫s ‚Äïquij‚Äï, chan c' å'ote ten ca' bin c'uchech tu ca reyintic.
\p 
\v 43 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti':
\p ‚ÄïTaj quin wa'aric tech baje'rer ti' y ånech yejeren ich C'uj.
\s1 Caj quimij Jes√∫s
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.45‚Äë56; Mr.‚ÄØ15.33‚Äë41; Jn.‚ÄØ19.28‚Äë30)
\p 
\v 44 Caj c'uchij c'ac'chunq'uin caj ac' å'ch åjij ich tu cotor ru'umin. Hasta las tres caj sasich åjij.
\v 45 Ti' toy ac'bir ic yum caj jatij u noq'uir tub t'ina'an ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Rajen jat chumuc u noq'uir tub t'ina'an quire' caj u yesaj to'on bic tabar ic bin  åc åtan C'uj. M å' ja wirej, a ucho' m å' c'ucha'an yor mac u je'ic u noq'uir quir u yocar  åc åtan C'uj tu cu ya'aricob ti' y ån C'uj. Chen raji' cu yocar a ucho' u jach ts'urir sacerdote. Teni' cu yocar turiri' yaxq'uin.
\v 46 Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj quimij Jes√∫s caj jat u noq'uir ti' t'ina'an. C'am caj aw åtn åjij Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïIn Tet C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, tan in ts'ic tech in pixam quir a c ånantic.
\p Caj ts'oc ya'aric caj quimij.
\p 
\v 47 A y åjt' ånino' cien soldado u winiquirob romano, caj yiraj ba' u ber ti' Jes√∫s caj u c'ujintaj C'uj caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïJach jaj a je' xiba' m åna' u si'pir toc taj yor.
\p 
\v 48 Ya'ab mac caj tarob uch quir yiricob u quinsa'r Jes√∫s. Caj ts'oc yiricob ba' u ber caj sutn åjob tu yatochob. Caj u p åxajob u semob quire' tan yesicob tucur u ca'ob quire' baxuc nanij u beticob u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\v 49 Tu cotor mac a yet manob Jes√∫s uch. Baxuc yejer a xquicob a tarob tu pach Jes√∫s ich u cajar Galilea. Caj yirob ba' u ber ti' Jes√∫s nanach chica'anob caj yirob Jes√∫s.
\s1 Caj chaquinta'b u baquer Jes√∫s ich japnin tunich
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.57‚Äë61; Mr.‚ÄØ15.42‚Äë47; Jn.‚ÄØ19.38‚Äë42)
\p 
\v 50 Ti' y ån ca'ch turiri' xib, ti' u tar ich u cajar Arimatea, ra' u wa'an u ru'umin Judea. Jos√© u c'aba'. Raji' turiri' u ts'urir u winiquirob jud√≠o. Jach tsoy yor Jos√©, Jos√© cu quibic a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån Mois√©s.
\v 51 M å' ja wirej, a Jos√©jo', tan u pajic u q'uinin cu tuchi'tic mac C'uj quir u reyinticob u winiquirob jud√≠o. Raji' cu pajic Jos√©. A Jos√©jo', m å' quet yor u c'ubic quinsbir Jes√∫s yejer u yet jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\v 52 Caj bin Jos√© ich Pilato quir u c'atic u baquer Jes√∫s.
\v 53 Pilato caj u ts'aj u baquer Jes√∫s ti' Jos√© quir u but'ic u baquer ich japnin tunich Jos√©, cu ya'araj ti' mac:
\p ‚ÄïEnsej u baquer Jes√∫s.
\p Caj ts'oc u yensa' caj u tapaj yejer s åc noc', lino u c'aba' u noq'uir, jach co'oj aro'. Caj bin u but'ej ich japnin tunich tu ric'ben, m åna' mac u but'm åni'.
\v 54 Ba' u ber ti' Jes√∫s. Ra' u q'uinin cu ch åquic yoch quir u qui'qui' jan ånob u q'uinin pascua. Raji' tabar u c'uchur tu q'uinin quir u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o.
\p 
\v 55 A xquico' a tarob ich u pach Jes√∫s caj ruq'uij ich u ru'umin Galilea caj binob tu pach Jos√© soc u yiricob u but'ur u baquer Jes√∫s ich japnin tunich.
\v 56 A xquico' caj ts'oc yiricob u but'ur u baquer Jes√∫s. Caj urob ich yatoch ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Caj u m ånob a qui' u boque' soc u cho'icob ich u baquer Jes√∫s. Raji' u ts'ac mirra u c'aba' yejer u ts'ac aloe u c'aba' quire' nanij u winiquir jud√≠o, u cho'ic ich u baquer a mac quimeno'. A xquico' caj u jesajob u b åj ti' u beyaj. Quire' ra' u q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o. An ten bic cu ya'aric tu ts'iba'an u t' ån Mois√©s.
\c 24
\s1 Riq'uij Jes√∫s tu quimen
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ28.1‚Äë10; Mr.‚ÄØ16.1‚Äë8; Jn.‚ÄØ20.1‚Äë10)
\p 
\v 1 U q'uinin u y ånxchun semana, jach a'ac'bir a xquico' caj w åc' ås binob tu but' u baquer Jes√∫s. Caj u cuchob a qui' u boque a caj u m ånajob.
\v 2 Caj c'uchob a xquico' caj yirob toc b åc' åsa'an u tunichir u mac u jor tu but'ij Jes√∫s.
\v 3 Caj ocob tu japnin tunich tu but'ij Jes√∫s. Chen m å' caj u yirob u baquer.
\v 4 A xquico' xaca'an u tucurob quire' yirob m åna' u baquer Jes√∫s. Seb caj yirob ti' y ån ca'tur xib tu ch'ica'anob xquic. U buquim ånob u noc' jach s åc t'inen.
\v 5 A xquico' caj chinrajob u jo'r quire' saj åcob. A xibo' caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïCa tarechex a c åxtex tu but' u baquer Jes√∫s?
\v 6 M å' ti' y ån a tera' baje'rer quire' riq'uij tu quimen, cuxa'an baje'rer. M å' wa c'ajtechex ba' caj u ya'araj techex uch. Ti' toy y ånechex ich u ru'umin Galilea.
\v 7 C'ajtechex caj ya'araj: ‚ÄúY ån in quinsa'r, a teno', quij Jes√∫s, quire' caj u tuchi'ten C'uj a baxuquechexo'. A mac jach c'aso', raji' cu bin u b åjiquenob ich cruz. Ca' bin ts'ocac in quinsa' quin bin in riq'uir, m åna' u nup u q'uinin.‚Äù Baxuc caj ya'araj Jes√∫s uch.
\p 
\v 8 A xquico' caj u c' å'otajob u t' ån Jes√∫s uch.
\v 9 Caj urob tu bin yirob tu but' u baquer Jes√∫s caj binob ich a oncejo' u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s. Baxuc ti' y ånob a yet manob Jes√∫s uche'. Caj u ya'arob ti' a ba' caj u yirob yejer a ba' caj u yubob.
\v 10 A xquico' a mac binob ca'ch quir ya'aricob ti' u cams åwinicob cuxa'an Jes√∫s. Raji'ob, Mar√≠a, a cu tar ti' u cajar Magdalena, yejer Juana, yejer Mar√≠a, u n å' Jacob yejer u jer m å' ya'ab xquic.
\v 11 Chen u cams åwinicob m å' ju quibob a ba' caj ara'b ti'ob: ‚ÄúRiq'uij Jes√∫s.‚Äù Cu chen tucricob a ba' caj u yubob ya'aric a xquic quire' yerob u sosoc a'bar.
\p 
\v 12 A Pedrojo', seb caj riq'uij caj u c' ånaj yacab caj bin yiric tu but'ij u baquer Jes√∫s. Caj c'uchij caj u tac ch'enaptaj caj u yiraj u noq'uir tu top u baquer uch. Chen u noq'uir y ån ich u way. Caj sutn åj tu junan ich yatoch jach jac'a'an yor a ba' caj u yiraj.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u yes åj u b åj ti' u cams åwinicob ca'turo' ich u berir Ema√∫s
\r (Mr.‚ÄØ16.12‚Äë13)
\p 
\v 13 Ra'iri' u q'uinin ca'turob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s, caj binob tu berir u cajar Ema√∫s. Y ån once kil√≥metros u nachir ti' u cajar Jerusal√©n.
\v 14 Caj pacran tsicbn åjob tu cu binob ich bej. Caj tsicbn åjob ti' a ba' u ber ti' Jes√∫s.
\v 15 Ti' toy cu tsicbarob ich bej tan u chich tsicbarob. Jes√∫s caj u c' ås n åts'aj u b åj ich u cams åwinicob soc quet u binob.
\v 16 U cams åwinicob m å' yerob wa Jes√∫s quire' m å' ts'a'b u t' ånin u c' å'ota'r ten u cams åwinicob.
\v 17 Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBa' ca chich tsicb åtiquex ich a ber? Biquinin tucurex a caj tu ca binex ich bej?
\p 
\v 18 Turiri' ich a winico' u c'aba' Cleofas caj u nuncaj ti' caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïA je' q'uina' tu cotor mac ich u cajar Jerusal√©n yerob ba' u ber a tera'. Cax jamach ti' y ånech ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Tin t' ån jari' teche', m å' a wer ba' u ber Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 19 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj:
\p ‚ÄïBa' u ber tera'? Raji'ob caj u nuncajob ti', caj ya'arajob. M å' wa ta wu'yaj ba' u ber ti' Jes√∫s a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret? Raji' y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj. A Jes√∫so' caj u qui'quintaj yor C'uj. Baxuc a pimo' caj u qui'quintaj yorob. Quire' caj u yirob u carem beyaj Jes√∫s. Baxuc a ba' caj u camsaj.
\v 20 M å' wa caj a wu'yaj ‚Äïquij ya'ara' ti'‚Äï u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer u jach ts'urirob u cajar a nuxibo', bic caj u c'ubajob Jes√∫s ti' Pilato caj ts'oc u ta'quicob u jo'r. Caj ara'b u bin b åjbir ich cruz.
\v 21 Baje'rer ‚Äïquij ya'ara' ti'‚Äï, y ån tres u q'uinin tu ts'oc u baj år Jes√∫s ich cruz. A tenob tan in pajicob wa raji' tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj quir u taquico'onex u winiquirob jud√≠o ti' u winiquirob romano.
\v 22 Bayiri' ‚Äïquij ya'araj‚Äï, xquic a p'eri'o' yejero'on caj u jac's in worob quire' a'ac'bir caj binob yirejob tu but' u baquer Jes√∫s.
\v 23 Caj c'uchob m å' ju yirob u baquer, caj sutn åjob tu y ånenob caj tsicb ån åjob tenob an ten bic tu jach irob y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj a mac caj u ya'araj ti'ob cuxa'an Jes√∫s.
\v 24 Bayiri' xib xan tres a p'eri'o'enob yejerob caj bin yirob tu but' u baquer. Caj yirob taj a ba' ara'b ten a xquicobo'. Chen m å' ju yirob Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 25 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin jach chichex a jo'rex quire' qui' ts'abir ca wacsiquex a worex quire' m å' ja wacsajex ta worex a ba' ts'ibta'b ten y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj uch.
\v 26 A werex jach taj y ån u muc'yaj Cristo quire' baxuc u c'at C'uj soc u bin s åjta'bir ten tu cotor mac.
\p 
\v 27 Jes√∫s caj u qui' camsaj ti'ob a ba' ara'b ti' tu cotor ich u t' ån C'uj ti' u w åc' ås b åjiri' ich tu cotor u t' ån C'uj. Caj u y ånxchun tub ts'iba'an ich u t' ån Mois√©s. Caj ts'oc u qui' camsic ti'ob a ba' ara'b ti' ten Mois√©s. Caj u qui' camsaj ti'ob a ba' ara'b ti' ten y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj uch.
\p 
\v 28 Tabar u c'uchurob tu cajar tu cu binob ca'ch. Jes√∫s irej wa bin u ca' u potmastej u cajar.
\v 29 Chen u cams åwinicob caj u chich arob ti' caj ya'arob:
\p ‚ÄïP'aten yejero'on, tabar u bin q'uin quire' tabar u yac'birch åj år.
\p Rajen Jes√∫s caj oquij quir u p'at år yejerob.
\v 30 Caj ts'oc u cutarob quir u jan ånob. Jes√∫s caj u chucaj u yoch pan caj ya'araj ti' C'uj:
\p ‚ÄïBayo' ‚Äïquij.
\p Caj u xat'aj caj u ts'aj ti'ob quir u janticob.
\v 31 Caj ts'a'b u t' ånin quir u c' å'oticob Jes√∫s seb caj binij Jes√∫s m å' ju yirob tu binij.
\v 32 Caj u pacraj arob:
\p ‚ÄïJach qui' ij cor ca'ch caj u tsicb åta to'on ich bej, caj u qui' tsicb åta to'on u t' ån C'uj, tu ts'iba'an.
\p 
\v 33 A ca'turo' u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s, ra'iri' u q'uinin seb caj w åc' ås urob ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Caj c'uchob tu much'a'an a oncejo' u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s yejer u jerob u rac'ob.
\v 34 A oncejo' caj ya'arajob ti' a tan tu c'uchurob:
\p ‚ÄïJach jaj ic Jaj Ts'ur, riq'uij tu quimen quire' Jes√∫s caj tu yes u b åj ti' Sim√≥n.
\p 
\v 35 A tan tu c'uchurob caj u tsicb åtajob a ba' u ber ti'ob ich u berir Ema√∫s. Caj u c' å'otajob Jes√∫s caj xat'aj u yo'och pan ti'ob.
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u yesaj u b åj ti' u jerob u cams åwinicob
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ28.16‚Äë20; Mr.‚ÄØ16.14‚Äë18; Jn.‚ÄØ20.19‚Äë23)
\p 
\v 36 Ti' toy cu tsicbarob a ba' u ber ti'ob. Seb caj ch'icraj Jes√∫s chumuc tu y ånob u cams åwinicob. Caj ara'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s:
\p ‚ÄïCa' qui'ac a worex ten C'uj ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s.
\p 
\v 37 Chen u cams åwinicob jach jaq'uij yorob caj u ch'aj sajquirob. Cu tucricob ca'ch caj u yirob u pixam a mac quimeno'.
\v 38 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin sajquechex? Biquinin ca tucriquex ta worex: Mac a je'ra'?
\v 39 P åctex a wirex in c' åb yejer in woc soc a werex ten. T årex a wu'yex wa ten quire' u pixam mac m åna' u b åq'uer an ten biquen y ån in b åq'uer. M åna' u baquer an ten biquen.
\p 
\v 40 Caj ts'oc ya'aric ti'ob aro' caj u yesaj u c' åb ti'ob soc yiricob tu b åja'an yoc yejer u c' åb.
\v 41 Quire' jach qui' yorob, rajen m å' ju quibob wa raji' quire' jac'a'an yorob xan. Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïChan chuquej ten a wochex in jantej.
\p 
\v 42 Robob caj u ts'ajob ti' u xet'er c'ac'bir c åy quir u chi'ic caj u y årob ti' cab.
\v 43 Jes√∫s caj u c' åmaj caj u chi'aj c åy  åc åtan tu y ånob baxuc cab caj u m åc'aj.
\v 44 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïA ba' caj in wa'araj techex ti' y ånen ta wicn ånex ca'ch. Caj in wa'araj techex ca'ch, y ån in nupsic tu cotor a bar ts'iba'an ich u t' ån Mois√©s. Baxuc a ts'iba'an ich u t' ån y åjtseq'uirob u t' ån C'uj. Baxuc a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån salmos.
\p 
\v 45 Ra'iri' u q'uinin Jes√∫s caj u ts'aj ti'ob ca' u najtejob a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj ti' Jes√∫s.
\v 46 Jes√∫s caj ya'araj ti'ob:
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc a je' ts'iba'an ti': ‚ÄúCristo a tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj. Y ån u quimij, caj ts'oc u quimij cu man m åna' u nup u q'uinin cu riq'uir ti' u quimirir, quire' a Cristojo', u parar C'uj.
\v 47 A techexo' y ån a bin a tsec'tiquex in t' ån ich tu cotor u cajar tu c åja'an mac. Tar ca y ånxchun a tsec'tiquex ich u cajar Jerusal√©n. Ca' a tsec'tex ti' ca' u y ån c'axejob tu yorob soc u p' åticob u c'asirob soc C'uj cu jawsiob u si'pirob.‚Äù
\v 48 Ca' xic a waquex ti' mac a ba' caj a wirex, baxuc a ba' u ber teno'.
\v 49 Baxuc xan, je' in tuchi'tic techex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj an ten bic caj u toc araj C'uj. Je' u p'at år ta wicn ånex. Tar ca p'at årex ich u cajar Jerusal√©n hasta ca' bin a c' åmiquex a muq'uex a tar u tar ich ca'anan ti' in Tet C'uj.
\s1 Jes√∫s cu bin ich ca'anan
\r (Mr.‚ÄØ16.19‚Äë20)
\p 
\v 50 Jes√∫s caj u p åyaj u berob u cams åwinicob ich u xur u cajar. Tabar u c'uchob ich cajar Betania. Caj u nacsaj u c' åb ich yoc'or u cams åwinicob caj u c'ataj ti' C'uj ca' c ånantacob ten C'uj.
\v 51 Caj ts'oc u c'atic ti' C'uj ca' c ånantacob ten C'uj, C'uj caj u p åyaj Jes√∫s ca'anan.
\v 52 Jamach p'atob u cams åwinicob quir u c'ujinticob Jes√∫s. Caj ts'oquij caj binob ich u cajar Jerusal√©n, jach qui' yorob.
\v 53 Rajra' ti' y ånob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s ich carem naj tan u c'ujinticob C'uj.
